 <office:body>
  <office:text text:use-soft-page-breaks="true">
   <text:sequence-decls>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Illustration"/>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Table"/>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Text"/>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Drawing"/>
   </text:sequence-decls>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2">et i-a sit, si nulla actio rerum consequatur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Incĭdo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cado.<text:line-break/>Incīdo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cædo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inciens,</text:span> tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drägtig:</text:span></text:span> ovis, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incīlis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: fossa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(afledningsdike),</text:span> Cato. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Incīle</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: (i. = fossa, quæ in via fit ad deducendam aquam, Fs.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afledningsrör, trumma, dike:</text:span></text:span> i-ia aperire, Cato; excitare in clivo, Col.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> in i-i omnia adhæserunt, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incīlo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utfara emot ngn,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tadla:</text:span> Lucr., Lucil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Incino <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cano.<text:line-break/>Incipio, -cipisso <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Capio.<text:line-break/>Incis . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Incīdo, Cædo. <text:line-break/>Incit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cieo.<text:line-break/>Inclitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Clueo. <text:line-break/>Includo, -clusio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Claudo.<text:line-break/>Inclutus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Clueo.<text:line-break/>Incoct . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Incoquo, Coquo. <text:line-break/>Incognitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cognosco, Nosco. <text:line-break/>Incohibilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cohibeo, Habeo.<text:line-break/>Incola <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Incolo, Colo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incŏlŭmis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frisk och sund; wälbehållen, oskadd, räddad:</text:span></text:span> hæ latebræ dulces - i-em mihi te præstant Septembribus horis, Hor.; contra damnatum et mortuum pro i-i et vivo dicere; valeant cives mei - sint i-es; civitates salvæ et i-es; alqd per alqm i-e habere, retinere, C.; ad suos se recipere i-em, Cs.; status, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Incŏlŭmĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oskadt tillstånd; säkerhet, räddning:</text:span></text:span> i. est salutis tuta et integra conservatio; i-em habere ab aliquo, præstare alicui, C.; polliceri deditis i-em, Cs.; ex tot tamque gravibus procellis ad i-em pervenit, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">I</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">ncŏmĭtio</text:span>, 1.: (comitium, eo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Draga inför folkförsamlingen:</text:span></text:span> Pt. Curc. 400.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Incompt . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Como.<text:line-break/>Incontentus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Contendo, Tendo.<text:line-break/>Incrementum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Incresco, Cresco.<text:line-break/>Increto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Creta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">I</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">ncrētus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">part.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> incerno <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(se detta under</text:span> cerno) = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Påsiktad:</text:span></text:span> Hor. Sat. II. 4. 74.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Inculco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Calco, Calx.<text:line-break/>Incult . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Colo.<text:line-break/>Incumbo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cubo.<text:line-break/>Iucunabula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cunæ.<text:line-break/>Incuratus, -curia, -curios . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cura.<text:line-break/>Incurs . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Incurro, Curro. <text:line-break/>Incus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Incudo, Cudo.<text:line-break/>Incusatio, -cuso <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Causa.<text:line-break/>Incussus, Incutio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Quatio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indāgo,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(indāges, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: Prud.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utan twifwel är ordet bildadt af</text:span> indu <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> ago, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liksom</text:span> amb- āges): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">indrifning, inneslutning, omringande af wilda djur medelst nät eller menniskoskaror: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spår-ringning, skallgång, klappjagt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> oftast concret = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">nätgård, jagtkrets:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> trepidant alæ saltusque i-e cingunt, Vg.; muniri silvis et flumine velut i-e, Cs.; densos i-e colles claudere, Tib.; agros i-e cingere, Ov.; vastāque feras i-e claudit, Luc.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> doctrinæ i-bus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nät)</text:span> persuadere alicui, Pn.; mille poenarum i-e noxios claudere, Pn. ep.; orbos velut i-e capere, T.; res altioris i-is (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som fordrar djupare forskning),</text:span> Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indāgo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indāgor</text:span> (Varr.), 1.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">egentl. (om jagt): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spåra, uppspåra, -drifwa:</text:span></text:span> canis natus ad i-dum, C.; capere feras i-antem (alii: indaganter), Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppspåra, utforska, utleta:</text:span></text:span> omnia i. et odorari; indicia, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indāgātio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spårande, forskning:</text:span></text:span> veri; rerum, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indāgātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som går på spår efter, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppspårare, -spanare:</text:span></text:span> celatorum, i., Pt.; Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indāgātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Forskarinna, uppspårarinna:</text:span></text:span> o vitæ philosophia lux, o virtutis i., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Indaudio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Audio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indĕ,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wäl af</text:span> in <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> de <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med förkortning af det sista ordet; jfr</text:span> dein, deinde): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Derifrån; deraf; derefter:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rummet:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Derifrån, dädan:</text:span></text:span> apud Græcos i-eque perlapsus ad nos et usque ad Oceanum Hercules, C.; in fines Vocontiorum pervenit: i. in Allobrogum fines exercitum ducit, Cs.; in Macedoniam, i. in Siciliam delatus est; tenuere arcem Sabini i-eque - descenderunt in æquum, L.; classe ad Euboeam appulsa Eretriam ceperunt: i. ad Atticam accesserunt, N.; occupat - currum - et invito grates agit i. parenti, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">på den sidan;</text:span></text:span> (hinc et inde = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">åt båda sidor;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> jfr</text:span> ab): hinc militum, i. locorum asperitas, T.; h. atque i. patens et nuda pæne cathedra, Juv.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Derefter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om ordning i rummet):</text:span> Cæsar sex legiones expeditas ducebat, post eas totius exercitus impedimenta collocarat, i. duas legiones - agmen claudebant, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Derefter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i tiden), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">derpå, derifrån;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tillsammans med andra tidsbestämningar = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ända,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> allt:</text:span> i. usque repetens; jam i. a principio, C.; ova parire solet pinnis genus condecoratum, non animam: post i. venit divinitus pullis ipsa anima; i. loci <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= derefter),</text:span> Enn. Ann. II. 22.; i. Tarquinius regnare coepit; i. Tullum regem populus jussit; jam i. ab initio Faustulo spes fuerat, regiam stirpem apud se educari, L.; i. Ephesum pervenit, N.; talibus i. modis ora indignantia solvit, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dermed, derifrån</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om början):</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Deraf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i partitiv mening = af dem o. s. w.:</text:span> fratri nati sunt filii duo: i. adoptavi alterum, Ter.; stant calices: minor i. fabas, olus alter habebat, Ov.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Deraf, derifrån,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i uttryck för ursprung l. orsak:</text:span> i. (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på denna föreställning grundar sig)</text:span> Homeri tota νεκυία, C.; i. nomen inditum, <text:soft-page-break/>L.; i. (i. e. e silice nati) genus durum sumus experiensque laborum et documenta damus, qua simus origine nati, Ov.; i. deductum est vocabulum, Qu.; i. caput morbi, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indĭdem</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dersammastädes ifrån, från samma ställe</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">källa:</text:span></text:span> expromere, Pt.; i. Ameriā an ex hac urbe sicarii?, C.; i. Thebis, N.; i. ex Aventino; falsi testes, falsa signa ex ea officina exibant: venena i. intestinæque cædes, L. XXXIX. 8.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Indefessus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Defatiscor, Fatim. <text:line-break/>Indefletus, -flexus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fleo, Flecto. <text:line-break/>Indemnatus, -demnis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Damnum.<text:line-break/>Index, Indicat . . ., -dicina, -dicium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Indĭco, Dĭco. <text:line-break/>India, -dicus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Indus.<text:line-break/>Indict . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Indīco, Dīco.<text:line-break/>Indidem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inde. <text:line-break/>Indigena, -genus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Geno.<text:line-break/>Indigens, -digentia, -digeo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Egeo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indĭges,</text:span> ĕtis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Landsgud</text:span></text:span> (ἥρως ἐγχώριος), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">halfgud,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> förgudad menniska, eg. i landet född (af</text:span> gigno?) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eller boende (af</text:span> ago, Serv. ad Vg. Georg. I. 498. Aen. XII. 794): Lares, dii Novensiles, I-tes, divi, quibus est potestas nostrum hostiumque, L.; di patrii, I-tes et Romule Vestaque mater, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Indigest . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Digero, Gero.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indĭgĭto,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> Fs. (Paul. Diac.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förklaradt med</text:span> nominare, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl. Corssens (Beiträge zur lateinischen Formenbildung</text:span> p. 425) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sannolika förmodan jemte</text:span> axamentum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildadt af præp.</text:span> in <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och stammen i</text:span> ajo (agio, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">säga): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åkalla, anropa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en gud enligt bestämdt formulär:</text:span> Mcb. Sat. I. 12. 21; 17. 5. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indĭgĭtāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åkallan,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> bön (af</text:span> Paul. Diac. 3. 114. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förklaradt med</text:span> incantamentum); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">samling af böner, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bönbok, ritual</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bok, hwari woro upptecknade de formler och sätt, hwarpå hwarje gud skulle åkallas</text:span> (rite vocari): Serv. ad Vg. Aen. XII. 794.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Indigus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Indigeo, Egeo.<text:line-break/>Indipiscor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Apiscor.<text:line-break/>Indiscrete, -cretus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Discerno, Cerno.<text:line-break/>Individuus, -divisus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Divido.<text:line-break/>Indo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Do <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Indu. <text:line-break/>Indolentia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Doleo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indŏles,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af samma rot som</text:span> inoleo, adolesco, suboles, proles; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> adolesco): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. wäxt, brodd till ngt:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i abstract mening = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Anlag, ämne, gry</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt; absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">anlag; art, förmåga, gåfwor:</text:span></text:span> i. virtutis, ad virtutem; i. bona, C.; magna regis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till konung)</text:span> in eo apparebat; Tullus quum i-e animi, tum spe victoriæ ferocior; hæc i. vitiorum virtutumque in Hannibale adolescente erat; tanta i. in Lavinia erat, L.; dare speciem i-is, Pn. ep.; adolescens lætæ i-is, Gell.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">concret = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Det uppwäxande slägtet; ungdomen</text:span></text:span> (proles, suboles): i. nobilitatis a Tarquinio excerpebatur, Val.; Romanæ i-i Virgilium enarrat Servins, Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Indolesco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Doleo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">I</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">ndŏmābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: (domo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Otämjbar:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indŭ</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indŏ</text:span> <text:line-break/>(endo), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Præp.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">in: I, på:</text:span></text:span> i. foro; i. mari, Enn. Ann. 243. 425.; Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Induciæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Indutiæ.<text:line-break/>Induct . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Induco, Duco.<text:line-break/>Inducula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Induo. <text:line-break/>Indugredior = Ingredior, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gradior.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indulgeo,</text:span> dulsi, dultum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> dulcis?):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med blott personligt object:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara god, mild; wisa godhet mot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">gynna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wara öm, mån om</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wara flat mot, wara swag för; öfwerse med, se genom fingret med, lemna frihet åt:</text:span></text:span> huic legioni Cæsar præcipue i-serat, Cs.; uni maxime, i., N.; filio nimium, Ter.; peccatis alicujus, C.; sibi i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bete sig egenmäktigt);</text:span> sibi i. liberaliter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lefwa fritt);</text:span> genio, Ps. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc.</text:span>: ejicienda est - hæc mollities animi: nimis me i-o, Ter.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui aliquid</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillstädja, unna, bewilja:</text:span></text:span> nihil his ad Antonium violandum, N.; balneum (Prusinis Trajanus), Pn. ep.; rudem alicui, Su. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui rei</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hängifwa sig åt, lemna fritt lopp åt; wara frikostig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med:</text:span> dolori, N.; insano dolori, Vg.; animo; amori, Ov.; spei, Ct.; ordinibus, Vg.; hospitiis nulla gens effusius, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Beflita</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig om, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wara mån</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om:</text:span> eloquentiæ, Qu.; hospitio, Vg.; valetudini, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indulgens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">God, mild, öfwerseende; fiat:</text:span></text:span> nutrix, C.; pater, N.; in captivos i., L.; imperator i-simus, Pn.; pater, mater, Inscr. sæp.; pater nimis, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indulgenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Godmodigt, mildt, lenfälligt:</text:span></text:span> loqui, C.; habere captivos i., L.; agere, Vell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indulgentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Godhet, ömhet, mildhet, nåd:</text:span></text:span> omni i-a nutrire puerum, L.; Cæsaris, C.; eā i-ā fuit in suos, ut -, N.; imperatoris, Pn.; materiemque sibi ducis (i. e. Augusti) i. quærit, Juv.; cæli, Vg.; fortunæ, Vell.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flathet:</text:span></text:span> intempestiva, Sen.; nocet, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nåd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">eftergift:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pĕrindulgens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mycket god, efterlåten:</text:span></text:span> in patrem, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Indumentum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Induo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Induo,</text:span> ui, ūtum, 3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> ex-uo):<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: (insticka, -foga, -weckla, blott</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">refl.</text:span>) se i-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> indui: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intränga, inweckla, insnärja sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i -; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">spetsa sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. bet.:</text:span> venti se in nubes, C.; se in laqueum, Pt.; se hastis, L.; se vallis acutissimis, Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Insnärja sig i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> se in captiones; se dum expedire vult, i-it; <text:soft-page-break/>sua confessione i-i, C. <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Påtaga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett (åtsittande) klädesplagg</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">alqd</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">påkläda</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">sibi</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui aliquid</text:span>), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ikläda, bekläda</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquem aliqua re</text:span>):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> talaria; torquem, C.; sibi loricam, Pt.; Herculi tunicam Dejanira, C.; se veste, Ter.; soccis; muliebri vestitu i-tum esse C.; - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc.</text:span>-<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">best. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>: vestem i-i, Ct.; exuvias i-tus Achilli, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ikläda, kläda, bekläda,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om utseende, gestalt o. s. w.:</text:span> dii i-ti specie humana; beluæ - forma humana i-tæ, C.; in vultus et terga ferarum alqm, Vg.; pomis se arbor i-it, Vg.; fructu se vitis, Col. - habes somnum imaginem mortis eamque quotidie i-is, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Antaga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> namn, tänkesätt, roll o. s. w.:</text:span> cognomen, C.; novum ingenium, L.; hostiles spiritus; proditorem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(spela),</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indūcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klädning:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indūmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klädebonad:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indūsium</text:span> <text:line-break/>(intusium), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lintyg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (qwinnors):</text:span> Varr., Non.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indūsiārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. förfärdigar lintyg:</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indūsiātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">klädd i -:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indūtĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. instickes, infogas:</text:span> vomis, Cato.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indūtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">påklädande (mots.</text:span> amictus = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">drapering kring kroppen), beklädnad:</text:span> ea, quæ sunt i-ui, Varr., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indŭviæ</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Indŭvies, Gell. IX. 13.), ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kläder,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> klädnad:</text:span> i-æ tuæ atque exuviæ uxoris, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indŭvium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: arboris, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bark:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sŭpĕrinduo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">taga, ikläda sig ofwanpå:</text:span> pænulam, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Indupedio, <text:line-break/>Induperator = Impedio, Imperator.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>ndus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Asien.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>ndus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> - i, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">indisk, Inder, Inderne.</text:span> <text:line-break/>India, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Indien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Indĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">indisk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Indusi . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Induo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Industrius,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Werksam, driftig, rask, företagsam:</text:span></text:span> in rebus gerendis acer et i. Dionysius; i-os homines Græci studiosos - doloris appellant, nos commodius laboriosos, C.; armis i., Juv.; vir innocens et i., Su.; <text:span text:style-name="T2">Comp.</text:span> i-ior, Pt., i-iior, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Industria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Werksamhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. egenskap), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">werksamhetsifwer; drift, sträfsamhet;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (practisk) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">duglighet;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (factisk) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">werksamhet:</text:span></text:span> contemnuntur ii, in quibus nulla est i.; i. in agendo; celeritas in conficiendo, in labore perferendo i.; stimuli i-æ et laboris; summa in eo spectatur i.; vinci opificum antelucanā i-ā; Attici labore et i-a factum est, ut -; tua et admirabilis natura et exquisita doctrina et singularis i.; in accusando cognita est L. Fufii i,; i-am oratoris in plura studia distrahi nolim; illa benignitas, quæ constat ex opera et i-<text:soft-page-break/>a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.:</text:span> ea, quæ fit pecuniā); adolescentium et in bellicis et in civilibus officiis vigeat i-a; si quid oratoriæ laudis nostrā attulimus i-ā; ponere i-am in aliqua re, C. - de i-a = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med flit, med afsigt (sökt):</text:span> lepos major et magis de i-a in Cæsare, C.; ob i-am (id.), Pt.; ludos ex i-a parat, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Industriōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Full af werksamhetsifwer, mycket werksam:</text:span></text:span> Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Industriōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Industrie</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span> -: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Raskt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">med ifwer; med drift:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span> milites ea, quæ imperasset, diligenter et i. administrarent; i. tutari, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īndūtiæ</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indūciæ</text:span>, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stillestånd, wapenhwila:</text:span></text:span> triginta dierum i-as facere, pacisci cum hoste, C.; in centum annos i-æ datæ; valebat apud Vejentes pacta i-arum fides; jam exierant i-æ, L.; petere, impetrare, N.; agitare, Sa.; rumpere, Js.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppehåll, ledighet, hwila:</text:span></text:span> litium, Pt.; in foro, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Indutilis, -dutus, -duviæ, -duvium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Induo.<text:line-break/>Inedia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Edo.<text:line-break/>Ineffabilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Effari, Fari.<text:line-break/>Inemptus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Emo. <text:line-break/>Inenodabilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Nodus.<text:line-break/>Inept . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Aptus. <text:line-break/>Inermis, -ermus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Arma.<text:line-break/>Iners, Inert . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ars.<text:line-break/>Inesco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Esca, Edo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">I</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">nexperrectus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: (expergiscor): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ej uppwäckt:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Inexplebilis, -pletus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Expleo, Pleo. <text:line-break/>Inextricabilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Extrico, Tricæ.<text:line-break/>Infabre <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Faber.<text:line-break/>Infacund . . ., Infam . . ., Infandus, Infans, Infant . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fari.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">I</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">nfaustus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: (faustus, faveo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Olycksam, olycksbådande:</text:span></text:span> Vg., Ov., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Infect . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inficio, Facio.<text:line-break/>Infens . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fendo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(Infer),</text:span> fĕra, fĕrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: (<text:span text:style-name="T2">nom. masc. sing.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">obr.): s. är nedanför, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedre, undre:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> supera, i-a, prima, ultima; mare i-um (= Etruscum); loca i-a, C.; interea sol albus recessit ad infera noctis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(den undre sidan af werlden),</text:span> Enn. ap. C. de Div. I. §. 107.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Underjordisk:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> isynn.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infĕri</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">de underjordiske, underjordens wäsenden</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (underjorden):</text:span> dii superi et i., Pt.; ad superos videtur deos potius, quam ad i-os pervenisse (Scipio); triceps apud i-os Cerberus; rationis ignoratio finxit i-os; ad <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> apud i-os poenas luere; ab i-is mortuos, testes excitare, revocare alqm, C.; exsistere ab i-is, L. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">Comp.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infĕrior</text:span>, ōris: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedre, lägre:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> ex i-ore loco dicere; ambulatio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(promenadplats),</text:span> C.; <text:soft-page-break/>ripa, Ct.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sednare:</text:span></text:span> ætate i., C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Underlägsen; ringare; swagare;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec.: i samhällsställning </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ringare, underordnad:</text:span></text:span> Timotheus belli laude non i. fuit quam pater; superior ordine, i-or fortunā, C.; navium numero i., Cs.; copiis, N.; Alexander i. foret, Ct.; humanos casus virtute i-es putare, C.; in i-es crudelis, in superiores contumax, C. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">Superl.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infĭmus</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nederst, lägst:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> locus mundi i.; i-a auricula mollior; summum, medium, i-um, C.; Janum ad i-um Argiletum Numa - fecit; i-a urbis loca circa forum, L.; ad i-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till grunden, bottnen);</text:span> ab i-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från foten l. från grunden),</text:span> Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: (till samhällsställning och sinnelag):</text:span> i-a fortuna et condicio servorum; i-a fæx populi; plebs; civis; i-o loco natus, C.; Atticus communis i-is, par principibus videbatur, N.; nunquam fere (in suffragio) ita descenderunt, ut ad i-os pervenirent; fautor i-i generis hominum; preces <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ödmjuka, krypande),</text:span> L.; ad i-as obtestationes procumbere, T.<text:line-break/>2.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Īmus</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nederst, lägst:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> ab imis unguibus ad summum verticem; ab imis faucibus, C.; radix montis, Cs.; tigna ab imo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nedifrån)</text:span> præacuta, Cs.; mare totum a sedibus imis ruere; gemitum dat pectore ab imo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från djupet af - -);</text:span> gemitus lacrimabilis imo auditur tumulo, Vg.; fundus; hæc Janus summus ab imo prodocet; faber <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. bor längst nere),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sist:</text:span></text:span> (persona) servetur ad imum, qualis ab incepto processerit; primo ne medium, medio ne discrepet imum, Hor.; mensis, Ov. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bild. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ringast:</text:span></text:span> valet ima summis mutare deus, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infrā</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> infer):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedan, nedanför; längre ned:</text:span></text:span> earum literarum exemplum i. scriptum est; partes stomachi, quæ sunt i., C.; nunquam fere i. (sc. secundam classem) descendebant, L.; non seges est i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i underjorden),</text:span> Tib.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Præp.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedanför, nedanom, under:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> i. Saturnum Jovis stella fertur; accumbere i. alqm, C.; collocare alqm i. alqm, Su. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tiden (sednare):</text:span> Homerus non i. Lycurgum fuit, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i ställning l. wärde):</text:span> is est i. infimos, Ter.; et secundis et i-a secundos locus est; omnia, quæ homini accidere possunt, i. se putare, C.; i. decem; i. se putare alqd, Pn.; quid nobis i. Ventidium dejectus Oriens objecerit?, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infĕrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lägre, för lågt ned:</text:span></text:span> altius evectus cælum cremabis, i. terram, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Īmĭtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Från grunden:</text:span></text:span> Gell., Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Īmŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nederst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i smekande uttryck):</text:span> Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infernus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedre, lägre:</text:span></text:span> partes i-æ, C.; amnis ex Molosside fluens in stagna <text:soft-page-break/>i-a, L.; mare i-um (= inferum), Luc.; i-a = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">underlifwet,</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Underjordisk:</text:span></text:span> dii cælestes, terrestres, i-i, L.; i-us Dis, i-a Juno, Vg.; apud i-os, Ppt.; i-a tangere, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infernas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: abies, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. wäxer på låg mark, lågland:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inferne</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dernedan (under jord):</text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infĭmātis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den lägste, ringaste (mots.</text:span> summates viri): Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infĭmĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">största ringhet:</text:span> Amm.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infĭmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förnedra:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Infercio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Farcio.<text:line-break/>Inferiæ, -ferialis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Infero, Fero.<text:line-break/>Inferior, -ferius, Infern . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Infer.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Infestus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rigtad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">beredd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till anfall l. strid, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hotande, fiendtlig; förbittrad, hätsk:</text:span></text:span> i-o spiculo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fälld pik)</text:span> petere alqd; pila i-a; i-o agmine ad urbem veniunt, L.; ardens i-o vulnere eum inse - quitur Pyrrhus, Vg.; latro, Hor.; i-um ferri in suos; clamor; oculi; animus; odium; fortuna, C.; animus dis hominibusque i., Sa.; adeo i-is animis concurrerunt, L.; i. in alqm, C.; is erat ei i-simus, N.; sibi i-os Teucros metuebat, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hotad, osäker, utsatt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för -:</text:span> tempus ætatis aliorum libidine i-um; iter, saltus i.; mare; provinciam i-am reddere, habere; pars Ciliciæ i-sima, C.; in dies i-or esse senectus Servii, i-ius regnum coepit, L.; itinera, Cs.; i-us telis, Ct. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infeste</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fiendtligt, hätskt:</text:span></text:span> i-sime contendere, C.; facere in alqm, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infesto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra osäker, ofreda; hota, angripa, skada:</text:span></text:span> mare, Vell.; filii vita i-ata, C.; munitiones i-re, Cs.; grues alqm, Col.; muscus arborem, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infestātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Angripare:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Inficet . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Facetus.<text:line-break/>Inficiæ = Infitiæ, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fateor.<text:line-break/>Inficio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Facio. <text:line-break/>Inficior = Infitior, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fateor.<text:line-break/>Infim . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Infer.<text:line-break/>Infinit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Finis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Infit,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">verb. Def.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Börjar; börjar tala:</text:span></text:span> caput erigere i., Lucr.; ibi i. Albanus; tum ita Tullus i., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Infitiæ, -fitialis, -fitiat . . ., fitior <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fateor.<text:line-break/>Inflat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inflo, Flo.<text:line-break/>Infletus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fleo.<text:line-break/>Inflex . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inflecto, Flecto. <text:line-break/>Influxio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Influo, Fluo.<text:line-break/>Informis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Forma.<text:line-break/>Infra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Infer.<text:line-break/>Infract . . ., -fragilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Infringo, Frango.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">I</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">nfrēnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: (frenum): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Obetslad:</text:span></text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Infrenis, -freno, -frenus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frenum. <text:line-break/>Infringo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frango.<text:line-break/>Infrons <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Frons. <text:line-break/>Infrunitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fruniscor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Infŭla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bindel, hufwudbindel,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt de, hwilka, bestående af långa band af kardad (ospunnen) ull och i wissa mellanrum omlindade af trådar, buros af prester, offerdjur, skyddsökande:</text:span> tantam rem tamquam pueriles delicias in i-is depingere, C.; sacerdotes cum i-is et verbenis, C.; Apollinis i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. bars af Apollos prest),</text:span> Vg.; (Iphigeniæ) i. virgineos circum data comptus ex utraque pari malarum parte profusa est, Lucr.; claris insignibus (magistratus) velut i-is velatos ad mortem destinari; navis velata i-is et ramis oleæ occurrit, L. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Helgedom, heliga ting; prydnader:</text:span></text:span> his insignibus et i-is imperii (i. e. agris publicis) venditis, C.; hæ literæ apud quosdam i-arum loco sunt, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infŭlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">prydd med</text:span> infula: (hostia), Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Infundibulum, -fusio, -fusus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Infnndo, Fundo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>ngævŏnes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">germaniskt folk.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>ngauni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liguriskt folk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Ingenero, -geniatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Geno. <text:line-break/>Ingenicul . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Genu.<text:line-break/>Ingenios . . ., -genitus, -genium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Geno.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingens,</text:span> tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stor, ofantlig, wäldig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i yttre och inre men.):</text:span> ex i-i immensoque campo in exiguum gyrum compellere; i. immanisque præda; divitiæ i-es, C.; æs alienum; sumptus, Sa.; facinus; gratia, Ter.; insula, Cs.; procella; vir i-is spiritus, L.; septem i-ia (cervorum) corpora; i. moles, pontus, pluvia, vox, bellum, manus, gemitus, Sarpēdon; gloria Teucrorum, Vg.; fossa; pinus; acervus; strepitus; i-ia facta (Romuli); i. ingenium latet hoc sub corpore; virtus; flagitium, Hor.; hostis, Sil.; Cimbri parva nunc civitas, sed gloriā i., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Ingenu . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Geno.<text:line-break/>Ingestabilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ingero, Gero.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inglŭvies</text:span>, ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kräfwa, swalg;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> meton. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">glupskhet, fråsseri:</text:span></text:span> vacua avium, Col.; serpens explet i-em, Vg.; stringere rem i-e, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Ingredior, Ingress . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gradior.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inguen,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ljumske:</text:span></text:span> dextrum, Vg.; tunicam obscoenum ad i. subducere, Hor.; prodest i-bus, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på ett träd: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Weck,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarifrån grenen utgår:</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inguĭnālis</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ingnĭnārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Inhibeo, -hibitio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Habeo.<text:line-break/>Inibi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ibi, Is.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Inject . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Injicio, Jacio. <text:line-break/>Inigo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ago.<text:line-break/>Inimic . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Amicus, Amo. <text:line-break/>Iniqu . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Aequus.<text:line-break/>Init . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ineo, Eo.<text:line-break/>Injur . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Jus.<text:line-break/>Injussus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Jubeo.<text:line-break/>Innabilis, Innato, Inno <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> No. <text:line-break/>Innoc . . ., Innoxius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Noceo.<text:line-break/>Innub . . ., Innuptus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Nubo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ī</text:span>no, us <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Īnōus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ĭ</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">noblītus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: (obliviscor): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ej glömsk; minnesgod:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">nŏlens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: (oleo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Luktlös:</text:span></text:span> olivum, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnŏleo,</text:span> ēvi, ĭtum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> adolesco): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inympa, inplanta:</text:span></text:span> natura induit nobis i-vitque in ipsis statim principiis amorem nostri et caritatem, Gell. XII. 5. 7.; inŏlitus, Jul. Val. de gestis Alex.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭnŏlesco</text:span>, ēvi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wäxa in uti</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">alicui</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rota sig in i, blifwa förtrolig med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> huc aliena ex arbore germen includunt udoque docent i-re libro; multa diu concreta modis i-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i själen)</text:span> miris, Vg.; assidua veterum scriptorum tractatione linguæ illius i-verat ea vox, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Inominalis, -natus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Omen.<text:line-break/>Inopia, -piosus, Inops <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Opis.<text:line-break/>Inoratus, Inorus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ōs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">nōtiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: (otium): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Orolig, beställsam:</text:span></text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inquam</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> sum; inquio, Prisc. VIII. 11), inquis (Hor., Ps.), inquit(l:<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sta och 3:e personen äro</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">præs.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och äfwen</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pf.</text:span>), inquĭmus (Hor.), inquiunt (C.), inquībat (C.), inquies (Catl.), inquiet (C.), inquii (Catl.), inquisti (C.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">imper.</text:span> inque. inquito (Pt.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">verb. defect.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som anwändes till anförande af annans ord i direct tal: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Säger:</text:span></text:span> (inquam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inskjutes efter ett eller flera af de anförda orden l. sättes efter dem alla; subjectet står, der det uttryckes med ett serskildt nomen l. pronomen, antingen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">före</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> de anförda orden, eller ock näst efter, sällan näst före</text:span> inquam): <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> dabuntur, inque; i-ito et me tangito, Pt. Bacch. 883. Rud. 1342; quum ille dixisset: tu igitur non nihil vides? Ego vero, inquam, video, villam tuam; tu vero, inquisti, molestus non eris; jubebis te, inquit, suscitari?; non potui mihi, i. Lamia, formam ipse fingere; tibi ego, Antipho (<text:span text:style-name="T2">voc.</text:span>), has sero, i-it, arbores; tum Crassus: vide, i., quam in levi arte plus adhibeatur laboris, quam in hac; equidem probo ista, Crassus i.; ubi sunt, i-unt, scyphi?; quid id ad me, i-es, C.; huic ille: nulla, i., mora est, N.; nonne vides, aliquis i-et; communi sensu plane caret, i-mus, Hor.; verum, i-is, amo: verum mihi dicito de me, Ps. I. 55.; Galla mea est, i-it, Juv.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. inquam, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid återknytande af en genom mellansatser afbruten period l. wid emphatiskt upprepande af ett l. flera ord:</text:span> delector enim <text:soft-page-break/>- quamquam te non possum corrumpere - delector, i., et familiā vestrā et nomine; virtus, virtus, i., et conciliat amicitias. et conservat, C.; libera per terras unde hæc animantibus exstat, unde est hæc, inquam, fatis avulsa voluntas, Lucr.<text:line-break/>b. inquit, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid inkast l. anföranden, som tänkas göras af ett obestämdt subject: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Säger man:</text:span></text:span> Synephebos ego, i-it, potius Cæcili quam Menandri legam?, C.; lædere gaudes, i., Hor.; Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inquĭlīnus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(<text:span text:style-name="T3">Inquĭlīna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> incola, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liks.</text:span> laquear <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> lacus?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som bor i främmande land l. hus: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utbörding; hyresgäst:</text:span></text:span> Cicero i. civis urbis Romæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ss. bördig från ett</text:span> municipium), Sa.; non solum i-i, sed etiam mures migrarunt; te i-o, non domino, C.; privatarum ædium, Su.; = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">samboende, granne i huset:</text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inquĭno,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Orena, besudla, nedsöla, befläcka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> aqua cadaveribus i-ta, C.; caput merdis, Hor.; uva pedes pressantes, Ppt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> se libidinibus, vitiis et flagitiis; comitia largitione; agros turpissimis possessoribus; officiosam amicitiam nomine criminoso; versus i-tus insuavissima litera, C.; famam alicujus, L.; argumenta sua poēta puerorum amoribus, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inquĭnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">moraliskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oren, smutsig, gemen:</text:span></text:span> homo ore, manu i-us; ea ratio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bewekelsegrund)</text:span> i-sima est; quis in voluptatibus i-ior?; sermo i-simus, blanditiæ flagitiosæ, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Färgad; inwigd, bewandrad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ngt (jfr</text:span> tinctus): vellus murice, Mt.; literis, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inquĭnāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: confluxerunt in hanc urbem multi i. loquentes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(orent),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inquĭnāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Orenlighet:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Cŏinquĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedsmutsa, -söla; smitta:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> stercore; progeniem suam, Col. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> scelere c-ri, Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Inquiro, Inquisit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Quæro. <text:line-break/>Insan . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sanus.<text:line-break/>Insat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Satis. <text:line-break/>Inscendo, -scensus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Scando.<text:line-break/>Insci . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Scio.<text:line-break/>Inscript . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inscribo, Scribo. <text:line-break/>Insculpo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Scalpo.<text:line-break/>Insecabilis, Inseco (-cui) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Seco.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Insĕco</text:span> (insĕquo?), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">obrukl. verbum, af hwilket förekomma formerna:</text:span> insece, <text:span text:style-name="T2">imper. præs.,</text:span> insecenda (Liv. Andr., Cato), insexit (Enn. ap. Fs. 111. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">M.): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förtälja, beskrifwa:</text:span></text:span> (Gellius XVIII. 9. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sätter ordet i sammanhang med</text:span> sequor, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ehuru han uppgifwer, att det i gamla skrifter aldrig förekom med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">qu,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och med gr.</text:span> ἔννέπω, ἔσπετε; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Bugge, Tidskrift for Philologi 1866, 18, 19.; Curtius, griech. Etymologi 427 sammanför</text:span> insece <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> ἔσπετε (σεσέπετε) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och st. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">säga</text:span>): virum mihi, Camena, insece versutum, Liv. Andr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwersättn. af</text:span> Ἄνδρα μοι ἔννεπε, Μοῦσα, πολύτροπον); insece, Musa, manu <text:soft-page-break/>Romanorum induperator quod quisque in bello gessit cum rege Philippo, Enn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Insectio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Berättelse</text:span></text:span> (narratio), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl.</text:span> Gell. XVIII. 9.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Insecta, -sectura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inseco, Seco. <text:line-break/>Insectanter, -sectat . . ., -secto, -sector, -secut . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Insequor, Sequor.<text:line-break/>Insepultus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sepelio.<text:line-break/>Insero <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> II. Sero. <text:line-break/>Insert . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Insero, II. Sero.<text:line-break/>Insicia, -siciolum, -sicium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inseco, Seco. <text:line-break/>Insid . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sedeo.<text:line-break/>Insign . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Signum. <text:line-break/>Insilia, -silio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Salio.<text:line-break/>Insipiens, -sipient . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sapio.<text:line-break/>Insit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Insero, I. Sero.<text:line-break/>Insolabiliter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Solor. <text:line-break/>Insolatio, Insolo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sol.<text:line-break/>Insolens, -solent . . ., -solesco, -solitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Soleo.<text:line-break/>Insomn . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sopio.<text:line-break/>Inspect . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inspicio, Specio.<text:line-break/>Inspergo, Inspers . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Spargo. <text:line-break/>Inspicio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Specio.<text:line-break/>Instabilis, -bilitas, Instans, Instant . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Stabilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Insto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">under</text:span> Sto.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Instar,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">indecl.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">concret: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bild:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (æquivalent), ngt, s. till storhet, wärde, betydelse är lika, motswarar, går upp emot, ersätter ngt annat: sål.</text:span> i. rei = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">så stor, så mycket, så god</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lika med; s. motswarar, s. ersätter:</text:span></text:span> Cæsar equi sui i. pro æde Veneris - dedicavit, Su.; parvum i. eorum, quæ spe concepisset, receptas Hispanias (Scipio) ducebat, L.; non vici i., sed urbis, C.; i. montis equum - ædificant; munus a te fundi suburbani i. exspectant; se clientes appellari, mortis i. putant; Plato mihi i. omnium est; unus ille dies mihi immortalitatis i. est, C.; vix duarum - legiuncularum i. in castris regis videretis, L.; principes sunt i. deorum, T.; mearum epistolarum - Tiro habet i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ungefär)</text:span> septuaginta, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">abstr. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utseende, storhet, betydelse:</text:span></text:span> ad i. castrorum, Js.; navis urbis i. habere videtur; ea vix minimi momenti i. habent; terra ad universi mundi complexum i. habet puncti <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(medelpunkt),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Instauro,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förnya, upprepa; åter anställa, återgifwa, återställa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> seclus - pristinum renovavit et i-vit; cavete, ne nova proscriptio a vobis i-ta esse videatur; cædem, C.; bella, L.; epulas, T.; dii, talia Grajis i-etis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wedergällen);</text:span> i-ti animi regis defendere tecta, Vg.; tunicas, Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: om offentliga lekar l. gudstjensthandlingar, wid hwilkas förrättning fel blifwit begånget:</text:span> feriæ Latinæ i-antur; id sacrificium (Bonæ Deæ a Clodio pollutum) Vestales i-arunt; ludi i-ti, C.; ludos Romanos diem unum i-arunt, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Instaurātīcius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: dies <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på hwilken skådespelen förnyas),</text:span> Mcb.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Instaurātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förnyande; anställande på nytt:</text:span></text:span> si ludi non <text:soft-page-break/>rite facti sunt, mentes deorum i-e placantur, C.; ludos ex i-e parare, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Instaurātīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. förnyas, åter anställes:</text:span> ludi, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Instaurātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">återställare:</text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Instīgo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> in -, distinguo?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppegga, -wigla, pådrifwa, reta, hetsa:</text:span></text:span> auditores orator; domus mea ardebat i-ante te, C.; dea i-ante fit; Romanos in Hannibalem i., L.; ad arma alqm, Vell.; me i-asti, Ter.; iracundiam, Sen.; sermonibus alqm, Col.; canes in alqm, Petr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Instīgātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: auditorum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Instīgātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Instīgātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppwiglare, -hetsare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (-inna):</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Instinct . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Instinguo, Stinguo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Instĭta,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bräm</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (kring nedersta randen af en romersk matronas</text:span> tunica): subsutā talos tegit i. veste, Hor.; longa, Ov. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skärp; band; säng-gjord:</text:span></text:span> ventrem constringere i-ā, Petr.; thyrsi, St.; Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Institio, Institor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> Insisto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">under</text:span> Insto), Instituo, Institut . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> Status) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sto. <text:line-break/>Instruct . . ., Instrumentum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Instruo, Struo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Insuāsum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mörk färg:</text:span> Pt. (d. l.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>nsŭber, bris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Insŭbres, um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> ium, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Insubrer, galliskt folk i norra Italien (hufwudstad</text:span> Mediolanum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Milano).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Insŭbĭdus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Enfaldig, smaklös:</text:span></text:span> nihil est istis i-ius; scitamenta (ornamenta orationis) i-a et inertia, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Insŭbĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Insuefactus, -suetudo, -suetus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sueo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Insŭla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: (sŏlum?)<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ö, holme:</text:span></text:span> i. Britannia; i. in fluvio Fibreno, C.; Paros i., N.; Tenedos i.; i-æ in Ionio magno, Vg. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gård, fastighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i stad, s. bildar ett eget qwarter för sig o. ej sammanhänger med andra, wanl. bestående af många större och mindre uthyrda lägenheter (mots.</text:span> domus = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">palats, s. bebos af egaren ensam):</text:span> i-am proscripsit, C.; domuum et i-arum, quæ amissæ sunt, rationem inire haud promptum fuerit, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Insŭlānus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öbo:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Insŭlāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. hör till l. är på ö, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ö-:</text:span></text:span> Js. XXXII. 2.; Amm.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Insŭlārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hyresgäst:</text:span> Petr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Insŭlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förwandlad till ö:</text:span> terra, Ap. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Insŭlensis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: = insularis: Sol.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Insŭlōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rik på öar:</text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pæninsŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(peninsŭla): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nästan ö, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Halfö:</text:span></text:span> Catl., L., Pn</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Insuls . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sal.<text:line-break/>Insult . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Insilio, Salio.<text:line-break/>Insumo, -sumptio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sumo, Emo. <text:line-break/>Insuper <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Super.<text:line-break/>Intact . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Tango.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intāmĭnātus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> contamino): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Obefläckad:</text:span></text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Intectus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Tego.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intĕger,</text:span> gra, grum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förmodligen af</text:span> in <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och roten</text:span> tag <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> tango, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">således eg.: orörd, som är i sitt förra, sitt rätta skick, oförminskad, oförändrad:</text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hel, oförminskad, oskadd; oförderfwad, oförfalskad:</text:span></text:span> i-a signa literarum; quum curia deflagrasset, lituus i. inventus est; veritas; tam i-æ sunt sententiæ, tam novæ, tam veræ, C.; fons, Lucr.; mane i-o etiamtum die, Hor.; sapor, Hor., Col.; i-ā etiam domo suā, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ej widrörd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">widgjord; oafgjord, oförändrad; ny;</text:span></text:span> causam alicui i-am reservare; rem ad suum reditum i-am esse (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwila, hållas öppen)</text:span> jussit; vel facere vel non facere i-um est mihi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(står mig fritt);</text:span> non i-um est mihi, quin faciam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jag har ej fria händer);</text:span> res est mihi in i-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jag har fritt wal),</text:span> C.; alqm in i-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i hans förra ställning)</text:span> restituere, Ter.; C.; de i-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= på nytt)</text:span> gratulari, ordiri; columnam ab i-o novam facere, C.; de i-o urbem (vi et armis conditam) legibus condere parat <text:span text:style-name="T5">Numn</text:span>, L.; res i-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(såsom ej afgjord</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med full beslutande rätt)</text:span> ad patres defertur, L.; tanquam ad i-um bellum omnia parantur, Sa.; magnus ab i-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på nytt)</text:span> seclorum vertitur ordo, Vg.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om lefwande warelser:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i physisk mening:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frisk, sund</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">så wäl ungdomlig, ungdomsfrisk, som </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">outtröttad, uthwilad, ej sårad, oskadd:</text:span></text:span> i-i et incorrupti sensus; i-a valetudo; ex proelio i-um discedere, C.; ætas, Ter., T.; i. a labore; defessis succedunt i-i, Cs.; exercitus, N.; i-um abire, Sa.; corpora; vires; ubi illuxit, Romanus miles i. satiatusque in aciem descendit; i. fuit Horatius, saucii Curiatii, L.; vos, o, quibus i. ævi sanguis, ait, solidoque suo stant robore vires, vos celerate fugam, Vg.; i-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= nyktre, mots.</text:span> uvidi), Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Orörd, obefläckad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om qwinnor):</text:span> ab aliquo puella, Ter.; filia, Pt. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i andlig mening:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till förståndet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sund, orubbad:</text:span></text:span> i-a mens, C.; i. es capitis?, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">moraliskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oförderfwad, ren, obefläckad, oförwitlig, ostrafflig, rättskaffens, ärlig:</text:span></text:span> vita i-rima; homo i. et sanctus; vir bonus et i.; testis i.; servare se i um; labem inferre i-is; i-a existimatio; in civitate nemo i-ior erat, C.; inter artes bonas i-um ingenium brevi adolevit, Sa.; i. vitæ scelerisque purus, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oberörd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt inflytande, utan fördom eller gunst: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fri, opartisk; främmande för, obekant</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span> i. quietusque judex; deos testor, me i-o animo et libero Sullam defendere; discipulus i. et rudis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(färsk),</text:span> C.; i. a conjuratione, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intĕgellus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skadeslös; fläckfri:</text:span></text:span> i-um præstare alqm, C.; castus et i., Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intĕgrasco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förnyas, börja på nytt:</text:span></text:span> malum, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intĕgre</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ostraffligt, ärligt, opartiskt:</text:span></text:span> vita acta i.; in aliqua re versari i.; vivere; judicare, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Riktigt, felfritt:</text:span></text:span> dicere; scribere, Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intĕgrĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kroppslig sundhet, friskhet, helsa:</text:span></text:span> corporis i., valetudo, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">språkets och stilens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Renhet:</text:span></text:span> latini sermonis; sanitas et i. (oratoris, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mots.</text:span> insulsitas et insolentia tanquam insania oratoris), C. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ostrafflighet, sedlig renhet; ärlighet:</text:span></text:span> summa vitæ i. et dignitas; summa innocentia et i.; mulier summa i-e et pudicitia; fides et i.; non fraus, sed i., C.; vitæ ante actæ, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intĕgro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Börja på nytt, förnya:</text:span></text:span> seditionem; pugnam, L.; carmen, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Återställa, hela, bota; uppfriska; wederqwicka:</text:span></text:span> amnes; omnia, Lucr.; animus defessus audiendo i-atur, C.; lacrimas i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(åter framkalla),</text:span> L.; in pravum elapsos artus, si salubris vis adhibeatur, posse i-ri; i-ta amicitia, Fl.; immania vulnera, rector, i-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(upprifwa)</text:span> jubes, St.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intĕgrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förnyelse, uppfriskande:</text:span></text:span> amantium iræ amoris i. est, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕdintĕgro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åter upptaga, börja på nytt, förnya, upprepa:</text:span></text:span> bellum alicui, C. ep.; orationem, verbum, C.; proelium, Cs., L.; clamorem, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Återställa, åter lifwa, wederqwicka, uppfriska:</text:span></text:span> copias deminutas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(åter göra fulltaliga);</text:span> animos, Cs.; pecus pastu, Varr.; iram, C., L.; memoriam, C.; animum legentium r-at varietas rerum, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕdtĕgrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förnyelse, upprepande:</text:span></text:span> ludorum, Varr.; verbi, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Integumentum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Intego, Tego. <text:line-break/>Intellect . . ., Intellig . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lĕgo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>ntĕmĕlii, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Intĕmĕlium, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad och folk i norra Italien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Intemerandus, -ratus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Temere. <text:line-break/>Intemp . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Tempus.<text:line-break/>Intentatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Tento.<text:line-break/>Intent . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se för öfrigt</text:span> Intendo, Tendo.<text:line-break/>Inter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> In.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intĕrāmenta,</text:span> ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Beklädnad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af skepp (i det inre):</text:span> L. XXVIII. 45 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Madv.;</text:span> ἅπαξ λεγ.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>ntĕramna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg.</text:span> inter amnes sc. sita): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i Umbrien.</text:span><text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i Latium.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Intĕramnas, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Interaneus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inter, In.<text:line-break/>Interbito <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Beto.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Intercalar . . ., -calat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Călo. <text:line-break/>Intercapedo, Intercept . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Capio. <text:line-break/>Intercess . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Intercedo, Cedo.<text:line-break/>Inter cĭdo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cado.<text:line-break/>Intercīdo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cædo. <text:line-break/>Intercino, Intercipio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cano, Capio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">I</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">ntercīse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: (cædo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i små</text:span> membra, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> commata: dicere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Intercludo, -clusio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Claudo. <text:line-break/>Intercurs . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Intercurro, Curro. <text:line-break/>Intercus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cutis.<text:line-break/>Interdict . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Interdico, Dīco.<text:line-break/>Interdiu <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Dies.<text:line-break/>Interductus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Duco.<text:line-break/>Interduim, <text:span text:style-name="T2">præs. conj.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> Interdo, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Do.<text:line-break/>Interdum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Dum. <text:line-break/>Interea <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Is.<text:line-break/>Interempt . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Interimo, Emo.<text:line-break/>Interfatio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Interfari, Fari. <text:line-break/>Interfect . . ., -ficio, -fio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Facio. <text:line-break/>Interfringo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frango.<text:line-break/>Intergerium, -gerivus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gero.<text:line-break/>Interibi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ibi, Is. <text:line-break/>Interject . . ., -jicio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Jacio.<text:line-break/>Interim <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Is. <text:line-break/>Interimo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Emo.<text:line-break/>Interior, -ius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inter, In.<text:line-break/>Interitio, -itus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Intereo, Eo. <text:line-break/>Interlocutio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Interloquor, Loquor. <text:line-break/>Interlucatio, -luco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lucus.<text:line-break/>Interlunis, -lunium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Luna.<text:line-break/>Intermenstruus, -mestris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mensis.<text:line-break/>Interminatus, -terminus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Terminus.<text:line-break/>Intermino, -minor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Minor, Minæ.<text:line-break/>Intermissio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Intermitto, Mitto.<text:line-break/>Intermundia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mundus. <text:line-break/>Internas, -terne <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s</text:span>e Inter, In.<text:line-break/>Internecio, -necivus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Neco.<text:line-break/>Internodium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Nodus. <text:line-break/>Internus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inter, In.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Interpello,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> appello, compello):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Falla i talet, afbryta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">alqm,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med ngt,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">alqd</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">göra inkast:</text:span></text:span> nihil te i-bo: continentem orationem audire malo, C.; i-a me, ut sciam, Lucil.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i offentliga förhållanden: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra inkast</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mot ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">protestera</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mot ngns beteende:</text:span> tribuni interregem i-ant, ne fieret senatus consultum, L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wäcka påstående</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mot ngn l. på ngt:</text:span> Jct.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hindra, störa, förhindra:</text:span></text:span> i-ent me, quo minus honoratus sim, modo ne i-ent, quo minus respublica a me administretur, C.; in alicujus jure alqm; victoriam, Cs.; otium bello, Ct.; pransus non avide, quantum i-et inani ventre diem durare, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Interpellātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fallande i talet, afbrytande:</text:span></text:span> cursum orationis i-e impedire, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Påstående</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om ngt:</text:span> Jct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Interpellātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som faller i talet l. stör ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Störare:</text:span></text:span> delectare se sine i-bus; alieni sermonis i., C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som wäcker påstående om ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kärande:</text:span></text:span> Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Interpolis, -polo, -polus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Polio. <text:line-break/>Interposit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Interpono, Pono.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Interpres,</text:span> prĕtis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m. f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: s. medlar, förmedlar öfwerenskommelse l. endrägt mellan twenne parter:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i handling: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Medlare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mäklare), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">underhandlare; ombud, bud:</text:span></text:span> tibi nova et luculenta condicio fertur me i-e; alqd per i-tes et amicos agere; sequestrem aut i-em corrumpendi judicii esse; ad flagitia i-e uti aliquo, C.; pacis, concordiæ i. (Menenius Agrippa), L.; Juno curarum (amoris) i.; Mercurius divûm i., Vg.; avis i. et satelles Jovis, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i fråga om ord och tankar:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tolk:</text:span></text:span> ad Græcam linguam i-e uti aliquo; loqui cum aliquo sine i-e, C.; quotidianis i-bus remotis per C. Valerium cum Divitiaco locutus est, Cs. literæ lectæ per i-em, L.; animi motus effert natura i-e lingua, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwersättare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (skriftlig, likwäl med hänsyftning på muntlig tolkning), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tolkare:</text:span></text:span> sequimur Stoicos non ut i.; i-um fungi munere; i-tes indiserti verbum ex verbo exprimere solent, C.; nec verbum verbo curabis reddere fidus i., Hor. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uttydare, förklarare, uttolkare, (tolk),</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i synn. i fråga om järtecken och gudarnes uppenbarelser:</text:span> nulla ars literis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ur böcker)</text:span> sine i-e percipi potest; grammatici i-tes poētarum; i. juris; ambiguorum et obscurorum; portentorum; somniorum; Sibyllæ; auspiciorum, C. -; veridica i. deorum (Carmenta), L.; Helenus i. divûm, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Interprĕtor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwersätta:</text:span></text:span> Panætium in his libris secutus sum, non i-tus; epistolam totidem fere verbis i-ri; philosophia, si i-ri velis, studium est sapientiæ, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uttyda, tolka, förklara:</text:span></text:span> jus civile populo; monstra; fulgura; reditu in castra liberatum se esse jurejurando i-batur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= tolkade öfwerenskommelsen så, att han påstod),</text:span> C.; obscure dicta, Qu.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tyda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (så l. så) = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fatta, uppfatta, förstå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt med ngt (med</text:span> 2 <text:span text:style-name="T2">accus.</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bedöma, döma:</text:span></text:span> bene dicta male; dicta in mitiorem partem i-ri; perverse disputationem philosophi; virtutem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dygdens begrepp)</text:span> ex consuetudine sermonis nostri i-emur; tardius, id est, ut ego i-or, diligentius; eam sapientiam i-antur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förstå med wishet en sådan l. något sådant),</text:span> qualem nemo consecutus sit; summam ejus felicitatem non satis grato animo i-amur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förstå att skönja på);</text:span> de liberalitate alicujus ita i-ri, ut -, C.; alqd ad voluntatem alicujus; recte an perperam, non i-or, L.; - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">passivt förekommer</text:span> i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i de sammansatta formerna, och isynnerhet i sjelfwa</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pf. part.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwersatt, uttydd:</text:span></text:span> ut ex libris Punicis nobis i-tum est, - quam paucissimis dicam, Sa.; nomen Vestæ; somnium, C. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Interprĕtāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwersättning, förklaring:</text:span></text:span> Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Interprĕtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uttydning, tolkning, förklaring; afgörande:</text:span></text:span> prisci verbi; malitiosa juris; foederis; somniorum; mea i-e ornatius explicari non potest, C.; nec traditur certum nec facilis est i., L.; dura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ordförklaring),</text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Interprimo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Premo.<text:line-break/>Interpunct . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Interpungo, Pungo.<text:line-break/>Interrasilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Interrado, Rado.<text:line-break/>Interritus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Terreo. <text:line-break/>Interrupt . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Interrumpo, Rumpo. <text:line-break/>Interscapilium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Scapula.<text:line-break/>Intersecivus, -sectio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Interseco, Seco.<text:line-break/>Intersero <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> II. Sero.<text:line-break/>Intersitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sino <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äfwen</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">part.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> I. Intersero).<text:line-break/>Interspersus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Spargo.<text:line-break/>Interstitio, -stitium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Intersisto, Sto.<text:line-break/>Intertrigo, -trimentum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Tero. <text:line-break/>Intervenium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vena.<text:line-break/>Intervent . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Intervenio, Venio.<text:line-break/>Intervers . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Interverto, Verto.<text:line-break/>Interula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inter, In. <text:line-break/>Intestabilis, -testat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Testis. <text:line-break/>Intestinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Intus, In.<text:line-break/>Intim . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inter, In.<text:line-break/>Intinctus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Intingo, Tingo. <text:line-break/>Intonsus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Tondeo.<text:line-break/>Intra, -trabilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inter, In.<text:line-break/>Intract . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Tracto, Traho. <text:line-break/>Intrico <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Tricæ.<text:line-break/>Intrigo, -trimentum, -trita <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Intero, Tero.<text:line-break/>Intrinsecus, Intro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(adv. och verb) se</text:span> Inter, In. <text:line-break/>Introductio, -gredior <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Duco, Gradior.<text:line-break/>Introitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Introeo, Eo.<text:line-break/>Introrsum, -trorsus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Verto.<text:line-break/>Introspecto, -spicio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Specio. <text:line-break/>Introvorsus = Introrsus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intŭbus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(inty̆bus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>):<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intŭbum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en wäxt:</text:span> Vg., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intŭbāceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Intus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> In.<text:line-break/>Intusium = Indusium, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Induo.<text:line-break/>Intybus = Intubus.<text:line-break/>Invasor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Invado, Vado.<text:line-break/>Invect . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inveho, Veho.<text:line-break/>Invent . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Invenio, Venio. <text:line-break/>Invers . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inverto, Verto.<text:line-break/>Inveter . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vetus.<text:line-break/>Invicem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vicis.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Invictus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vinco.<text:line-break/>Invid . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Video.<text:line-break/>Invinius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Vinum.<text:line-break/>Invis . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Invideo, Video. <text:line-break/>Invita . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Invito.<text:line-break/>Invite <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Invitus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Invīto,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bjuda, inbjuda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: bjuda till l. ss. gäst; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">emottaga, undfägna, pläga:</text:span></text:span> ad coenam: ad prandium; tecto ac domo; hospitio, C.; domum alqm; i-ti hospitaliter per domos, L.; se vino ciboque, Sa.; alqm; se poculis, Pt.; se largissime, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">anbud, söka förmå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">locka; reta, framkalla:</text:span></text:span> in legationem liberaliter i-or a Cæsare; ad agrum colendum senectus i-at; præmiis ad rem i. alqm; ingenia gloriā i-antur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lockas);</text:span> ad legendum jucunditate (orationis) i-ri; i-at vera ratio bene sanos ad justitiam, C.; ad deditionem hostes; in colloquium alqm, Cs.; spes eum i-at; ad occasionem i-ri, Pn.; - appetitum animi allicere et i., C.; (queruntur in silvis aves) somnos quod i-et leves, Hor.; id vomitiones, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Införa, -leda:</text:span></text:span> mare fossis, Sol.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invītābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lockande:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invītāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lockelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ngt, som lockar), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">retelse:</text:span></text:span> multa habebat i-a urbis et fori; voluptates nulla ad res necessarias i-a afferunt senibus, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invītātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inbjudning, bjudning, uppfordran; lockande:</text:span></text:span> in Epirum i. liberalis; i-es adventusque hominum, C.; vini largior, Gell.; i. quædam ad dolendum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invītātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inbjudare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (bud):</text:span> Cæsaris i., Mt. -<text:line-break/>(<text:span text:style-name="T3">Invītātus</text:span>), <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span> u, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppfordran:</text:span></text:span> i-u tuo, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sŭbinvīto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Halft uppfordra, stöta på:</text:span></text:span> me s-aras, ut ad te scriberem, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Invītus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Owillig, motwillig; nödd och twungen;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ofta att öfwersätta med adv.: ogerna, mot </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sin</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wilja (om det swarar till subjectet); mot ngns wilja (ss.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl. absol.</text:span>): sapiens nihil facit i-us; dilectus i-orum atque a pugnando abhorrentium; i-simus eum a me dimisi; i-us feci, ut eum e senatu moverem, sed libidinem notandam censebam; me i-simo; nihil decet i-ā Minervā, i. e. repugnante natura, C.; fossam ducebat, quo facilius, si se i-o transire conarentur, prohibere posset, Cs.; i-us i-am dimisit, Su.; tu nihil i-ā facies dicesve Minervā; verbaque provisam rem non i-a sequentur, Hor.; aures; oculi; mulier, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Invīte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Motwilligt, nödigt, ogerna:</text:span></text:span> i. cepi Capuam; i-ius ad hoc sermonis genus accessi; i-sime a me discessit, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pĕrinvītus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mycket motwillig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ogerna):</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Invius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Via.<text:line-break/>Inulte, -tus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ulciscor. <text:line-break/>Inunctio, -ungito <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Inungo, Ungo. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Involūcre, -lūcrum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Involvo, Volvo. <text:line-break/>Involŭcris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Volo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭnŭla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ålandsrot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wäxt):</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Inustus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Uro.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>nuus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">herdeguden</text:span> (Faunus).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Io,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Interj.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Huj!, hurra!, bravo!, o!, aj!:</text:span> io, Arethusa!, Ov.; io Bacche; io triumphe, Hor.; uror, io, remove - faces, Tib.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ī</text:span>o, Ius (-onis Pt.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. qwinnonamn. </text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jŏcus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span>: -ci <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> -ca, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skämt, lek:</text:span></text:span> liberalis; lascivus; j-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på skämt)</text:span> dicere alqd; Pt., j-o uti; non ad ludum et j-um facti sumus; facilis est distinctio ingenui et liberalis j-i; j. scurrilis, mimicus; j-a seria miscere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hafwa skämt och allwar gemensamt)</text:span> cum aliquo; j-i causa adhibere alqd; remoto j-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skämt å sido);</text:span> extra j-um, per j-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på skämt)</text:span> dicere alqd, C.; j-a atque seria agere cum aliquo, Sa.; ne j-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på skämt)</text:span> quidem mentiebatur, N.; liberior; turpes historiæ inserere j-os; j-os agitare cum aliqua, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skämtet, löjet personificeradt:</text:span> Venus, quam J. circumvolat et Cupido, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŏcor</text:span>, I.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(joco, Pt.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skämta; säga något på skämt:</text:span></text:span> duplex est j-di genus, unum illiberale, alterum elegans; j-ri cum aliquo; inter se in aliqua re; hæc j-tus sum, C.; in alqd j., Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŏcābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skämtande, förlustande sig:</text:span></text:span> Val.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŏcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skämtande; skämt, infall:</text:span></text:span> nunc venio ad j-es tuas, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŏcōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skämtsam, lustig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om personer och saker); s. sker l. föres o. s. w. på skämt:</text:span> homo, Varr.; res j-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> seriæ), C.; furtum; j-i munera Liberi, Hor.; ludi; verba, Ov.; lis, Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŏcōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skämtsamt, lustigt:</text:span></text:span> eum lusi satis j., C.; j-ius dicere alqd, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŏcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Litet skämt:</text:span></text:span> j-o dicere, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŏcŭlāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Löjlig:</text:span></text:span> audacia, Ter.; j-e istud et a multis sæpe derisum; o licentiam j-em!, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŏcŭlāria</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skämtsamma infall:</text:span></text:span> fundere, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŏcŭlārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: id.: Ter.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŏcŭlor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skämta:</text:span></text:span> L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŏcŭlātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skämtare:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŏcŭlātōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: Diom.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>ōla <text:line-break/>(Iolla), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>ŏlāus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. gr. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>olcus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Thessalien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>ŏlē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. qwinnonamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭon,</text:span> ii, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Viol-blomma:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>on, Iōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>ōnes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Jonerne.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ĭōnĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Jonien (i mindre Asien).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ĭōnĭcus, <text:line-break/>Ĭōnĭăcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ī</text:span>ŏnius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: mare, Vg., Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>ordānes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Palæstina.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭōta,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">indecl.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">vocalen</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">i</text:span>: C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭōtăcismus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förherrskande af</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i uttalet:</text:span> Cap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">J</text:span>ŏviālis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. tillhör Jupiter:</text:span> Mcb. <text:line-break/>Jovis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Juppiter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ī</text:span>phĭănassa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ī</text:span>phĭcrătes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ī</text:span>phĭgĕnīa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ī</text:span>phĭmĕdīa ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ī</text:span>phĭnŏē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ī</text:span>phis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ī</text:span>phĭtus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Ipse <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Is.<text:line-break/>Ir <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hir.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äfwen ofta i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span>): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wrede, harm, förbittring, sinnets uppbrusning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sinne); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">anfall af wrede; lidelse; hämndbegär</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (begär att hämnas l. skada); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">owilja, bitterhet:</text:span></text:span> i. prohibeatur in punibendo; irā aut aliqua perturbatione incitatus; iræ cedere; cum ira nihil recte fieri potest; i. defervescit; ea pars animi, in qua ægritudines, iræ, cupiditates versantur; i. est libido puniendi; (Plato tres finxit animi partes), rationem, iram (θυμός, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">modet),</text:span> cupiditatem, C.; iræ sunt inter eos; iras inter se gerere; iram evomere in alqm, Ter., irā incendi, exacui, N.; mollirent (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">låta sjunka)</text:span> iras!; in nos vertite iras; i. regi mota est; irā inflammari, incendi; irā infensus et periculo conterritus; iras graviter ulcisci; iram sustinere; iræ resederunt; i. plebis in patres; i. prædæ amissæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwer bytets förlust),</text:span> L.; justa; præceps; pervicacior; tenere, supprimere, vincere iram. Ct.; tantæne animis cælestibus iræ!; Aeolus temperat iras ventorum; ereptæ virginis, conjugis i.; subit i. cadentem ulcisci patriam, Vg.; colligit et ponit iram temere; i. furor brevis est; tristes iræ; conferbuit i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(begär),</text:span> Hor.; cadit i. metu, Ov.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> Sen. de Ira); sine ira et studio, quorum causas procul habeo, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Īrācundus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böjd för, snar till wrede; het, hetsig, argsint; wåldsam</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till lynnet, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">häftig:</text:span></text:span> animus, Pt.; senes morosi, i-i, difficiles, C.; Ariovistus, homo i., Cs.; invidus, i., iners, vinosus, amator; tu es i-ior Hadriā, Hor.; i-simus, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Īrācunde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Argt; med hetta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">häftighet:</text:span></text:span> vehementer me agere fateor, i. nego; quo quis est ingeniosior, eo docet i-ius, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Īrācundia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Häftighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i lynnet (ss. habituel egenskap), lätthet att wredgas, </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wåldsamt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> lynne, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hetta:</text:span></text:span> in summis tuis laudibus unam excipiunt i-am; Peripatetici laudant i-am dicuntque eam utiliter esse a natura datam, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utbrott</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">yttring</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ett wåldsamt lynne, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wrede:</text:span></text:span> sic definitur i.: libido ulciscendi; est inimica consilio; i-æ servire, resistere; i-ā moveri; i-am remittere, sedare; i-ā ardere, efferri, inflammari, C.; omittere, reprimere, Ter.; dimittere, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Īrascor</text:span>, sci: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wredgas; blifwa wred, ond, arg, förargad:</text:span></text:span> Peripatetici virum esse negant, qui i-i nesciat; neque vero audiendi, qui graviter i-dum inimicis putabunt, C.; de nihilo; alicui vehementer, Pt.; suis; patriæ, N.; nostram vicem, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Īrascentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: = iracundia a.: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Īrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wred, uppbragt, förbittrad:</text:span></text:span> quo te modo accepissem, nisi i. essem; i-um alqm habere; villico factus erat i-ior; Cæsar fuerat Massiliensibus i-simus; i. alicui de aliqua re, C.; i. tibi, quod - nil dignum sermone canas; mare i-um, Hor.; dis i-is vivere, Juv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Īrāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I wredesmod, i förbittring:</text:span></text:span> dimissus, Phdr.; alqm intueri, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ŏbīrascor</text:span>, sci: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wredgas:</text:span></text:span> fortunæ, Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ŏbīrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förbittrad:</text:span></text:span> fortunæ, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ŏbirātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: C. (l. d.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pĕrīrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mycket uppbragt:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sŭbīrascor</text:span>, sci: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Något wredgas, bli stött:</text:span></text:span> interdum soleo s-i; brevitati literarum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sŭbīrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Något litet ond, stött på:</text:span></text:span> tibi, C.; s-ior, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īris,</text:span> is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Iris</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (regnbågens gudinna l. den personificerade r.); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">regnbåge:</text:span></text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swärdslilja:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Īrĭnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af swärdslilja):</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Irnea <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hirnea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īrōnīa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ironi, spe, gyckel</text:span></text:span> (quum alia dicuntur ac sentias): i-a dissimulantiaque Socratis; bella i., quum jocamur: sin asseveramus, vere dicendum est; germana i., C.; loqui sine i-a, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Irpex,</text:span> ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett åkerbruksredskap (harf, klös?):</text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Irpini <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hirpini.<text:line-break/>Irrasus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Rado. <text:line-break/>Irrepto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Irrepo, Repo.<text:line-break/>Irresectus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Reseco, Seco.<text:line-break/>Irresolubilis, -lutus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Resolvo, Solvo.<text:line-break/>Irretio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Rete. <text:line-break/>Irretortus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Retorqueo, Torqueo.<text:line-break/>Irris . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Irrideo, Rideo.<text:line-break/>Irrĭto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Reor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Irrīto,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr.</text:span> prorito): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Reta;</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppreta:</text:span></text:span> canis i-tus, Pt.; vi fortissimum virum, C.; animi i-ti, L.; taurus i-tior, Gell. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Reta, egga, sporra, drifwa, uppdrifwa; lifligt röra, göra intryck på:</text:span></text:span> cupiditatem et licentiam pueri, C.; vitia vetando; infantiam ad alqd, Qu.; virtutem animi, Lucr.; i-ata ira deorum Terra, Vg.; ad iram i., Ov.; ingenia, Su.; segnius i-ant animos demissa per aures, quam, quæ sunt oculis commissa fidelibus, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Irrītābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sticken, retlig:</text:span></text:span> animus, C.; genus i-e vatum, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Irrītābĭlĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: Ap. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Irrītāmen</text:span>, ĭnis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Irrītāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Medel att reta, egga; retmedel, retelse:</text:span></text:span> i-men animi avari, Ov.; certaminum i-ta, L.; effodiuntur opes, i-ta malorum, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Irrītātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Retande, upphetsande; retelse:</text:span></text:span> animorum, L.; (mulieres) nullis spectaculorum illecebris, nullis conviviorum i-bus corruptæ, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Irrītātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Irritus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Reor.<text:line-break/>Irrumatio, -mator, -mo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ruma.<text:line-break/>Irrupt . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Irrumpo, Rumpo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ī</text:span>rus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en tiggare på Ithaka.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭs,</text:span> ea, ĭd, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Pron. personale</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">determinativum</text:span>: (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat. plur.</text:span> ībus (ĭbus?), Pt., Lucr. VI. 755; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Buecheler, die lateinische Declination): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Han, hon, det; den, det:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">swarande till något föregående:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.; substantivt i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">nom.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl. blott utsatt i motsats till ett annat subject, l. der man, efter att hafwa nämnt och beskrifwit personen, i en följande period öfwergår till att berätta om hans deltagande i den sak, som är i fråga:</text:span> is est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det är han),</text:span> Pt.; Theseus optavit interitum filii, quum is patri suspectus esset de noverca; id gaudeo; ejecit e poculo vinum, ut id (ɔ: poculum) resonaret; justis et fidis hominibus, id est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det will säga),</text:span> bonis viris, ita fides habetur, ut nulla sit de iis fraudis suspicio; eo medicamento sanus factus est; promisisse nollem (se in foro saltaturum), et id arbitror fuisse gravitatis; o rem turpem et ea re miseram, C.; apud Helvetios longe nobilissimus fuit Orgetorix. Is conjurationem nobilitatis fecit; ea res est Helvetiis enuntiata, Cs.; id negotii <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det göromålet);</text:span> eum a deo significari murum dicebat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(att guden menade det med ordet mur);</text:span> relatum legent, quis musicam docuerit Epaminondam, aut in ejus virtutibus commemorari, saltasse eum commode, N.; is locus urbis erit, requies ea certa laborum, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sådan, så mycken:</text:span></text:span> id ætatis homo, id ætatis esse <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(så gammal);</text:span> id temporis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid den tiden),</text:span> C.; non ea vis animo nec tanta superbia victis, Vg.; ad id loci <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> locorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(så långt)</text:span> venire, Sa.<text:line-break/>c. et is, isque, et is quidem, atque is, neque is, sed is = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Och</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">men den</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">det,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tillfogande en ytterligare bestämning till ett ord i samma satssammanhang:</text:span> veste indutus talari, eaque sordida; quod adolescentes, et ii quidem indocti, contemnunt, id docti extimescant!; animus habet primum memoriam, eamque infinitam, rerum innumerabilium; Cratippum audis, idque Athenis; erant in eo <text:soft-page-break/>multæ literæ, neque eæ vulgares; severitatem probo, sed eam modicam, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bestämdt genom ett relativt pronomen l. en conjunction:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Han; den:</text:span></text:span> ejus auditor Strato, is, qui Physicus appellatur; et ii, quibus evenit - ut morerentur, et iis, quibus eventurum est, miseri; ea, quæ vis, ut potero, explicabo; qui mei est studiosus, is est mihi carissimus; eo lugent, quod eos orbatos vitæ commodis arbitrantur; fletus ex eo est, quod eum, quem dileximus, vitæ commodis privatum arbitramur idque sentire; ea est - sapientia boni civis - commoda civium non divellere; ea lege natus es, ut utilitas tua communis sit utilitas; ne id modo consideret quam illa res honesta sit, sed etiam -; id agunt, ut viri boni esse videantur; ea sunt consecuta, ut - mirum sit, accidere illa potuisse, C.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">En sådan; sådan:</text:span></text:span> non sumus ii, quorum vagetur animus errore; non is sum, ut mea me delectent; is sum in illum, quem me esse vis; ea sum ætate, ut -, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Eā</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">abl. sing.</text:span>), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På den wägen; der:</text:span></text:span> ea proxime accedi poterat, C.; ea elephantus ire poterat, qua antea homo vix repere potuerat, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Eātĕnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till den gräns), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Så widt, så långt:</text:span></text:span> verba persequens e., ut ea non abhorreant a more nostro; jus civile e. exercuerunt, quoad populum præstare voluerunt, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Antea</text:span> <text:line-break/>(antĭdea, L.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förut:</text:span></text:span> si a. fuit ignotum, nunc est cognitum; licet videre multos, qui a. fuerint commodis moribus, prosperis rebus immutari; sensim hanc consuetudinem jam a. minuebamus; id numquam a. acciderat, C.; ea elephantus ire poterat, qua a. homo vix repere potuerat, N.; tum Liscus, quod a. tacuerat, proponit; quod a. postulasset, id per se fieri licere -, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intĕreā</text:span>. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Under tiden</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (så länge, till deß); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">emellertid</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om händelser, s. afbryta ett tillstånd):</text:span> i. sol albus recessit ad infera noctis, Enn.; i. loci <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(derunder),</text:span> Pt., Ter.; i., dum hæc coguntur, licet undique carpentem justā repleri juris scientiā; i. misi Sulpicium, qui tela ex ædibus Cethegi efferret, C.; respondit - ad Idus reverterentur. I. - a lacu - ad montem murum fossamque perducit, Cs.; sic requiescunt arva nec nulla i. est inaratæ gratia terræ; i. magno misceri murmure pontum - sensit Neptunus, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Postea</text:span> <text:line-break/>(postĭdea, Pt.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Efter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sedan den tiden</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (deß), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sedan, sedermera:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> eum postidea nunquam vidi, Pt.; clari et antea fuerant et p. fuerunt; multa divinitus deplorata narrabat, ut nihil incidisset civitati p. mali, quod non impendere vidissent; aliquanto p.; brevi p.; nulla antea lex de repetundis fuerat: at p. tot leges, tot rei, tot damnati, ut -; is nobis, antequam Philonem cognovimus, ut philosophus, p. vero, ut vir bonus - probabatur; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">räknadt från det närwarande:</text:span> extremum quum venit, præterita voluptas pro nihilo est, quia p. nulla est futura, C.; bina p., i. e. post Romulum, opima parta sunt spolia; Attius, cui p. Appio Claudio fuit nomen, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Derefter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i rummet eller ordningen; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">dernäst; widare:</text:span></text:span> fertilissima - inoculatio, p. emplastratio, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i frågor:</text:span> quid p.? = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwad mer?;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i wederläggningar) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hwad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">än se’n?, hwad då</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hwad följer wäl deraf)? -:</text:span> cedo quid p.?; quid p., si Romæ assiduus fui?, C.; nemo post reges exactos de plebe consul fuit. Quid p.? Nulla res nova institui debet?, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Posteāquam</text:span> - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Posteaquam</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Conj.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Alltse’n, sedan:</text:span></text:span> p. me totum reip. tradidi, tantum erat philosophiæ locus, quantum -, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prætĕreā</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utomdeß,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ytterligare (i positiva uttr. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">till,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i neg. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mer), deßutom:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> nihilne vobis in mentem venit, quod p. a Crasso requiratis?; duo p. testes; id tibi uni concedam, p. nemini, C.; multi p., quos fama obscura recondit; munera p. Iliacis erepta ruinis ferre jubet, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid öfwergångar i talet l. i uppräkningar: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Deßutom; för öfrigt; widare:</text:span></text:span> p. ajunt, te Cyprum proficisci, Ter.; p. - vati si qua fides - unum illud tibi - proque omnibus unum prædicam, Vg.; in primis operam dabunt, ut juris æquitate suum quisque teneat - et neque - neque -: p., quibuscumque rebus - poterunt, rempublicam augeant; contemni se putant, despici, illudi: p. in fragili corpore omnis odiosa offensio est, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ytterligare = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hädanefter, mera:</text:span></text:span> et quisquam numen Junonis adoret p.?, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Proptĕreā</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Derför, fördenskull:</text:span></text:span> p. hæc ira est; p. quod serviebas liberaliter (manu misi te), Ter.; (mirum videtur) p. quod non sæpe fit; hæc p. de me dixi, ut mihi Tubero - ignosceret, C.; vectigalia coëmpta habebat, p. quod illo licente contra liceri audebat nemo, Cs.; p. quia, C.; p. quoniam, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Eō</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>I. (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dit:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. (i rummet): dit, dertill, deri, derpå o. s. w.:</text:span> repente eo Q. Catulus cum fratre venit, C.; eo concurrere; eo (in equos) - legionarios milites imposuit, Cs.; eo turba omnis - perfugit; laturos eo spolia posteros nuncupavit, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i tiden) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Till deß,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tillsammans med</text:span> usque (u. eo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> eo usque): u. eo premit earum capita, dum captum amittant, C.; eo u. dum, donec, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Derhän, dertill</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i factiska förhållanden):</text:span> eo redeunt fortunæ meæ, Ter.; eo rem adducere; eo accessit, C.; eo magnitudinis procederent, ut - gloriā æterni fierent, Sa.; res Romana eo crevit, ut jam magnitudine laboret sua, L.; eo rem deducere; eo compellere alqm, N.<text:line-break/>II. (<text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span>):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Der, på den punkten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sällsynt):</text:span> eo habebas quinque legiones; eo loci res erat, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Derför</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af den orsak l. i den afsigt); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">derigenom:</text:span></text:span> frater es: eo vereor; mortem suorum eo lugent, quod eos (miseros) putant; non eo dico, quo -; eo pluribus scripsi, ut -, C.; eo dico, ne -, Pt.; eo misi, ut fieret, L.; mercatoribus est aditus magis eo, ut, quibus vendant, <text:soft-page-break/>habeant, quam quo ullam rem ad se importar i desiderent; eo, quod re frumentaria nos intercludi posse confiderent - - nostros lacessere coeperunt, Cs.; sera juvenum venus eoque inexhausta pubertas, T.; - eo (se) deceptum (esse), quod non commissum a se intelligeret, quare timeret, Cs.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid comparativ: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Desto, så mycket</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mera),</text:span> quod <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som),</text:span> quo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ju),</text:span> si <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om):</text:span> eo gravior est dolor, quo culpa major; - eo magis, si ea sunt in adolescente; eo magis, minus -, quod -, C.; eo sibi minus dubitationis dari, quod - eas res memoria teneret, atque eo gravius ferre, quo minus merito populi Romani accidissent, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ădeō</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: (ad-eo; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> adhuc, quoad): <text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Derhän:</text:span></text:span> a. res rediit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(är det kommet),</text:span> Ter.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dittills</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (correlat till ett</text:span> dum, quoad, donec): Pt., Ter.; usque a. in periculo fuit, quoad scitum est, Sestium vivere, C.<text:line-break/>III. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. i </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">den grad, så</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (utmärker alltid en </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hög</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> grad, deruti skiljande sig från</text:span> ita, tam, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwilka ord dock äfwen i nämnda betyd. äro wanligare hos</text:span> Cic.): <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med följande jemförelse-sats:</text:span> adeone hominem esse infelicem, ut ego sum?, Pt<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med följande följdsats:</text:span> adeone hospes es hujus urbis, ut hæc nescias?, C.; a. non <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> nihil, ut - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(så litet, så långt ifrån, att -),</text:span> L. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utan correlatsats:</text:span> <text:line-break/>α. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.</text:span> a. erat summa observatio in bello movendo, C.; a. atroces coorti sunt, L.; non obtusa a. gestamus pectora Poeni, Vg.; cetera de genere hoc - a. sunt multa - loquacem delassare valent -, Hor.<text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stundom i reflexioner blott uttryckande en bekräftelse (så sannt, wißt är det): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Alltså:</text:span></text:span> a. - quanto minus rerum, tanto minus cupiditatis, L. præf.<text:line-break/>γ. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i asyndetiska jemförelser: till den grad = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Så mycket mer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mindre</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (säkrare):</text:span> æqualium quoque, a. superiorum intolerans; ne quieto quidem milite regimen: a. furentes infirmitate retinentis ultro accendebantur, T.<text:line-break/>IV. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med förlorad demonstrativ-betydelse öfwergången till en förstärkande l. determinerande partikel:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Till och med:</text:span></text:span> intra moenia atque a. in senatu versatur; magna atque a. maxima, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bekräftande, synon. med</text:span> vero <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gr.</text:span> περ), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ofta tjenande till att företrädeswis framhålla det ord, wanl. ett pronomen, hwarwid (wanl. efter hwilket) det sättes; öfwersättes i sw. med: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Också, ja, just,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> men oftast blott genom förstärkt tonwigt på nämnda ord:</text:span> nihil est mendaciloquum magis neque a. argutius; neque a. hasce emi mihi neque usuræ meæ, Pt. nulla civitas fuit non suspecta nobis. Id a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(också)</text:span> haud scio, mirandumne sit, Cs.; teque a. decus hoc ævi te consule inibit -; tuque a. (Auguste, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">efter anropande af gudarne),</text:span> Vg.; magis a. id facilitate, quam ulla alia mea culpa contigit, C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stundom i imperativsatser i sammanhang med pronomina l. adverbia:</text:span> Vg. IX. 156.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭdeo</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Derför; fördenskull:</text:span></text:span> hoc i. fit, quia -, Pt.; i. ille summum bonum εὐθυμίαν appellat; quod multos dies epistolam tuam in manibus habui, i. multa in eam conjecta sunt; i. disputabo - ut doceam; i. contra mulieres scripsit, ne edictum ad Chelidonis <text:soft-page-break/>arbitrium scriptum videretur, C.; i-que eum amicum sibi adjungi cupiebat, N.; non quin <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för det att l. som om icke)</text:span> breviter responsum reddi potuerit, i. delectos - ad eum missos esse, L.; fenus agitare - ignotum i-que magis servatur, quam si vetitum esset, T.; non i. (mater) eum bis Grajûm armis vindicat, Vg.; ne me i. foliis brevioribus ornes, quod -, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭbī</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">locativ</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> is; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> tibi): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Der, derstädes:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> i. postis est, ubi templi aditus, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Då:</text:span></text:span> i. infit Albanus, L.; i. ille cuculus: o ocelle mi, fiat, Pt.; ubi videt, me tam facile victum quærere, i. coepit me obsecrare, Ter. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Derutinnan, derwid:</text:span></text:span> i. (in bellis intestinis) juventutem suam exercuit, Sa.; i. nos paratos inveniet, C.; numquid ego i. peccavi?, Pt.; i. sum (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">derpå tänker jag),</text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭnĭbi</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Derstädes</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> superbia nata i. (Capuæ) videtur, C.<text:line-break/>b. i. est res = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">är i görningen, nära fullbordad:</text:span> sperare debemus, id aut i. esse aut jam esse confectum, C.; = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nästan:</text:span> mors eum i. occupavit, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intĕrĭbi</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Under tiden:</text:span></text:span> vos ite intro; ego i. ex hoc erogitabo -, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Postĭbi</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sedan, derefter:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Idcirco</text:span> <text:line-break/>(iccirco; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> id <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> circus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen skrifwet ss. twå ord),</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Derför,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för det), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fördenskull</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (utan correlat l. swarande till ett</text:span> quod, quia, si, ut, ne): si triumphi prærogativam putas supplicationem et i. casum potius, quam te, laudari mavis, non semper triumphus sequitur supplicationem, C. ep.; vos Pontii vires non habetis: num i. est ille præstantior?; non i. eorum usum dimiseram, quod iis succenserem; quia natura mutari non potest, i. veræ amicitiæ sempiternæ sunt; non si Opimium defendisti, i. te bonum civem putabunt, C.; hæc i. - scripsi, ut existimes me pro te laborare, C. ep.; se i. ad eum venire noluisse, quo facilius civitatem in officio contineret, Cs.; non i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för det)</text:span> flammæ vires posuere, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intĕrim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> inter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> im = eum, id):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Under tiden, emellertid, till deß; här-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">derunder:</text:span></text:span> i. dum de condicionibus inter se agunt, interficitur Sabinus; quoad ipse aberat, naves i. ædificari jussit, Cs.; patrum i. animos certamen regni versabat; Roma i. crescit Albæ ruinis, L.; serviendum esse feminæ et insuper duobus adolescentibus, qui rempublicam i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tills widare,</text:span> vivo Tiberio) premant, quandoque distrahant; i. Messalina Lucullianis in hortis prolatare vitam; vicesimo anno Nero consulatum iniret atque i. extra urbem proconsulare imperium haberet, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Emellertid,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> inledande en berättelse om något owäntadt l. plötsligt, som afbryter ett tillstånd:</text:span> Ligarius nullo se implicari negotio passus est. I. P. Varius Uticam venit; Piso maris oras petivit, quum i. milites ejus domum obsidere coeperunt, C.; i. accidit illa calamitas apud Leuctra Lacedæmoniis, N.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Emellertid,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i oberoende sats l. i bisats med</text:span> quum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">närmande sig </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till adversativ betydelse (dock, likwäl):</text:span> post Leuctricam pugnam Lacedæmonii se nunquam refecerunt, quum i. Agesilaus non destitit patriam juvare, N.; quod alias vitiosum, i. alias rectum est; fortior vocatur, qui armorum inscius in pugnam ruit, q. i. frequenter suis viribus ipse prosternitur, Qu.<text:line-break/>4. = interdum: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Emellanåt, stundom, understundom:</text:span></text:span> id i. fit, quia fastidiunt, i. quia omnino non possunt, Qu.; Sen., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Īdem</text:span>, eădem, ĭdem, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Pron. determinativum</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Den samme; samme:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absolut, utan correlat:</text:span> hæc duarum hodie in vicem et hic et illic mulier feret imaginem et eadem erit, verum alia esse adsimulabitur, Pt.; non i. semper dicere, sed i. spectare debemus; non i. expedit; non i. sentio; eodem modo de Demosthene judico; hic i.; i. iste Mithridates; ejusdem illius inimici contio, C.; i. illud intervallum, Cs.; i. ille populus, N.; non semper i. floribus est honos vernis; sol aliusque et i. nascitur, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">motswaradt af</text:span> qui, atque, quasi; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mera sällan af</text:span> ut, et, cum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. af</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>: animus erga te i. est, ac fuit, Ter.; causas subesse oportet easdem, quas dixi justas causas esse bellorum; i. id valere oportet, ac si prætor indicaret; sensu amisso fit i., quasi non natus esset omnino; disputationem exponemus iisdem verbis, ut actum disputatumque est; negas ejusdem esse severitatis Catilinam expulisse et Murenam defendere; non est i. ferre, si quid ferendum est, et probare, si quid non probandum est; erant nobis perirati, quod non i. illis censuissemus, C.; Gallorum eadem oppugnatio est ac Belgarum; eodem tempore mandata referebantur et legati veniebant, Cs.; eodem mecum patre genitus, T.; invitum qui servat, idem facit occidenti, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillsammans med</text:span> unus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> par = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">En och den samme:</text:span></text:span> nihil potest esse diutius uno eodemque statu; versare multis modis unam et eandem rem; unus idemque animus; exitus omnium unus atque i. fuit, C.; par atque idem periculum, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jemte ett annat nomen ss. attribut l. appositum l. prædicat tillagdt eller utsagdt om ett förut nämndt substantiv; i sw. att öfwersätta med: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Också; på samma gång; derjemte; tillika; jemwäl; deremot:</text:span></text:span> beneficentia, quam eandem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(också)</text:span> benignitatem appellari licet; tantum ego in excellente oratore et eodem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på samma gång)</text:span> bono viro pono esse ornamentum civitati; animus acer et acutus idem; nemini video Græcorum contigisse, ut i. in utroque genere elaboraret; callidos homines - eosdem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillika)</text:span> viros bonos esse volumus; quod (jus) gentium est, i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(också)</text:span> civile esse debet; inventi sunt multi, qui - vitam pro patria profundere parati essent, iidem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(men på samma gång)</text:span> gloriæ jacturam ne minimam quidem facere vellent; Alcidamas rhetor i-que philosophus, C.; satrapes i-que regis gener, N.; informes hiemes reducit Jupiter, i. summovet; rebus angustis animosus - appare: sapienter i. contrahes vento nimium secundo turgida vela; quum res deficiunt, satis inter vilia fortis: verum ubi quid melius contingit, et unctius i. vos sapere et solos aio bene vivere, quorum conspicitur nitidis fundata pecunia villis, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Eādem</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">abl. sing.</text:span>), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På samme wäg:</text:span></text:span> e., qua ceteri, fugere noluit, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Eōdem</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ditsammastädes; till samma ställe, åt samma håll, dit äfwen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ock:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> e. sua conferunt; e. omnes clientes Orgetorix conduxit, Cs.; e. perfugere, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> addendum e. est, ut ne criminibus inferendis delectetur amicus, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tills. med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">gen. part.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> locus: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På samma ställe</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">punkt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i eg. och oeg. bet.:</text:span> res e. loci est, quo reliquisti, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭbīdem</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På samma ort</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ställe, dersammastädes:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> i. in Sicilia, C.; navem ter fluctus i. torquet agens circum -, Vg.; quid? quod - dedisti? - i. una traho <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det räknar jag in i samma summa),</text:span> Pt. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i och med detsamma:</text:span> læsit in eo (quod homines coēgit et armavit), Cæcinam sublevavit i., C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i samma ögonblick:</text:span> C. de Fin. I. 6.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭdentĭdem</text:span> (idem et idem), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ideligen, alltjemnt, flere gånger, esomoftast:</text:span></text:span> referebam oculos ad terram i., C.; hostes i. ad suos in silvas (se receperunt), Cs.; explorare; quærere, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ipsus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(arch.,</text:span> Liv., Enn., Acc., Pt., Ter.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ipse</text:span>, ipsa, ipsum, (<text:span text:style-name="T2">gen.</text:span> ipsīus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poet.</text:span> ipsĭus), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Pron. determinativum</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> is, pe, sus = is; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Corssen, Aussprache</text:span> II. 83; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i formen</text:span> sapsa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äro båda pronomina böjda, i formen</text:span> eapse <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blott det förra): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sjelf:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. absolut l. i mots. till ett annat hufwudord: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Han,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hon o. s. w. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sjelf;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett pronomen personale sättes i denna betydelse </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">icke</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till</text:span> ipse; <text:span text:style-name="T2">gen.</text:span> ipsius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwersättes med </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">egen:</text:span></text:span> res i-a indicat; i-e solvi, Ter.; non ego possum, quæ i-a sese venditat, tutarier, Pt.; ut i. cum Græcis Latina conjunxi, sic tibi censeo esse faciendum; in astrologia C. Sulpicium audimus (operam ponere), in geometria Pompejum i-i vidimus; societas hominum inter i-os <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sinsemellan);</text:span> Ennius Bruges, non Phryges dicebat: i-ius declarant libri; mihi volo ignosci, ceteris i. non ignosco; non solum i-a fortuna caeca est, sed cæcos eos efficit, quos complexa est, C.; i-orum linguā Celtæ, nostra Galli appellantur; Labienum munitioni præfecit: i. in Italiam contendit, Cs.; i. seram vites, Tib.; Phyllida mitte mihi, meus est natalis, Iolla: quum faciam vitulo pro frugibus, i-e venito; navim i-ius ante oculos fluctus subvertit, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">prægnant om husbonden l. om hufwudmannen för en skola:</text:span> Pt.; ipse dixit (Pythagoras), C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillsammans med reflexivum:</text:span> sum mihi i. testis, Ter.; hoc in me i-e sæpe experior; non egeo medicina: me i-e consolor; sibi i. consentit; nati sunt homines, ut i-i inter se <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwarandra inbördes)</text:span> aliis alii prodesse possent; eget nullo omniaque sua in se i-o posita putat; amicitia orta est, ut, quod quisque minus per se i-e posset, id acciperet ab alio, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bisats af</text:span> oratio obliqua <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">framhållande den person l. sak, som är den styrande satsens subject, i mots. till andra saker l. personer: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Han, hon, de</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (betonadt):</text:span> (monebant Helvetii), ne Cæsar aut suæ virtuti magnopere confideret aut i-os despiceret, Cs.; virtus facit, ut eos diligamus, in quibus i-a inesse videatur, C.; si i. populo Romano nihil præscriberet, non oportere sese a pop. Rom. in suo jure <text:soft-page-break/>impediri, Cs.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="T2">et ipse</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Äfwen han,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> der om ett nytt subject samma prædicat utsäges som om ett föregående:</text:span> Crassus tres et i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(liksom motparten)</text:span> excitavit recitatores, C.<text:line-break/>6. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Af sig sjelf; för sig sjelf:</text:span></text:span> ova parire solet genus pinnis condecoratum, non animas: post inde divinitus insinuatur i-a anima, Enn.; valvæ se i-æ aperuerunt; e manibus civium delapsa arma i-a ceciderunt, C.; his actis aliud genitor secum i. volutat, Vg.; satis est orare Jovem, qui donat et aufert, det vitam, det opes, æquum mi animum i-e parabo, Hor. <text:line-break/>7. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med starkare betoning: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sjelfwe</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (utmärkande fullkomlig identitet l. det nomen l. pron., till hwilket det fogas, ss. ngt större l. mera owäntadt); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">just; äfwen, till och med, redan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (blott):</text:span> in i-is nuptiis, Ter.; postulatione i-a profitentur, omnia se amici causa esse facturos; magnitudo animi in his i-is despiciendis elucet; moriendum est, et id incertum, an eo i-o die; non loquor de vulgari amicitia, quæ tamen et i-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äfwen den, redan den)</text:span> et delectat et prodest; hoc i-um volo; decem i-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(just</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">præcist)</text:span> dies, C.; sub i-o vallo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(just</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tätt inunder);</text:span> i-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blott)</text:span> terrore vincere alqm, Cs.; vestibulum ante i-um; Antandro sub i-a, Vg.; terror e i-o bellum profligare, T.<text:line-break/>8. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Superl.</text:span> ipsissimus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skämtsam bildning) = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sjelfwaste</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (han), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">just densamme:</text:span></text:span> Pt. Trin.<text:line-break/>9. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i uppräknande af saker i ordningsföljd efter rum, rang o. s. w.</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åter:</text:span></text:span> ex tribus illis reip. generibus longe præstat regium: regio autem i-i præstabit id, quod ex tribus permixtum erit, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Istĕ</text:span>, ista, istud <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hos</text:span> Pt., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med bortkastadt</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">i,</text:span> <text:line-break/>ste <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o. s. w.),</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Pron. demonstrativum</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Den der:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl. om ngt, s. tillhör den person, med hwilken man talar (dig l. eder), ngt s. af denne säges o. s. w.:</text:span> non tu i-am (tuam) linguam prætruncari jubes?, Pt.; sunt i-a, Læli <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det s. du säger);</text:span> i-ud tuum scelus; quum i-a sis auctoritate, Cato, non ita loqui debes; i-a omnia (quæ vos requiritis) semper contempsi; i-am culpam, quam vereris, ego præstabo, C.; animi est i-a mollitia, non virtus, Cs.; exue i-am mentem; iste deus qui sit, da, Tityre, nobis, Vg. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. demonstrativt, wanl. med föraktlig l. hatfull bibet., derför om motpart inför domstol:</text:span> i-a (tyrannorum) in figura hominis feritas - beluæ; illi multo mihi hoc facilius remisissent, si i-um (Cæcilium) non nossent aut si i. apud eos quæstor non fuisset; quæstores utriusque provinciæ, qui i-o (Verre) prætore fuerunt, - vehementer i-ius cupidi, ex i-ius cibariis liberaliter tractati, C.; potuit duci coena sine i-is (deliciis), Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos sednare förf.</text:span> = hic: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Istīc</text:span> (iste - ce; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos</text:span> Pt. <text:line-break/>stic; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> illic, hic), istæc, istuc <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> istoc, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Pron. demonstr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Den der</text:span></text:span> (= iste, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blott mera lifligt påpekande):</text:span> quid istuc est, Philocomasium?; vide, sitne istæc vostra intus!; istæc ætas (tua); istoc exemplo, Pt.; est istuc quidem alqd, sed nequaquam sunt in isto omnia; Chrysippus idem istuc dicit, quod est dictum a te, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Istā</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Istāc</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På den der wägen:</text:span></text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Istactĕnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Allt dittills; så långt:</text:span></text:span> i. tibi libertas data est orationis: - tace, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Istī</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Istīc</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Der,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wanl. = hos dig l. eder):</text:span> crepundia i-i in ista cistula insunt, Pt.; jam i-c adero, Ter.; nempe tu i-c ais esse erilem concubinam; mane i-c, Pt.; i-c <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(der du och Cæsar äro)</text:span> est res publica, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Istim</text:span> (Pt.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Istinc</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Derifrån; deraf:</text:span></text:span> i. se subterducere, Pt.; libenter i. tanquam a domino furioso profugi, C.; par tem posco mihi i., de istoc vidulo, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Istō</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Istoc</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Istuc</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dit; deri:</text:span></text:span> do fidem, me i-o ituram, quo jubes, Pt.; i. se admiscere, mittere; i-oc intromittere, Pt., venire, C.; i-uc venire, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Istorsus</text:span>, (= isto vorsus), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ditåt:</text:span></text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ī</text:span>sæus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īsăgōgē,</text:span> es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inledning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till en wetenskap; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">läro-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">handbok:</text:span></text:span> pueriles, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Īsăgōgĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: id.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>săra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Gallien (Isêre).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭsătis,</text:span> is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wejde:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>sauri, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk i mindre Asien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ĭsaurus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ĭsaurĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>schia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö wid södra Italiens kust.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ischĭas,</text:span> ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Höftwärk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">-sjuka:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ischĭăcus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ischĭădĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Höftsjuk:</text:span></text:span> Cato, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īsĕlastĭcus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: i-i ludi = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kappkörningsspel, kappränningar:</text:span></text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ī</text:span>sĭdōrus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ī</text:span>sis, is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> Īsĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Isis, ægyptisk gudinna.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Īsĭăcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>smărus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: pl. -a, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Thracien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ismărĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>smēnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod wid Thebæ.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ismēnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">thebansk.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ismēnis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Thebanska.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ī</text:span>sŏcrătes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Īsŏcrătēus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Īsŏdŏmos,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: genus (structuræ), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af likformiga stenar,</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Īsŏpleurus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liksidig:</text:span></text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Īsoscĕlĕs</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Likbent triangel:</text:span></text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>ssa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö i Adriatiska hafwet.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Issæus, <text:line-break/>Issaĭcus, <text:line-break/>Issensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>ssus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Cilicien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Istā, Istac, Iste <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Is.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>ster, tri, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Donau, enkannerligen deß nedre del.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Istrĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>stri, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Istrĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk och land wid Adriatiska hafwet.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Isthmus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Näs,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt det corinthiska:</text:span> C., L. <text:line-break/>Isthmĭăcus, <text:line-break/>Isthmĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Isthmĭa, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">isthmiska spelen:</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Isti <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(adv.),</text:span> Istic <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(pron. och adv.),</text:span> Istim, Istinc, Isto, Istoc, Istorsus, Istuc <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Iste, Is.<text:line-break/>Istiusmodi (istius modi) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Modus. <text:line-break/>Istria, Istri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ister.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭtă,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af roten i</text:span> is? <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">correlat till</text:span> ut, quasi, si <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">m. m.):</text:span><text:line-break/>I. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på det sättet:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> i. est locutus, Ter.; sit i. sane; istud quidem i. necesse est; i. credo; hæc i. teneantur, ut constitutum sit; in herba se abjecit atque i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i sådan ställning)</text:span> locutus est; decorum ad omnem honestatem pertinet, atque i. pertinet, ut non recondita quadam ratione cernatur, sed sit in promptu; id si i. est, ut animus in morte evolet ex custodia corporis, quis me felicior?, C.; Romanis nuntia, cælestes ita velle, ut Roma mea caput rerum sit: proinde sciant et i. posteris tradant, nullas opes Romanis resistere posse, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">swarande till något föregående: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sålunda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (så som wisats eller bewisats); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">alltså; under sådana förhållanden; då</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> itaque), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">derför:</text:span></text:span> i., quam ille duplicem putavit esse rationem, in V partes distribui oportere reperitur; dixit Scævola, te de eloquentia tanquam in schola disputasse. I. me frater exoravit ut huc secum venirem, C.; i. utrumque per se indiget alterius auxilio, Sa.; i. sine periculo tantam multitudinem interfecerunt, Cs.; nemo alteri concedere animum inducebat. I. rem inter se consociant, L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i jemförelser swarande till ett</text:span> ut <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bisats:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i jemförelser med afs. på werklighet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Så, så wißt:</text:span></text:span> ut Germanos in Gallia versari noluerant, i. Romanos inveterascere in Gallia moleste ferebant, Cs. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I den mon; i den ordning:</text:span></text:span> ut <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ju)</text:span> quisque est optimus, i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(desto)</text:span> difficillime alios esse improbos suspicatur, C.<text:line-break/>4. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I sådan afsigt, till sådan bestämmelse:</text:span></text:span> non i. nati sumus, ut ad ludum et jocum facti esse videamur, C.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">under det wilkor; i det fall, med den inskränkning; då, </text:span></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blott då</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">så,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wisserligen, men -):</text:span> hoc ipsum, quod recte fit, i. est justum, si est voluntarium; crebris nos literis appellato, atque i., si idem fiet a nobis; i. senectus honesta est, si - nemini mancipata est; equidem i. sum cupidus in illa longiore te - disputatione audiendi, ut - quotidiano tuo sermone sim contentus, C.; pax i. convenerat, ut - Tiberis finis esset; i. gratiam ineunt, ut non - plus darent juris, quam retinerent, L.; i. conveniet - vertere seria ludo, ne deus - migret in obscuras tabernas, Hor.<text:line-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i frågor och swar:</text:span> Pt., Ter.; casu, inquis. Itane vero? <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(werkligen?);</text:span> non dicis igitur: miser est M. Crassus, sed tantum miser M. Crassus. - I. plane <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(alldeles! ja wißt!),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Så</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">till den grad:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> non sum i. hebes, ut istud dicam; hæc i. sunt in promptu, ut res disputatione non egeat; i. celeriter pueri res innumerabiles arripiunt, ut non - accipere videantur, sed reminisci; enumerare longum est: i. sunt multi; i. multi sunt imbecilli senes ut nullum - vitæ munus exsequi possint; i. non <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(så litet)</text:span> superstitiosus, ut - sacrificia et fana contemneret; i. non timidus ad mortem, ut - - in acie sit interfectus, C.; acriter, Cs.; legationem - adversus gentem Achæorum i. de ipsis meritam, L.<text:line-break/>2. non i., haud i. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Icke just, icke synnerligen, icke serdeles:</text:span></text:span> non i. multo post; non i. diu, C.; haud i. magnus; non i. multi, N.; non i. magnus suorum numerus, C.; hoc erat in votis, modus agri non i. magnus, Hor. <text:line-break/>III. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Så wißt, så sannt, lika wißt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i önskningar:</text:span> i. me Venus amet; i. me amabit Sancta Saturitas, Pt.; i. vivam, ut id facio; i. me dii juvent, C.; equidem de te nil tale verebar - i. me tibi referat ovantem Jupiter, Vg.<text:line-break/>IV. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos de archaistiske förff. i satser, som utmärka grunden till det, som säges i den föregående satsen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ty:</text:span></text:span> immortales mortales flere si foret fas, flerent divæ Camenæ Nævium poētam. Ita postquam ille est Orcino traditus thesauro, obliti sunt Romæ loqui latina lingua, ap. Gell.; timeo, quid rerum gesserim: ita dorsus totus prurit, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭtăque</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.</text:span> = (ita <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> que =) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Och så:</text:span></text:span> ita volo itaque postulo, Ter.; - i. loquuntur, C.; i. fecerunt, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Derför ock; derför, på grund</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">i följd deraf, fördenskull:</text:span></text:span> antiquitas - melius ea, quæ erant vera, cernebat. I. unum illud erat insitum priscis illis, esse in morte sensum; i. (Plato) philosophos ad rempublicam ne accessuros quidem putat, nisi coactos; est i. id genus situm in commutatione verborum, C.; Dumnorix - civitates suo beneficio obstrictas habere volebat. I. rem suscipit, Cs.; decorum erat tum ipsis capessere pugnam ducibus. Avide i. se certamini offert, L.; i. eo profectus est, quo - -, N.; i. urgeret coepta, T.; nunc i. et versus et cetera ludicra pono, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭtem</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Likaså; så:</text:span></text:span> fecisti i., ut solent, C.; i. nos sumus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i samma ställning),</text:span> Pt.; indignatur i. - privatis versibus exponi coena Thyestæ, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Likaledes, jemwäl, också:</text:span></text:span> hoc i. Scipioni videbatur; quærunt ex me, credo i. ex te, Scævola; non solum corporis, qui ad naturam apti <text:soft-page-break/>sunt, sed multo etiam magis animi motus probandi, qui i. ad naturam accommodati sunt; a patre, ab amicis i.; hoc in Libero servant, in Libera non i., C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om motsatta ting:</text:span> sunt alii - simplices et aperti, fraudis inimici - i-que alii, qui quidvis perpetiantur, dum id, quod velint, consequantur, C.; i. Allobroges ad Cæsarem se recipiunt, Cs.; contemplator i., quum nux - induet se in florem, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ännu</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (en, en gång):</text:span> demo unum, d. et item unum, Hor.; semel - item, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭtĭdem</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Likaså; så; likaledes:</text:span></text:span> i. tibi dolet, ut mihi, Ter.; deorum liberos non i. (ex sexu nominant), Varr.; nunc i. ab eodem capienda primordia, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ī</text:span>tălus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>tălus, pl. -li, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Italier:</text:span></text:span> saxa vocant Ĭtali, Vg.; Ītala per Grajos orgia ferre choros, Ppt. <text:line-break/>Ītălus (fere poēt.) <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">italisk.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ītălia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Italien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ītălĭcus, <text:line-break/>Ītălius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Ītălis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A. f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(poet.).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ītălĭca, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Hispanien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ītălĭcensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Iter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Eo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭtĕrum,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">För andre gången; ännu en gång; ånyo:</text:span></text:span> i. decipi stulti est; i. consul, C.; Cæsar i. ad Ariovistum legatos mittit; si i. experiri velint, se i. paratum esse decertare, Cs.; colonia, suppleto numero colonorum, i. deducta est, L.; primo, i., tertio; semel atque i., i. et sæpius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(flere gånger),</text:span> C.; i. atque i., i. i-mque (id.), Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭtĕro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: göra andre gången l. om igen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upprepa, förnya; åter göra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till föremål för en handling):</text:span> pugnam, L.; cursum; voces; æquor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(åter befara),</text:span> Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i ord </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upprepa:</text:span></text:span> i-a eadem ista mihi, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Plöja om:</text:span></text:span> opus est agro non semel arato, sed novato et i-to, C.; collem i-re, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭtĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upprepande; omplöjande:</text:span></text:span> verborum, C.; agri, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭtĕrāto</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ännu en gång, upprepade gånger:</text:span></text:span> Js.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>thăca, ae <text:line-break/>(Ĭthăcē, es), <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö i Ioniska hafwet.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ĭthăcensis, <text:line-break/>Ĭthăcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>thy̆phallus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> = Priapus: Col. <text:line-break/>Ĭthy̆phallĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: metrum (—⏑—⏑—⏑), Gramm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Itidem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ita.<text:line-break/>Itinerarius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> Iter), Itio, Itito <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Eo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>tius portus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i Gallien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Ito <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Eo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>tōnē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>tōnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Boeotien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ĭtōnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>tūræus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> -æi, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslagsnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Itus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Eo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ĭ</text:span>tys, y̆os, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Jŭba,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Man:</text:span></text:span> equorum, C.; equina, Ov.; leonis, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om hjelmbusken:</text:span> Vg.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om halsfjäder på fåglar:</text:span> Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭbātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">försedd med man:</text:span> fera; leo, Sen.; stella <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(comet),</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">J</text:span>ŭba, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">numidiskt personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jŭbar,</text:span> ăris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">strålande </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ljus, strålglans:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. och eg.:</text:span> tremulum in æde j. spargere, Ov.; galeæ, St.<text:line-break/>2.<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. om solens l. stjernornas </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ljus:</text:span></text:span> j-e exorto, Vg.; Lucifer j. extulit undis, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> Cæsar fundit ab ore j., Mt.; regale, Cd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Jubatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Juba.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jŭbeo,</text:span> jussi, jussum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bjuda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i strängare mening:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. (construeradt wanl. med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">inf. præs.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(aldrig</text:span> fut.) <text:span text:style-name="T2">act.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och en</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. subj. dertill, sällan med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">inf. act.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och blott en objects</text:span>-<text:span text:style-name="T2">acc.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">någon gång med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">ut</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">conj.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. blott</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">conj.</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">undantagswis med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">dat. pers.</text:span>): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bjuda, tillsäga, befalla, låta:</text:span></text:span> lex j-et recte facere; rem integram ad suum reditum j-sit esse; j-bis igitur te suscitari?, C.; eos adventum suum exspectare j-sit; in summo jugo duas legiones - et omnia auxilia collocari ac totum montem hominibus compleri j-sit; quod j-si sunt, faciunt, Cs.; jubesne me foedus ferire?; de se deos consuli jussit; signa ferri j-sit; quo j-si erant, conveniunt, L.; Hesiodus j-et majore mensura reddere id, quod acceperis, C.; et pater Anchises fatis dare vela j-bat, Vg.; jube maneat, Ter.; militibus suis j-sit, ne qui eorum violarentur, Cs. (inc. l.); j-sit, ut naves Euboeam peterent, L.; Britannico j-sit, exsurgeret; Drusus j-sit tributum, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om folket ss. subject: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förordna, besluta, stadga,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. lag) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">antaga; wälja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (embetsmän): (med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">ut</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">conj.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">inf.</text:span>): quæ populus j-sit aut plebs scivit; leges j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(antaga)</text:span> aut vetare; pop. Rom. j-sit, ut statuas Verris quæstores demoliendas curarent, C.; populus rogationem j-sit; j-sit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillade)</text:span> Mario provinciam Numidiam populus, Sa.; (plebs) id modo scivit jussitque, ut senatus decerneret, qui Romæ regnaret; - inde Tullum Hostilium - regem populus j-sit, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i mildare mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bjuda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bedja, råda, uppmana;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i helsningar: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bjuda, bedja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">önska):</text:span></text:span> ponere j-bam, de quo quis audire vellet: ad id aut sedens aut ambulans disputabam; sperare nos amici j-ent, suadent, hortantur; Cæsar te sine cura esse j-et, C.; Tanaquil excelsa et alta sperare - virum j-et; populum j-bat bono animo esse, L.; Dionysium salvere jube; illum j-si valere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bjöd honom farwäl),</text:span> C.; <text:soft-page-break/>ire (Fabios) fortes, ire felices j-ent inceptisque eventus pares reddere, L.; urbis amatorem Fuscum salvere j-emus, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jussum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: (<text:span text:style-name="T2">part.</text:span>): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Befallning, bud:</text:span></text:span> putasne, id j. (populi) firmum ac ratum futurum?; j-a deorum immortalium; j-a ac vetita populorum, C.; mihi j-a capessere fas est; exsequi j-a, Vg.; peragere, rescindere, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jussu</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af obr.</text:span> jussus, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>): alicujus, meo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o. s. w.: på ngns, min o. s. w. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Befallning, bud:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injussus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ej ombedd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">befalld:</text:span></text:span> i-i non desistunt unquam (cantare), Hor.; hæc veniunt i-a, Sen.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ej ålagd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">föreskrifwen:</text:span></text:span> non i-a cano, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injussu</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> jussu) alicujus: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utan befallning af ngn:</text:span> vetat Pythagoras i-u imperatoris, id est dei, e statione abire; i-u suo, C.; i-u consulis pugnare, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jūbĭlum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hojtande, muntert rop:</text:span></text:span> (rusticorum, pastorum), Sil.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūbĭlo</text:span>, 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hojta, skrika:</text:span></text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūbĭlātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Jucund . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Juvo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">J</text:span>ūdæus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Iude.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Jūdæus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Jūdăĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">judisk.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Jūdæa, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Iudéen.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jūdex</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> jus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> dico, Varr), ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Domare:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg., juridisk men. (= bisittare l. medlem af rätten l. nämnden, ej = domhafwanden,</text:span> quæsitor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> qui præest judicio): hunc quæsitorem et j-em omnes metuebant; sedere j-em in alqm; apud j-es res agitur; j. pronuntiat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fäller det utslag),</text:span> oportere -; esse j-em de re pecuniaria; j-em habere alqm, sumere; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om prætorn)</text:span> j-es constituere, ponere, dare alicui; j. verissimus, sapiens, religiosus, C.; j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">är, ss. den s. dömer efter positiv lag och sträng rätt, skiljaktig från</text:span> arbiter = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">freds- l. förlikningsdomare:</text:span> quum ad j-em causam labefactari sentiunt, ad arbitrum veniunt; judicium est pecuniæ certæ, arbitrium incertæ, C.; j. quæstionis = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nämndens förman, s. stundom företrädde</text:span> quæsitor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(prætorn), deraf:</text:span> quæstioni j-em præesse, Cs.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen om medlem i en dömande folkförsamling:</text:span> se j-em quisque, se dominum vitæ necisque inimici (Coriolani) videbat, L.; non supplex turba timebat (aurea ætate) j-is ora sui, sed erant sine j-e tuti, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. l. oeg. men.: i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Domare:</text:span></text:span> acer et bonorum et vitiorum suorum j.; æquissimus horum studiorum existimator et j.; j-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(critiker)</text:span> me esse, doctorem nolo, C.; male verum examinat omnis corruptus j.; (mea carmina) nec in æde sonant certantia j-e Tarpa, nec -, Hor.; morum j., Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūdĭcium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dömande, dom:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i allm. domares befattning l. deß utöfning l. rätt, förmåga dertill) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Domare-befattning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> befogenhet att sitta domare; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">domsrätt:</text:span></text:span> j-a manere apud ordinem senatorium volunt; j-a transferre a senatoribus <text:soft-page-break/>ad equites, C.; hoc senatus consulto Romano magistratui - domi militiæque imperium atque j. summum - permittitur, Sa. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Domstol, rätt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wanl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rätts-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lagskipning, rättswäsende:</text:span></text:span> j. corrumpere pecuniā; pop. Rom. j-orum severitatem desiderat; assequar, ut populo Romano j. potius, quam judicibus reus defuisse videatur; vetus j-orum vis et gravitas; j-orum æquitas, levitas; j-a reperta sunt distrahendarum controversiarum causa; leges j-aque vi et armis sublata sunt; ratio j-orum constat ex accusatione et defensione; multa civibus inter se communia, leges, jura, judicia -, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i uttrycken: inför rätt l. rätta, jfr</text:span> jus), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rättegång, rättsförhandling, rättegångsordning:</text:span></text:span> lis est in j-o; j. exercet <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(leder, handhafwer)</text:span> prætor; res vocatur, adducitur, deducitur in j-um; in j-um vocare, j-o arcessere alqm; j. fit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hålles)</text:span> de aliquo, de re, de vi; j. accipere (a prætore), conflare, vincere; j. mandati <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om ett uppdrag)</text:span> constitutum est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kommit till stånd),</text:span> C.; j. habet aliquis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(den sakegande),</text:span> C., N.; in j-um venire, N.; iniquo j-o circumveniri; j. capitis, pecuniæ, publicum, privatum, C.; miror, quo pacto j. illud fugerit (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kommit ifrån),</text:span> Hor.; j. capitale, domesticum, Qu.<text:line-break/>d. j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kallas sjefwa den </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rättsfråga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. den </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">uppgift</text:span></text:span> (formula), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwilken rättens ordförande</text:span> (prætor, quæsitor) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förelägger nämnden</text:span> (judicibus) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">att afdöma, hwilket heter:</text:span> j. dare in verba aliqua (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">efter ett wißt formulär):</text:span> j. sit ejusmodi: Octavius judex esto: si paret <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utrönes),</text:span> fundum Capenatem P. Servilii esse -, C. Verr. II. 2. 30.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rättens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dom, utslag;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm. myndighets </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utlåtande, yttrande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om ngt:</text:span> j. facere de re; potentiæ alicujus j. suum condonare; j. rescindere; de ejus meritis senatus tanta j-a fecerat; censorum j-a; Horatius (in cooptando augure) juratus dignitatis meæ j. fecerat, C.; rex ne tam tristis j-i aut secundum j-um supplicii auctor esset, duumviros dixit, L.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pröfning, dom, urskilning, öfwerläggning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (berådt mod); omdöme (som hyses l. fälles), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">öfwertygelse:</text:span></text:span> negat rem esse sui j-i; ita præcurrit j. amicitia tollitque experiendi facultatem; j-o alicujus permittere alqd; multi faciunt multa sine j-o; j-o, constanter, considerate conferre beneficia; gravius j. in dicendo subimus; id aliorum sit j.; deorum j-a de morte afferunt; exposui non philosophorum j-a, sed delirantium somnia; facere j-um, quanti quisque faciendus sit; interponere suum, flectere suum j. adversus alqm; ferri multitudinis j-o; facere multa aliorum j-o; ex eorum fontibus nostro j-o arbitrioque hauriemus; stare suo j-o; eos, qui suo j-o rempublicam tueri volunt, (inimicos existimare non debemus), C.; subjicere se alicujus j-o, Ter.; Ambiorix j-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med afsigt)</text:span> exercitum non conduxit, Cs.; j. animi mutare, Sa.; proferre suum j., Pn.; homo sui j-i, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pröfnings-, urskilnings-, omdömesförmåga; omdöme, smak:</text:span></text:span> præditus firmo j-o; j. acre et certum; sincerum et subtile; intelligens, C.; artibus videndis j. subtile, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūdĭciālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. hör till rättegång l. domstol, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rättegångs-, juridisk:</text:span></text:span> genus dicendi j-e; molestia; causa, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūdĭciārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: id.: res; quæstus; lex <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ang. rättegångswäsendet),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūdĭciŏlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">litet (anspråkslöst) omdöme:</text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūdĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Döma:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentl. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">intr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">döma, fälla dom:</text:span> ii, qui j-ant (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mots.</text:span> is, qui dat judicium, i. e. prætor); de aliqua re inter aliquos, de aliquo, contra alqm; secundum leges; ex æquo et bono, non ex callido versutoque jure j.; recte et integre; incorrupte, C.; sub formula j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(efter lagens bokstaf),</text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">transit.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afdöma, fälla dom i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en sak:</text:span> dixit Fimbria, se illam rem nunquam j-turum esse; causa est a diis immortalibus j-ta, C.; judicium j-re, C. poēt.; res j-ta = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">præjudicat,</text:span> C. <text:line-break/>b. perduellionem j-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(döma öfwer),</text:span> p-nem alicui j-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(döma skyldig till -),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Döma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">genom dom förklara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt för rätt l. ngn för ngt, för att hafwa gjort ngt:</text:span> si j-retur ceteris verbis divortium fieri -; j-etur - hostis Antonius, C.; senatus Catilinam et Manlium hostes j-at; eos senatus j-verat contra rempublicam fecisse, Sa.; exsulem alqm j., N.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Döma:</text:span></text:span> vere si volumus j-re -; non recte de aliquo; de virtutis robore ex ipsa virtute; natura tacita j-at de immortalitate animorum; j. diligenter, fastidiose, libere de aliqua re; poētæ ex persona j-bunt, quid quemque deceat; tyrannus ille ipse j-vit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förklarat, erkänt),</text:span> quam esset beatus, C.; gravius de aliquo; oculis, in utram partem fluat flumen, j-ri non potest, Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bedöma, pröfwa:</text:span></text:span> benevolentiam non ardore quodam amoris j-emus; hæc pondere, non numero j-antur; Chaldæi oculorum fallacissimo sensu j-bant ea, quæ ratione atque animo videre debebant; illud est sic j-dum; alqd odio et amore, non veritate, C.; alqm ex ingenio, Ter.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">prægnant: förmå att döma, pröfwa i wetenskapliga ting; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tänka:</text:span></text:span> aliquantum se adeptos arbitrantur ad j-dum (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i philosophien),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förklara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn för ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">anse; hålla före, öfwertyga sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om ngt:</text:span> Apollo Socratem j-vit sapientissimum; Socrates sapientissimus judicatus oraculo Apollinis; inhumatos miseros, mortem malum j-ant; id nefas et impium j-dum est; honore dignum j-ri; id recte fieri j-bant; j-vit, illis nihil adimi oportere, C.; hoc genus scripturæ leve j-ant, N.; cur hunc - quisquam ab officio discessurum j-ret; locum opportunissimum j-re, Cs.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Finna godt, besluta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (anse rådligt l. lämpligt); i synn. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">impersonelt:</text:span> ab eorum consiliis abesse j-sti, C. ep.; mihi j-tum est deponere illam personam, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūdĭcātum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afdömdt mål; fäldt utslag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (præjudicat); ådömd </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">plikt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">summa:</text:span></text:span> j. est res, de qua sententia lata est; rarum j. afferre; j. solvere, facere, negare, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūdĭcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dömande, rättegångsförhandling:</text:span></text:span> longi subsellii j. si tibi unum alterumve diem abstulerit, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss.</text:span> term. techn. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">är</text:span> j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sjelfwa domstolen i motsats till den öfrige delen af rättegångsförhandlingen,</text:span> C. de Inv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūdĭcāto</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med öfwerläggning, berådt mod:</text:span> Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūdĭcātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: ars <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. dömer, pröfwar),</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūdĭcātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Domarebefattning, -embete:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Abjūdĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fråndöma,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på laglig wäg </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">frånkänna:</text:span></text:span> rem ab aliquo; ab hoc ordine populus Romanus rationem veritatis, integritatis a-vit; sibi ipse libertatem a-vit, C.; ager a-tus, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Adjūdĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tilldöma,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> genom (laga) dom </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillerkänna; döma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till förmån för ngn: </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> in medio relictum quod erat, populo Romano a-vit; alicui domum, causam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rätten, segren i ett mål);</text:span> alqd terræ; alqm alicui in servitutem, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> (Augustus), si quid abest, Italis a-at armis, Hor.; Pompejus salutem imperii et orbis terrarum mihi (Ciceroni) a-vit, C.; optimum saporem ostreis, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dījūdĭco</text:span> (dis-judico), 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Döma, fälla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (afgörande) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utslag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (emellan - -); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">afgöra, afdöma, slita</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en twist:</text:span> inter has sententias, C.; uter utri anteferendus sit, Cs.; sorte alqd, Qu.; controversiam, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Urskilja:</text:span></text:span> vera et falsa; vera a falsis; jus et injuriam, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dījūdĭcātio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afdömande, skiljedom:</text:span></text:span> ista est magna, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dījūdĭcātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injūdĭcātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oafdömd, oafgjord:</text:span></text:span> alqd relinquere i-um, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Præjūdĭcium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: (p. dicitur res, quæ quum statuta fuerit affert judicaturis exemplum, quod sequantur; judicium autem res, quæ causam litemque determinat, Ascon.):<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i juridisk men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I förwäg fälld dom (fördom),</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> förr än laga steg tagits, antingen directe i samma sak l. indirecte i en sak, som till denna står i causalt sammanhang (icke = præjudicat = utslag i analogt fall, hwilket heter</text:span> res judicata <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> exemplum): de Verre non p., sed plane judicium jam factum putatur, quod percrebruit, Siculos omnes actorem suæ causæ contra illius injurias quæsisse; iniquam legem instituet, si existimabit, judicium accusatoris in reum pro aliquo p-o valere oportere; dicebat Metellus, p. se de capite Verris per hoc (ministri ejus) judicium nolle fieri; Oppianicus jam duobus p-is (i. e. condemnatione et ejus, apud quem venenum deprehensum erat, et ejus, qui Oppianico conscius illi facinori fuerat) condemnatus erat, C.; neminem, majore cura occupatis animis, verum esse p. tantæ rei afferre (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">genom ett föregående utlåtande inwerka på afgörandet),</text:span> L.; p-is liberare reum; p-a ab ipsis judicibus facta, Qu.; in patrem meum p. quæritur, Sen.; sine p-o dicimus causam, Ct.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Föregående undersökning:</text:span></text:span> Jct.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afgörande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">dom i förwäg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">på förhand:</text:span></text:span> p-o juvare alqm <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(genom att friwilligt till någon afstå sin del af det arf, på hwilket den andre tänker göra laga anspråk),</text:span> Pn.; absque p-o tu interea sede, dum quærimus, utrum conveniat te sedere an illum, Gell.; victoria hujus vel illius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af de båda enwigeskämparne)</text:span> pro p-o accipitur, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förfång:</text:span></text:span> Jct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Præjūdĭciālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. hör till dom l. undersökning på förhand:</text:span> Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Præjūdĭco</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentl. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På förhand döma, yttra sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer ngt, före den </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">egentliga, lagliga behandlingen l. i en annan sak, hwars afgörande inwerkar på den ifrågawarandes:</text:span> apud censores, qui magistratu abierint, edant - quid in magistratu gesserint, deque iis censores p-ent (- integra tamen res accusatori judicioque servetur); cur non Aviti exemplo usus es, ut per illum (i. e. condemnatione illius), qui attulisset venenum, de hoc (qui nunc reus est) p-retur?; res semel et iterum p-ta, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: på förhand l. i förwäg </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Döma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">afgöra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> id arroganter non p-o, C. ep.; opinio p-ta = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fördom,</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Juga . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Jugum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jūgĕrum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl.:</text:span> -ĕra, -ĕrum, -ĕribus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(beslägtadt med</text:span> jugum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af roten</text:span> jŭg [jūg-, juug] i jugis, juugo, jugulum): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Plogland</text:span></text:span> (duo actus quadrati i. e. 240 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fot i längd, 120 i bredd,</text:span> Varr.): plus quam decem medimna ex j-o exarare; quaternorum j-um, C.; agri; N.; mille arare j-a, Hor.; paucis j-bus, Juv. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åker, jord:</text:span></text:span> movet j-a labefacta fossor, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūgĕrātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på l. för hwarje plogland:</text:span> Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūgĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">indelning i plogland:</text:span> Frontin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jūgis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> jungo):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Beständig, aldrig trytande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (spec.: ej utsinande):</text:span> puteus, C.; aqua, Sa.; thesaurus, Pt.<text:line-break/>b. auspicium juge = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">när ett spann af dragare stallar,</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūgĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Alltjemnt:</text:span></text:span> Ap.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">straxt:</text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jūglans,</text:span> andis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: (Jovi-glans): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Walnöt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (träd och frukt):</text:span> hæc glans optima et maxima a Jove - appellata est, Varr.; candentibus j-ium putaminibus barbam sibi adurere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Jugo, Jugosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Jugum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jŭgŭlā,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Jŭgŭlæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stjernbilden </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Orion:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jŭgŭlum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭgŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nyckelben, strupe, hals:</text:span></text:span> habere concava j-a, C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">isynn. i uttr., s. betyda döda l. dödas:</text:span> alicui dare, præbere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(låta döda sig),</text:span> C.; gladium demittere in j-um alicujus, Pt.; petere j-um, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gå ngn in på lifwet, in på hufwudsaken,</text:span> C., Qu.; ostentare alicui j-um pro aliquo, C.; offerre j-um alicui, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭgŭlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Strypa, döda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> civem; suem, C.; Eumenes in carcere a custodibus j-tus est, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedslå, -göra; beslå, öfwerbewisa:</text:span></text:span> alqm suo gladio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(beslå ngn med hans egna ord),</text:span> Ter.; causa j-ta; is confessione sua j-atur; alqm factis decretisque j.; plumbeo gladio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med de swagaste medel, den minsta ansträngning)</text:span> j. alqm, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭgŭlātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nedhuggande:</text:span> virorum, Cs. (Ht.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jŭgum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: ngt som förenar, lagdt öfwer:</text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ok</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på dragare (seltyg, -don): </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> bestiis j-a imponere; ad j-um accedere, C.; j-o solvere tauros; bos j-a detrectans, Vg.; subacta cervice fert j. juvenca; equis <text:soft-page-break/>demere j., Hor.; per temonem percurrere et in j-o insistere, Cs.; per j-a (equorum solis) chrysolithi - radiabant; bos j. fert, patitur, sustinet, Ov.; bos subit j.; j-o leones subdere, Pn.; notabile j. (Gordii), Ct.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ett par</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> dragare; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">par</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.:</text:span> in agris minore instrumento, minus multis j-is remanserunt (aratores), C.; j. impiorum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mått för jord</text:span></text:span> (modus, quo metiuntur rura): j. vocant, quod juncti boves uno die exarare possunt, Varr., Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ok</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. bild för </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förening:</text:span></text:span> diductos Venus cogit aëneo, Hor. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ok,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. symbol l. bild för träldom:</text:span> legiones sub j-um missæ sunt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(under ett spjut, s. hwilade på och förenade twenne andra),</text:span> C., Cs.; a cervicibus j. servitutis dejicere, repellere, C.; tentari patientiam, ut, si j. acceperint, obnoxios premat, L.; excutere, Ct., Pn.; exuere, T.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twärträ, slå, bom:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twärträ,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (bärstång, -ok), hwarwid korgar l. dyl. buros fästade:</text:span> j. continet sirpiculos, Varr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bom</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i wäfstol:</text:span> tela j-o vincta est, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wågbalk;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wågens tecken på himmelen:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>d. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Roddarebänk:</text:span></text:span> sedent per longa j-a, Vg. <text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twärträ, -slå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hwilande på</text:span> pedamenta), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwarwid winstockarnes toppar stödja l. slingra sig):</text:span> quibus stat recta vinea, dicuntur pedamenta: quæ transversa junguntur, j-a: ab eo vineæ jugatæ dicuntur; vineæ sunt aut simplici j-o (porrecto ordine) aut compluviatæ quadruplici <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(så att liksom en löfsal bildas; jfr</text:span> compluvium, jugatio), Pn. <text:line-break/>III. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bergs-rygg, ås:</text:span></text:span> ex j-o (montis) fiunt (fluminum) divortia, C.; legiones summum j. montis ascendere jubet; in j-o (montis) consistere; summum j. nacti hostes loco depellunt, Cs.; Alpium, Hor.; per j-a Cynthi exercet Diana choros, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭgālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som går i ok l. spann, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spann-:</text:span></text:span> jumenta, Ct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭgāles</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spannhästar:</text:span></text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>b. tela j., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wäfstol med bom,</text:span> Cato.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till äktenskap l. bröllop hörande, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Äktenskaps-, bröllops-:</text:span></text:span> vinculum; lectus, Vg.; tæda; jura, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭgārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hopspänd i par:</text:span> Hyg. - vicus J., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett qvarter i Rom.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭgārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oxskötare, ryktare:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭgo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hopfoga, förena:</text:span></text:span> furcas perticis, Col.; vineæ j-atæ, Varr.; vineas adminiculari et j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förse med</text:span> juga II. e), Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> virtutes omnes inter se nexæ et j-tæ sunt, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bortgifta, gifta:</text:span></text:span> huic eam pater j-arat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förmält),</text:span> Vg.; patrum (senatus) decreta super j-dis feminis, Hor.; verba j-ta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(beslägtade, jfr</text:span> conjugo), Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭgābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förenlig:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭgāmentum</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭgūmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">twärträ i tröskel:</text:span> Cato.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭgūmento</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förena:</text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭgātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">winstockarnes </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Okande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. förseende med twärträn till stöd för topparne:</text:span> j-is duæ species sunt, directa et compluviata, in <text:soft-page-break/>longitudinem et latitudinem jugata, Varr.; adminiculorum ordines, capitum j., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭgōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bergig:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Adjŭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Foga intill; tillfoga:</text:span></text:span> vitem (jugo), Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">(<text:span text:style-name="T3">Bĭjŭgis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">nom. sing. comm.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">obr.),</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bĭjŭgus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twespanns-, twebets-:</text:span></text:span> equi b-es, Vg.; curriculum, Su.; b-i leones; certamen b-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med twespann),</text:span> Vg. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bĭjŭgi</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twespann</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af hästar:</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bĭjŭgum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: id.: Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bīga</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl.:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bīgæ</text:span> (bijugæ), ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twespann, twespänd wagn</text:span></text:span> (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wagn med 2 hästar):</text:span> non dicitur una biga, sed unæ b-æ; b-æ a conjunctu dictæ, Varr.; Hector raptatus b-is (Achillis), Vg.; b-æ Auroræ, Vg.; b-a, cui Victoria institerat, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bīgātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> bigæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i prägeln:</text:span> argentum; numus, L.; - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.,</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjŭgus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förenad:</text:span> Prisc. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjŭgŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till äktenskap l. bröllop hörande:</text:span> myrtus, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjŭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanföra, -binda, förena:</text:span></text:span> amicitiam similitudo morum, C.; nuptiis sibi aliquam, Ap. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. i gramm.:</text:span> verba c-ta, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. höra till samma stam:</text:span> c-ta verba, ut sapiens, sapienter, pluo, pluvia, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjŭgātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förening:</text:span></text:span> mellis et fellis, Ap.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ords </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stamförwandtskap:</text:span></text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i gramm. = conjugation:</text:span> Prisc.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjŭgātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som förenar, stiftar (förening):</text:span> amoris Hymenæus, Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjux</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjunx</text:span>, jŭgis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">comm.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Make, maka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">man och hustru:</text:span> huic (Dido) c. Sychæus erat, Vg.; carissime, Ov.; fidelissima, C.; Sabinorum omnis multitudo cum liberis et c-bus venit, L.; ereptæ c-is ira; c. Creusa, Vg.; cum c-e casta, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">älskare, -inna:</text:span> Ppt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om djur:</text:span> c. columba abducta marito, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. ulmus c. vitis, Col. <text:line-break/>d. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kamrat:</text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjŭga</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Maka:</text:span></text:span> Jovis, Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjŭgālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Äktenskaplig, äktenskaps-:</text:span></text:span> amor, dii, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjŭgium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förening, förbund:</text:span></text:span> corporis atque animæ, Lucr. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. af man o. qwinna:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Äktenskap, äkta förbund, giftermål:</text:span></text:span> prima societas in ipso c-o est, proxima in liberis; c-a virorum et uxorum; c. Tulliæ meæ, C.; nec jam furtivum Dido meditatur amorem: c. vocat, Vg.; nostri c-i memor vive, Livia, Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kärleksförbund; älskog:</text:span></text:span> non oro (Dido) antiquum c., quod <text:soft-page-break/>prodidit (Aeneas); equæ sine c-is gravidæ fiunt, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">meton.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Make, maka:</text:span></text:span> c-mque domumque, patres natosque videbit (Helena), Vg.; c. principis devotionibus petere, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjŭgiālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Äktenskaps-:</text:span></text:span> foedus; jura: Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dĕcemjŭgis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: currus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tio-spänd; förspänd med 10 hästar:</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injŭgis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: hostia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. ej burit ok),</text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Octōjŭgis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">åtta tillsammans l. på en gång (eg åtta i spannet):</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quădrĭjŭgis</text:span> (quattuor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> jugum) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quădrĭjŭgus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fyrspänd,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om hästar l. wagn (fyra i ett spann l. förspänd med 4 hästar):</text:span> q-es equi, Vg.; q-us currus, Vg.; q-i equi, Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quădrĭjŭgi</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fyrspann af hästar,</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quădrīga</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Quădrĭjuga), ae, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quădrīgæ</text:span>, gārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fyrspann</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af dragare (wanl. hästar); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fyrspänd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fyrbets wagn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jemte hästarne):</text:span> asinorum, Varr.; curru q-arum vehi, C.; duabus admotis q-is in currus earum distentum alligat Metium, L.; falcatæ q-æ, L.; apta q-is equa, Hor.; Amphiaraēa q-a, Ppt.; - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanligast omtalad ss. förekommande wid kappränningar på Circus och i festtåg, ss. attribut för gudar o. s. w.:</text:span> ut quum carceribus sese effudere q-æ -, Vg.; quasi desultorium in q-arum currum incurrere, C.; Jupiter cum q-is in culmine Capitolii, L.; Circensibus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid Circusspelen)</text:span> bigas q-asque agitaverunt nobilissimi juvenes, Su. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttryck till betecknande af skyndsamhet l. seger:</text:span> viribus atque q-is petimus bene vivere, Hor.; in adolescentiam tuam per medias laudes quasi q-is vehentem transversa incurrit misera fortuna reipublicæ, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dubbelpar:</text:span></text:span> initiorum q-æ sunt, locus et corpus, tempus et actio, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quădrīgārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">körswen på fyrbetswagn (i Circus):</text:span> Varr., Su., T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quădrīgārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: habitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sådan körswens),</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quădrīgātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: numus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> qu. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i prägeln,</text:span> L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Quădrīgŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sējŭgis</text:span> (sex, jŭgum), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: currus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sex hästar förspänd,</text:span> Ap. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sējŭges</text:span>, sc. equi = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sex hästar i ett spann:</text:span> s. aurati in Capitolio positi, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sējŭgis</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sējŭgātus</text:span> (sē, jugum), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afsöndrad:</text:span></text:span> gentes s-es, Sol.; animi pars - ab actione corporis s-ta, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Subjŭgus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">satt l. spänd under oket:</text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Subjŭgius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: lora, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">okremmar,</text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Subjŭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Underkufwa:</text:span></text:span> provincia s-ta, Pseud. - Asc.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Subjŭgātor</text:span>, ōris <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Transjŭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerfara:</text:span></text:span> mons Athos a Xerxe t-tus est: Mel. (d. l.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trĭjŭgis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: cisium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(trespänd),</text:span> Aus. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trĭjŭgus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trefaldig:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dragare, dragdjur, ök</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (häst, åsna o. s. w.):</text:span> nitida; j-is deportare alqd; quum morarentur j-a (Argivæ sacerdotis), filii ad jugum accesserunt, C.; vehi junctis j-is; cornua j-orum, N.; j-a sarcinaria; j-orum et carrorum quam maximum numerum coëmere, Cs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūmentārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: mola, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. drifwes af dragare,</text:span> Jct. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūmentārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åkare:</text:span></text:span> Inscr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sŭperjūmentārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: Claudius Imp. pædagogum barbarum et olim s-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stallmästare?</text:span> præfectum jumentariorum?) habuerat, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jungo</text:span>, junxi, junctum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Foga, sluta till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hopfoga, förena, -knippa, -binda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre mening:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> complexu j-gi cum aliquo; corpora inter se j-ta; in certamine se j. ad alqm, C.; tigna inter se; lintres, Cs.; dextram j. dextræ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lägga hand i hand);</text:span> dextras j-imus hospitio (<text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span>); infert se socium Aeneas atque agmina j-it, Vg.; humano capiti cervicem equinam j.; versus impariter j-ti, Hor.; templum j-tum foris duobus, Ov. - M. Pomponius ex me et te j-tus est (i. e. ejus nomina ex nostris), C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om dragare: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hopoka, spänna för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wagnen); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sammansätta, -ställa;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> äfwen om wagnen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">spänna för, förspänna:</text:span></text:span> equum equo (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>), Cs.; j-at vulpes et mulgeat hircos; curru j-it equos; j-ti currum dominæ subiere leones; j. pares juvencos, Vg.; j-re equos Titan velocibus imperat Horis, Ov.; jumentis j-tis vehi, N.; reges ad currum, Juv.; rhedam equis, C.; vehicula, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om orter: genom brygga) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förena, sammanbinda:</text:span></text:span> pons urbem et insulam continenti, Ct. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen:</text:span> amnem ponte = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">slå brygga öfwer floden,</text:span> Pn.; pontem j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(slå brygga),</text:span> Vg., Pn.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanfoga, förena, -binda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. med abstracta och concreta obj. (med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">cum</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl., dat.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och blotta</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span>); verba extrema cum consequentibus ita, ut ne aspere concurrant; prudentiam cum eloquentia; eloquentia j-da est probitate summaque prudentia, C.; foedere, societate alicui j-i; socia arma j-re alicui, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i äktenskap l. kärlek </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förena, förmäla:</text:span></text:span> Dido se viro (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>); connubio j-am stabili, Vg.; j-amur amore, Tib.; matrimonio j-i alicui, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ord: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammansätta</text:span></text:span> (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bilda genom sammansättning):</text:span> translata aut facta aut j-ta verba, C.; verba j-untur ex duobus latinis integris, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stifta, knyta, sluta, ingå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (förening; jfr</text:span> jungere pontem): cum hominibus nostris amicitias, consuetudines j-bat; omnis caritas inter duos aut inter paucos j-itur, C.; affinitatem, foedus j. cum aliquo, L.; foedus; pacem, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Junctus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nära förenad, närstående:</text:span></text:span> causa cum exitu, C.; comes, Ov.; j-simi, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Junctim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillsammans, i sammanhang, i följd:</text:span></text:span> duos consulatus j. gessit, Su. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Junctio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förbindelse:</text:span></text:span> aliquā teneri, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Junctūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fogning, band; hop-spännande:</text:span></text:span> tignorum inter se, Cs.; lapidum, Col., Vitr.; boum, Col. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förbindelse:</text:span></text:span> generis, Ov.; callida j. verborum, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Junctus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: id. Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Juxtā</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Præp.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inwid, bredwid, nära wid,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i eg. och oeg. bet.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> j. accubat, Vg.; legio, quæ j. constiterat, Cs.; j. accedere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(intill),</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lika, i lika mon, utan åtskilnad:</text:span></text:span> j. tecum scio, Pt.; id j. mecum omnes intelligitis; eorum ego vitam et mortem j. æstumo, quoniam de utraque siletur, Sa.; me sustentavit, j. ac si frater esset, C.; j. hieme atque æstate bellum gero; aliaque castella j. ignobilia; j. eam rem ægre passi patres, quam quum consulatum vulgari viderent, L.; j. periculoso, ficta seu vera promeret, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Præp.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bredwid, inwid, utmed:</text:span></text:span> j. viam, N.; vicina Ceraunia j., Vg.; j. ancillas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid - sida, bland)</text:span> lanam facere, Varr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nära,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i tiden:</text:span> senior et j. finem vitæ, T. Dial. 22. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nära intill, näst intill</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i tillstånd l. till beskaffenhet):</text:span> populi imperium j. libertatem, paucorum dominatio regiæ libidini propior est; velocitas j. formidinem, cunctatio propior constantiæ est; j. seditionem ventum est, T.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Näst, näst efter:</text:span></text:span> j. religiones fides humana colitur, L.; j. deos in tua manu positum est, T.; vilitate j. beluas est, Pn.; j. Varronem doctissimus, Gell.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i sammanhang med), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I följd af; enligt:</text:span></text:span> huic cum Aebutio j. vicinitatem consuetudo fuit, L.; inimicitiæ periculosiores sunt j. libertatem, T.; j. præceptum ducis, Js.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Juxtim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I närheten, på nära håll:</text:span></text:span> j. quadrata, procul visa sunt rotunda, Lucr.; j. assidere, Su. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">Præp.</text:span>: j. flumen, Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Abjungo</text:span>, nxi, nctum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spänna ifrån:</text:span></text:span> juvencum, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skilja, lösgöra, afsöndra:</text:span></text:span> Demosthenes se ab hoc judiciali dicendi genere a-rat, C.; a-to Labieno et iis legionibus, quas una miserat, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Adjungo</text:span>, nxi, nctum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Foga till; tillfoga, -knyta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Foga, lägga, sluta, närma till; förbinda med:</text:span></text:span> parietem ad parietem; accessionem ædibus a.; insula (urbi) ponte a-itur, C.; insula urbi a-ta, N.; vitem ulmis a-re, Vg. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spänna för:</text:span></text:span> tauros aratro; mures plostello, Hor.; equos, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. följeslagare (bundsförwandt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Låta sluta sig till;</text:span></text:span> se a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sluta sig till:</text:span></text:span> se alicui comitem, fratrem alicui, C.; a-to Samnitium exercitu, L.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i inre mening:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: i handling, ord, tanke </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bifoga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. bihang), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillfoga, tillägga, -knyta, förbinda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sluta sig, komma till:</text:span></text:span> ad gratiam metum; ornamenta dicendi ad elegantiam; duobus generibus injustitiæ propositis causas a-imus utriusque generis; rebus præsentibus (homo rationis particeps) a-it et annectit futuras; huic veri videndi cupiditati a-tus est principatus appetitus; duabus illis personis tertia a-itur; syllabam ad verbum; a-to, ut iidem prudentes haberentur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om dertill kom);</text:span> a-xit, id minime esse mirandum, C.; ea loca provinciæ finitimæ a-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förena, införlifwa med),</text:span> Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i wänskap l. förbund </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sluta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förmå att sluta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sig) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">till, förena, förbinda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillwinna, winna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngn (sig); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">göra förbunden:</text:span></text:span> se ad alqm a. et applicare; se ad causam, rationes alicujus; alqm ad amicitiam, alqm sibi, se alicui socium, uxorem; aliquem beneficio ad necessitudinem suam; alqm ad usus suos a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(winna för -);</text:span> te mea erga te studia mihi a-unt; hic dies me valde Crasso a-xit; diligentia vestra - mihi a-da est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tagas i anspråk ss. bundsförwandt, hjelpare),</text:span> C.: Ambiorigem sibi societate et foedere a-unt; Sequani Ariovistum sibi a-rant; in spem veniebant de ceteris a-dis civitatibus, Cs.; viros aut a. sibi aut interficere, Sa.; alqm amicum, in amicitiam a., N.; aliquem in societatem, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillägga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. egendom, tillhörighet, tjenande bihang:</text:span> agros populo Romano, C.; urbes imperio suo, Sa.; eam scientiam, quam tu a-is oratori; juris scientiam eloquentiæ tanquam ancillam a., C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bereda, förwärfwa; gifwa, skänka:</text:span></text:span> decus et dignitatem alicui; sibi auxilium, C.; inimicos alicui, Cs.; fidem rebus commenticiis; verbis solutis numeros, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wända, rigta åt; tillämpa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (anwända):</text:span> suspicionem ad prædam (accusatorum) potius, quam ad egestatem (S. Roscii); iis (quæ ab aliis dicta sunt) nostrum scribendi ordinem a-imus, C.; animum ad studium a., Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Adjunctus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Comp.</text:span> -ior, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Närgränsande, nära:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rum: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Närbelägen:</text:span></text:span> agri, Sil.; prædia continentia et a-a; arteria ostium habet a-um linguæ radicibus, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tid:</text:span> horum ætati a-ti duo Fannii fuerunt, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(factiskt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nära sammanhängande; wäsentlig för, s. tillhör:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (constr. ss.</text:span> proprius): perveniam ad ea, quæ hujus causæ propiora et a-ora sunt; hostia maxima parentare pietatis a-um esse putabant, C.; semper in a-is (ævo) ævoque morabimur aptis, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: i rhetoriken l. logiken:</text:span> a-um, a-a = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Attribut;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> det, s. står i förhållande till en sak: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">relation, omständighet:</text:span></text:span> ex a-is (sic concluditur): si bonum est justitia, recte est judicandum, Qu.; loci argumentorum ex a-is repeti possunt, ut quæratur, quid ante rem, quid postea, quid cum re eveniat, C. - pronuntiatum a-um = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hypothetiskt omdöme,</text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Adjunctio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillfogande, bifogande:</text:span></text:span> ii fines bonorum, in quibus nulla est virtutis a.; verborum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Anslutning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i wänskap, umgänge):</text:span> hominis ad hominem, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rhetoriken: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillsats, tillägg,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">inskränkande tillägg, </text:span></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wilkor:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/>d. C. Her. IV. 37.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Adjunctor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. tillägger, -fogar:</text:span> Galliæ, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjungo</text:span>, nxi, nctum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanfoga, förena, förbinda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre mening:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> eam epistolam (Acilii) cum hac tua c-xi; C.; calamos cera; c. dextras, Vg.; montem cum oppido muris; naves cum castris munitione c-re; necesse est nobis Gergoviam contendere et cum Arvernis nosmet c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stöta tillsammans med -),</text:span> Cs.; ædificia moenibus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bygga omedelbart intill, låta sammanhänga),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spänna, sätta tillsammans</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i rede:</text:span> boves, Cato; bis binos equos, Lucr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammansätta:</text:span></text:span> quæcumque cluent, his c-ta duabus rebus invenies, Lucr.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förena, förbinda:</text:span></text:span> Gallias duas uno imperio; salutem alicujus cum salute communi; semper ad meam utilitatem cum Græcis Latina c-xi; non tanti est illud, quod prodesse videtur, ut cum aliquo malo c-atur; hæ artes ne minima quidem societate eloquentiæ c-untur; celeritas respondendi subtili urbanitate c-ta, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i förbund, bolag, slägtskap, wänskap, umgänge o. s. w. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förena, förbinda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngn:</text:span> Germani sese cum his c-rant; Remi propter veteres inimicitias nullo modo cum Hæduis c-i poterant, Cs.; socium fallere, qui in negotio se c-xit, Cs.; Macedonibus c-i, L.; foedere alicui c-i; hunc cape consilii socium et c-e volentem, Vg.; cum aliquo usu, affinitate, propinquitate, benevolentiā, hospitio c-i; alicui alqm communia c-rant, C., feminam sibi matrimonio, L.; se cum aliquo viro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gifta),</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stifta, tillwägabringa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (förening):</text:span> amicitiam; benevolentiam; Romulus Sabinorum connubia c-xit, C.<text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">göra ngt tillsammans med ngn:</text:span> bellum c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gemensamt föra,</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>d. (= continuare) = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">göra (utföra, iakttaga o. s. w.) i ett, utan afbrott:</text:span> consulatus, Su.; abstinentiam cibi, T.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ord = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förbinda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (construera):</text:span> vocales c., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">låta sammansmälta i uttalet,</text:span> C.; verba <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sammansätta),</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjunctus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre menin g:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanhängande; gränsande, stötande intill:</text:span></text:span> supercilia, Su.; tecta muris, L.; Paphlagonia Cappadociæ, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammansatt:</text:span></text:span> c-um est id, quod sine (pernicie) sejungi non potest, Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tiden </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nära, närstående:</text:span></text:span> ætate c-ior, C. <text:line-break/>b. verba c-ta = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förbundna, i sammanhang stående (mots.</text:span> simplicia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> singula), C. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">genom slägtskap l. wänskap </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nära förenad, förbunden; närstående, förtrogen:</text:span></text:span> omnium civium Romanorum sanguis c. est; non solum amicitiā, verum etiam cognatione c. cum aliquo; homo c-simus; officiis, usu, consuetudine c.; et cum illis et inter se c-simos fuisse M’ Curium et Ti. Coruncanium memoriæ proditum est; alicui <text:soft-page-break/>concordiā c-simum esse; ut quisque erit c-simus, ita in eum benignitatis plurimum conferetur, C.<text:line-break/>d. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gemensam:</text:span></text:span> cum Scipione mihi c-a cura de re publica et de privata fuit; summum bonum ita instituit, ut nihil habeat cum virtute c-um, C.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanhörande;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i oeg. men.) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">beslägtad; s. står nära; öfwerensstämmande, enlig:</text:span></text:span> talis simulatio vanitati est c-ior, quam liberalitati; philosophia oratori est c-a maxime; præcepta (officii) naturæ c-a; virtuti tuæ fortuna c-a est; vita rustica cum officio, C. <text:line-break/>f. c-um pronuntiatum = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sammansatt (copulativt) omdöme:</text:span> Gell. XVI. VIII. 9. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjuncta</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wäsendtliga) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Attribut,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> egenskaper:</text:span> ex c-is argumenta ducere, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjuncte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I förening, tillsammans:</text:span></text:span> c. re et verbo risus movetur, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I sammanhang med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">betingadt, med ett wilkor:</text:span></text:span> si quid simpliciter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(obetingadt, categoriskt),</text:span> si c. elatum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utsagdt)</text:span> est -, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I förtroligt umgänge:</text:span></text:span> c-e, c-ius, c-sime vivere cum aliquo, N., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjunctim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillsammans, i förening:</text:span></text:span> referre de aliqua re, C.; petere auxilium salutis c. (cum amico), N. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjunctio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förening, sammanhang:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> c. virtutum; c. naturæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sammanhanget i werlden),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förening, förbindelse, samfund</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> menniskor emellan (af allmän l. serskild art, ss. slägtskap, wänskap, grannskap, kamratskap, förbund, bolag o. s. w.):</text:span> ad c-em hominum et ad naturalem communitatem nati sumus; optime societas hominum c-oque servabitur, si -; c-es fratrum, consobrinorum sobrinorumque; sanguinis c. devincit homines benevolentiā et caritate; c-is appetitus procreandi causa; vicinitatis; quæsturæ c. (cum proconsule) liberorum necessitudini proxima est; Cæsaris cum Pompejo, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frändskap, slägtskap:</text:span></text:span> syllogismi nonnulla est cum finitione conjunctio, Qu.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ords l. begrepps </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanställning, förbindelse:</text:span></text:span> vitare quasdam c-es verborum, Qu. - hæc. c. (sententiarum) ex repugnantibus est, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. = en wiß förbindelse af 2 ord: mots.</text:span> adjunctio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> disjunctio, C.<text:line-break/>d. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förbindande ord, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">conjunction:</text:span></text:span> demptis c-bus plura dissolute dicere, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjunctus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förbindelse, sammansättning.</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dējungo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åtskilja:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Disjungo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dījungo</text:span>, nxi, nctum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skilja, aflägsna:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> intervallo locorum et temporum d-i; ab Italia freto d-i, C.; agnos a mammis matris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(afwänja, -hålla),</text:span> Varr.; longe Italis d-imur oris, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spänna ifrån:</text:span></text:span> jumenta, C.; boves ab opere, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tiden skilja:</text:span> eorum ætates non annis, sed seculis d-tæ fuerunt, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skilja, hålla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> utom förbindelse med; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">aflägsna, söndra:</text:span></text:span> se a corporibus, ab orationibus; populum a senatu; alqm ab amicitia alicujus, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i begreppet </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skilja:</text:span></text:span> honesta a commodis; oratorem et philosophum, C.; pastionem a cultura (agri), Varr. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Motsätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (disjunctivt förbinda):</text:span> ex iis, quæ d-untur, unum verum esse debet, falsa cetera, Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Disjunctus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skild; aflägsen:</text:span></text:span> terræ d-simæ, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som är långt ifrån</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ej nås af l. befattar sig med):</text:span> vita a scelere; ab imperitorum intelligentia sensuque longissime d-um, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Serskild:</text:span></text:span> non dijuncti erant doctores, sed iidem vivendi præceptores et dicendi, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skild</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">olik med; motsatt:</text:span></text:span> monstrum d-um et diversum; omne ita d-um, quasi aut etiam, aut non, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om stil: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Osammanbunden</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lös):</text:span> concursus verborum d-i et hiantes, C.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. ss. rhetorisk term:</text:span> d-um est, quum eorum, de quibus dicimus, unumquidque certo concluditur verbo: sic: populus Rom. Numantiam delevit, Carthaginem sustulit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o. s. w.,</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Disjuncte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Comp.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I bestämd åtskilnad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i disjunctiv form, i form af disjunctivt omdöme):</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Disjunctim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span> = disjuncte: Jct. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Disjunctio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(personers) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skilsmässa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (afsöndring), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">söndring:</text:span></text:span> tantus luctus, tanta d.; d-em facere (ab amico); animorum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Motsättning, motsats, disjunction</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i logisk men.):</text:span> in d-e plus uno verum esse non potest, C.<text:line-break/>c. disjunctum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> disjunctus. 2. e.: C., Qu. (IX. 3. 45.).<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Disjunctīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Disjunctiv</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i logisk l. gramm. men.:</text:span> proloquium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(omdöme),</text:span> Gell. - conjunctio, Charis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injungo</text:span>, nxi, nctum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Infoga; foga intill:</text:span></text:span> asseres in asseres; aggerem muro, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillfoga, -skynda:</text:span></text:span> reipublicæ detrimentum, C.; alicui injuriam, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pålägga, kasta på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn (en börda, ett göromål), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">påbörda, ålägga:</text:span></text:span> servitutem alicui, Cs.; munus, onus alicui; si quid i-re inferiori velis, prius in te ac tuos idem juris (statuas), L.; laborem alicui, Qu.; tibi i-imus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bedja),</text:span> ut -, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Interjungo</text:span>, nxi, nctum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Foga emellan, slå i hop:</text:span></text:span> dextræ i-tæ sunt (ducum), L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spänna ifrån</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för en stund, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lösa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> att beta:</text:span> equos, Mt. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rasta:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sējungo</text:span>, nxi, nctum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afskilja, skilja, åtskilja:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skilja, upplösa:</text:span></text:span> conjunctum est id, quod sine (pernicie) non potis est sejungi, Lucr.; Alpes Italiam a Gallia s-unt, N.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i werkligheten </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afskilja, aflägsna; hålla ifrån, skild</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ifrån;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">refl.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">afhålla sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från -:</text:span> s-e te aliquando ab iis; tua calamitas a <text:soft-page-break/>reip. periculo s-atur; animus a spe s-i non potest; se a libertate verborum s-re, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">isynn.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">part.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sējunctus</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afskild, serskild, skild</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. ligger utom, ej beröres l. beror af):</text:span> Atticus nullam s-tam sibi amico voluit fortunam; hoc a re proposita s-tum est, N.; (ars constat ex) rebus perspectis planeque cognitis atque ab opinionis arbitrio s-tis, C.; rhetorice a virtute s-ta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(oförenlig),</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i begreppet l. uppfattningen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skilja, åtskilja; göra, uppställa skilnad:</text:span></text:span> fortunam ab inconstantia s.; cogitatione morbum s. ab ægrotatione; nunc ita s-am, quasi possit quisquam, qui non idem prudens sit, justus esse, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sējunctim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Serskildt, åtskils:</text:span></text:span> Tib. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sējunctio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afskiljande:</text:span></text:span> C., Qu. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">söndring = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twedrägt:</text:span></text:span> Fl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Subjungo</text:span>, nxi, nctum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Foga inunder, spänna för:</text:span></text:span> puppis s-ta leones (i. e. quæ s-tos habet leones = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deras bilder inunder),</text:span> Vg.; tigres curru (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>), Vg. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Underkasta, underordna, underlägga, tillägga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. uppgift l. befattning, betydelse o. d.; logiskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">underordna, hänföra under:</text:span></text:span> multas urbes sub imperium pop. Romani; orbem sub jus et potestatem alicujus; omnes artes oratori, C.; mihi res, non me rebus s-re conor, Hor; uni utrumque nomen, Lucr.; translationi et hæc ipsa Aristoteles s-it, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillfoga, bifoga,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. fortsättning af eget tal l. ss. swar:</text:span> hæc s-ta sunt, C.; verbo idem verbum, Qu.; is dicit, ego pauca s-o, Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sätta i stället:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Subjunctīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">underordnande:</text:span> modus, Gramm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Transjungo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spänna om, på andra sidan:</text:span> mulam, Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Jugument . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Jugo, Jugum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">J</text:span>ŭgurtha, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">numidisk konung.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Jŭgurthīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">J</text:span>ūlius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Jūlius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Jūlia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på en romersk</text:span> gens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och deß medlemmar.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Jūliānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>ūlus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: n. pr. = Ascanius. <text:line-break/>Iūlēus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Jument . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Jugum.<text:line-break/>Juncetum, -ceus, -cinus, -cosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Juncus.<text:line-break/>Junct . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Jungo, Jugum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Juncus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Säf:</text:span></text:span> mollis, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Juncētum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">säfrik ort, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waßbänk:</text:span></text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Junceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är af säf l. liksom af säf:</text:span> sporta, Col.; virgo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wek, späd),</text:span> Ter. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Juncīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> = junceus: Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Juncōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Säfrik:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ējuncesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blifwa späd:</text:span></text:span> Pn. (inc. l.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ējuncĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Säflik,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tunn, spenslig:</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Jungo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Jugum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jūnĭcŭlus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">winranka:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Junior <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Juvenis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jūnĭpĕrus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">En-buske, -träd:</text:span></text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">J</text:span>ūnius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn en romersk</text:span> gens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och deß medlemmar.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">J</text:span>ūnius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn för årets sjette månad och deß dagar:</text:span> mensis, C.; calendæ, Col. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om härledningen se</text:span> Ov. Fast. VI. init.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Junix <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Juvenis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">J</text:span>ūno, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Juno,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> gudadrottningen:</text:span> <text:line-break/>Jūnōnius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Jūnōnālis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Jūnōnĭcŏla, ae, c.: (colo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dyrkare af Juno:</text:span> Ov. <text:line-break/>Jūnōnĭgĕna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">son af Juno:</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">J</text:span>uppĭter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">J</text:span>ūpĭter (Jovis pater), <text:span text:style-name="T2">gen.</text:span> Jŏvis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Juppitter,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> den högste guden. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Himmel, luft:</text:span></text:span> J. malus urget; sub Jove frigido, Hor. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">J</text:span>ūra ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bergsnamn:</text:span> Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Jura . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Juro, I. Jus. <text:line-break/>Jureconsultus, -peritus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Jus.<text:line-break/>Jureus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Jus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jurgium</text:span> <text:line-break/>(jurĭgium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> jus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> ago?), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Träta, gräl, gnabb, ordwexling; onda ord:</text:span></text:span> ex inimicitiis j., maledicta, contumeliæ gignuntur; inter eos exstitit; in j-o respondere alicui; j-is abstinere; j-o contendere cum aliquo, C.; j-a nectere cum aliquo, Ov.; notabile j.; acre j. (in senatu), T.; j-o abigere alqm, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jurgiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grälaktig, trätlysten:</text:span></text:span> Xanthippe, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jurgo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Träta, gräla:</text:span></text:span> ancilla cum Davo, Ter.; vicini inter se, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förebrå, bestraffa:</text:span></text:span> jure Trausius istis j-atur verbis, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Objurgo</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">arch.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Objūrĭgo</text:span> (Pt. Merc. 46. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Ritschl; jfr. Lorenz</text:span> Mil. gl. 496), 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Banna, förebrå, göra förebråelser, bestraffa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med ord):</text:span> aliquem ut pater; et monendi amici sæpe sunt et o-di; o. alqm de <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> in aliqua re; o. verecundiam alicujus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(göra ngn förebråelse för -);</text:span> o-bar, quod nimio gaudio pæne desiperem; o. alqm, ut sit firmior, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i handling </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Näpsa, bestraffa, tukta:</text:span></text:span> soleā, puer, o-bere rubra, Ps.; ferulis, flagris alqm, Su.; colaphis, Petr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Objurgātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förebråelse, bestraffning:</text:span></text:span> o. (adhibeatur), si est auctoritas, tum admonitio, quasi lenior o.; monitio acerbitate, o. contumelia careat, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Objurgātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bestraffare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. gör förebråelser:</text:span> benevolus, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Objurgātōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af förebrående innehåll l. syftning, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förebrående, bestraffande:</text:span></text:span> epistola, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Objurgĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Banna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (häftigt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bestraffa:</text:span></text:span> Pt. (Trin. 68 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Fl.;</text:span> objurigo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Ritschl,</text:span> Index lect. 1854).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Juri . . ., Juro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Jus.<text:line-break/>Jurulentus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Jus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Jūs,</text:span> jūris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blott</text:span> jūra, <text:span text:style-name="T2">nom.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">acc.</text:span> (jurium, Cato): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (egentl. positiv: ordet är wäl i slägt med</text:span> jubeo, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss.</text:span> rus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> ruo, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och deß ursprungliga form</text:span> juvus, ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">analog med</text:span> gen-us, generis):<text:line-break/>1. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rättsbestämning, -sstadgande; lag,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ofta i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">sing.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">collectivt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lagens bud:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">positiv, borgerlig l. religiös </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rätt, lag:</text:span></text:span> j. civile = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">privaträtt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> så wäl af folket stiftad</text:span> (lex), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som rättssedwänja</text:span> (consuetudo civilis): legum ac j-is civilis scientia; rudis in j-e civili; j. civile discere ab aliquo; hæc j-a civilia (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">juridiken ss. wetenskap)</text:span> jam diu versantur in nostra familia (Scævolarum); de j-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eller</text:span> jus respondere (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gifwa upplysningar l. råd i lagfrågor);</text:span> j-is optime constituti interpretatio semper apud nos in honore fuit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> C. Or. pro Murena); j-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lagens bud l. stadganden om)</text:span> usucapionum, stirpis, gentilitatis, tutelæ; j-is peritus; j-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> jure consultus; j-is ignarus, rudis in j-e; j. publicum; j-a publica, quæ sunt propria civitatis atque imperii <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(statsrätten, romerska statsrätten);</text:span> j. pontificium; j. prætorium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= prætors förordningar, mots.</text:span> leges); omnia j-a (divina et) humana pervertere; mortuis j-a religiosa tribuere (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med afseende på dem stifta);</text:span> nullo se j-e publico <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(samhällets lag)</text:span> et legitimo vinci patiuntur; ex j-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enligt lag, i laglig wäg);</text:span> contra jus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(olagligt);</text:span> controversa j-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(omtwistade rättspunkter l. lagfrågor),</text:span> C.; si mala condiderit in quem quis carmina, j. est judiciumque, Hor.; j-is nodos et ænigmata solvere, Juv. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> 4.).<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allmännare mening:</text:span> j. hominum, gentium, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">allmän menniskorätt (naturrätt); folkrätt;</text:span> j. naturæ, j. humanæ societatis violabit, si quis plus appetet eo, quod ei obtigit; j-a belli; cum justo hoste multa j-a sunt communia; j. amicitiæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wänskapens lagar)</text:span> deserere, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rätt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om det, som enligt lagen är rätt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rättwisa, lag:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enligt positiv, skrifwen lag:</text:span> summum j., summa injuria; j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sträng rätt, lagens bokstaf)</text:span> urgebat Crassus, æquitatem Antonius; ad extrema j-a decurrere; non de facto, sed de j-e certatur; eæ causæ, de quarum j-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rättsliga beskaffenhet)</text:span> dubium esse non possit, non solent in judicium adduci; j. dicere, reddere; j-a describere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skipa rättwisa, rätt, lag);</text:span> j. erat (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det war i lagen tillåtet),</text:span> ad sacrificium curru vehi sacerdotem, C.; j. stat ab eo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(han har rätten på sin sida);</text:span> postulare j.; j. causæ, L.; j-a dabat, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> j. dicis, petis; cum bono j-e, sine bono j-e; j. æquumque oras, Pt.; j-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med rätta)</text:span> irasci, Ter.; j. est belli, ut victis victores ex arbitrio imperitent, Cs.; non quæro, j-e an injuriā; j-e lugere possum vitam hominum; optimo j-e rideri, laudari; j-e plectimur; j-e cum hoste pugnare non poterat, C.; j-e omnes: Galba negabat, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">någons </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rätt, rättighet:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rättighet, som tillhör person l. sak </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(rättstillstånd):</text:span></text:span> æquo et pari j-e cum civibus vivere; j. mutandæ civitatis; domus, prædia optimo j-e (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som egas på de bästa besittningswilkor för den enskilde);</text:span> de j-e suo decedere, cedere; j. suum tenere, obtinere, persequi, amittere; j. eripere alicui; hoc pro meo j-e mihi sumo; suo j-e sibi vindicare <text:soft-page-break/>alqd; Cæsar omnes provincias gentesque uno calamitatis j-e comprehendit (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gjort alla till slafwar);</text:span> is hoc j-e est, C.; j. suum armis exsequi, Cs.; pro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> de suo j-e agere, Ter.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">myndighet, makt, befogenhet:</text:span></text:span> sui j-is esse <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wara myndig, sjelfständig);</text:span> omnes provinciæ sub j-e consulis esse debent; provinciam obtinere optimo j-e, C.; sua esse (dicebat) ejusmodi imperia, ut non minus haberet j-is in se multitudo, quam ipse in multitudinem, Cs.; patrio j-e animadvertere in filium, L.; aliter nullius earum rerum consuli j. est, Sa.; j. a patribus etiam nunc usurpatur, vi adempta, L.; j. habere in alqm, in alqd, Pn.; j. datum sceleri (in bello civili), Luc.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> casus obliqui: in jus, in j-e = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inför rätta, inför domstol</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">domare; i rättsfrågor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (uttrycket brukas om en saks behandling inför lagskipande myndighet i allm., mots.</text:span> judicium = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dom, utslags fällande):</text:span> in j-e abjurare pecuniam, Pt.; in jus vocare alqm, adducere alqm; in j-e cavere, consilio juvare; hærere in j-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om en advocat),</text:span> C.; si in jus vocat, ito, XII Tabb.; in jus ire de re sua, N.; in jus ad regem rapi, L., Hor.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förbindelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. afgifwes):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sammanställningen</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jusjūrandum</text:span>, jurisjurandi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o. s. w.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ed,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> edlig förpligtelse (borgerlig, mots.</text:span> sacramentum = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">krigarens ed):</text:span> est j. affirmatio religiosa, C.; j. sanctissimum, Cs.; j. dare, C., Cs.; j. conservare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hålla);</text:span> j-i fidem servare; j-o teneri, astringi; j-o liberari, solvi; fraus j-i; j. negligere, violare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bryta);</text:span> contra j. facere; j-o firmare alqd; j. hostium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till fienderne gifwen),</text:span> C.; alqm j-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> ad j-um adigere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förmå att swärja, taga ed af ngn);</text:span> j-o inter se sanxerunt, ne quis ea enuntiaret; j-o obstrinxerant civitatem, se obsides non repetituros; j-o inter se confirmare alqd, Cs.; ab aliquo exigere j. in verba aliqua; j. reddere, interponere, L.; alligare fidem j-o, Sen.; deferre j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(erbjuda sig till edgång),</text:span> Qu.; concipere j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(affatta),</text:span> T. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utom denna sammanställning:</text:span> fidei sacratæ j., Acc. ap. C.; poena j-is pejerati <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för mened),</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūrĭdĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är för lagskipning:</text:span> conventus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(thing),</text:span> Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūrĭdĭcus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">domare:</text:span> Sen., Cap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūrĭdĭciālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: constitutio, status, causæ, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">der det ej twistas om factum, utan om deß laglighet l. olaglighet:</text:span> C., Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūrisconsultus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūrĕconsultus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūrispĕrītus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūrĕpĕrītus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äfwen skrifna ss. serskilda ord),</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lagfaren</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i borgerliga lagen), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">jurist:</text:span></text:span> j. is est, qui legum et consuetudinis ejus, qua privati in civitate utuntur, peritus est, C. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(se widare</text:span> consultus (consulo) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> peritus).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūrisdictio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äfwen skrifwet ss. twå ord): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lag-skipning; domsrätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jurisdiction); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">domareförrättning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (thing); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">domarebefattning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (prætors); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lagskipningsdistrict,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (domsaga):</text:span> j-em absolvere, conficere, C.; celebrare, L.; j. M. Atilio prætori urbano mandata est: (M. Aemilius, cujus peregrina sors erat (i. e. j. inter peregrinos) Luceriam provinciam haberet), L.; j. ei evenerat, T.; sub <text:soft-page-break/>suam j-em urbes, provincias, nationes subjungere, C.; mediterraneæ, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injūrus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Orättrådig:</text:span></text:span> oderunt di homines i-os, Næv. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Ribb.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injūrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Orättwis, obillig; orätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om handlingar):</text:span> pater, Ter.; negat (id fore), quia sit i-um, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injūria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Orätt, orättwisa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. handling, ej ss. egenskap):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i och för sig: (olaglighet, orätt):</text:span> summum jus summa i.; duobus modis, aut vi aut fraude, fit i.; juris et i-æ quæstio; i-ā = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">med orätt, utan skäl, obefogadt:</text:span></text:span> non i-ā suspectus fuit; neque mehercule i-ā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(och det med rätta),</text:span> C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Orätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">orättwisa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i handling l. ord), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">oförrätt, öfwerwåld:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> patris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hårdhet),</text:span> Ter.; non tulit patriæ i-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af fäderneslandet);</text:span> civium, tua i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af dig),</text:span> C.; i-æ Hæduorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mot H.),</text:span> Cs.; i-ā afficere, lacessere, lacerare alqm; i-am inferre, facere, injungere alicui; fit alicui i.; i-am propulsare, defendere, prohibere ab aliquo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(afwärja);</text:span> i-ā prohibere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wärja)</text:span> alqm; i-am pati; accipere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lida)</text:span> i-am ab aliquo; ulcisci i-as; oblivisci i-arum; gravis eum afflixit i., C.; Helvetiorum i-æ populi Romani <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mot R. f.);</text:span> alqm defendere, prohibere ab i-is, Cs.; utrinque i-æ factæ; illi contigit otium sine i-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utan att förorättas),</text:span> L.; bella suscipienda sunt, ut sine i-a in pace vivatur, C.; nostræ i. cædis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af l. i mordanfallet på oß),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: personlig (kroppslig) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mißhandling, wåld</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. angrepp på ngns heder; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förolämpning, förnärmelse, kränkning:</text:span></text:span> i-æ sunt, quibus aut pulsatione corpus aut convicio aures aut aliqua turpitudine vitam alicujus violant; i-arum actio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för öfwerwåld);</text:span> i-arum damnari, C.; virgini facere i-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kränka),</text:span> P<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">t.;</text:span> hic sanguis (Lucretiæ) castissimus ante regiam i-am, L.; i-arum formulam intendere alicui, Su.: i. spretæ formæ (Junonis), Vg.; integritatem atque abstinentiam in tanto viro referre i. virtutum fuerit, T.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af opersonlig orsak wållad </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skada, åwerkan:</text:span></text:span> ignis; pluviæ, Col.; cælestis, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injūriōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer och deras handlingssätt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Orättfärdig, orättwis, orätt; wåldsam:</text:span></text:span> in eo peccant, quod i-i sunt in proximos; avaritia est i-a appetitio alienorum; ab iuvito emere i-um est; in socios i. et contumeliosus, C.; adversus alquem i-ior; i-um est ex rapto vivere, Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wåldsam, skadlig:</text:span></text:span> ventus, Hor.; ictus, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injūriōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med orätt; med wåld</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mißhandling:</text:span></text:span> suspicari; mercatores i-ius tractati, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injūrie</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Orätt:</text:span></text:span> Næv. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Ribb.</text:span> Trag. 42.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injūrior</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwa orätt, öfwerwåld:</text:span></text:span> omne fortuitum citra nos sævit et i-atur, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swärja; gå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">aflägga ed:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. pf.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och någon gång i de dermed sammansatta formerna deponentialt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.:</text:span> j-vi linguā: mentem injuratam gero, Acc. ap. C.; adduci non potuit, ut j-ret aut obsides daret, Cs.; sancte, Ter.; conceptis <text:soft-page-break/>verbis j-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förestafwad ed),</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid ngn l. ngt:</text:span> per deos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. blott</text:span> deos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid gudarne),</text:span> C.; numina j-ta; dis j-da palus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwarwid gudarne swärja),</text:span> Ov.; alicui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid ngn),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swärja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt l. på ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">med ed bedyra, lofwa:</text:span></text:span> j. jusjurandum verissimum pulcherrimumque; ex animi sententia j. alqd; quod ita j-tum est, ut mens conciperet, fieri oportere; j. morbum (i. e. se morbo laborare); j-verat, se rediturum esse, se illum interfecturum esse; decem homines ad senatum misit Hannibal j-tos se redituros, C.; j-re me jussit, numquam me in amicitia cum Romanis fore, N.; j. calumniam i. e. se sine calumnia accusaturum, C., L.; j-o, me Tarquinium ferro ignique exsecuturum esse, L.; j-at bene solis esse maritis; j-bas fore hunc amorem mutuum, Hor.<text:line-break/>d. j. in litem, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">beswärja processens rättmätighet l. sin fordran;</text:span> in leges <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till dem</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">så att man underkastar sig dem = på att hålla dem),</text:span> C.; in verba alicujus i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">efter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngns ord, aflägga den ed han förestafwar, swärja honom trohet l. lydnad,</text:span> Cs.; L.; in verba j-bas mea; j-re in verba magistri, Hor.; mihi j-tus est, se argentum dare, Pt.; ex lege, in quam j-ti sitis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Edswuren</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om wittne l. domare):</text:span> crede mihi j-o; quum j-o sententia dicenda est, meminerit, deum se adhibere testem, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injūrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som ej swurit, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ej edswuren, ej bunden af ed:</text:span></text:span> mentem i-am gero, Acc. ap. C.; i-us in codicem id inferre noluit, C.; jurati i-ique fugiunt, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūrāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ed:</text:span></text:span> Sen. (d. 1.), Jct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūrandum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ed:</text:span></text:span> Pt. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> jusjurandum)<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ed:</text:span></text:span> Mcb. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūrātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som swär l. swurit:</text:span> falsus j., Mcb.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">edswurne </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wärderingsmän</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid census, trol. biträden till censorerne (ej desse sjelfwe):</text:span> census quum sum, j-i recte rationem dedi, Pt.: ornamenta et vestem muliebrem - in censum j-es referre jussi, L. (XXXIX. 44. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Mdv.) - bildl.:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Abjūro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swärja sig fri</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ifrån</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">edeligen förneka:</text:span></text:span> mihi a-re certius est, quam dependere, C.; in jure a-ant pecuniam, Pt.; id, quod creditum est, Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Adjūro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ytterligare swärja; swärja, lägga ed</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ett påstående, på ngt; i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">swärja, bedyra:</text:span></text:span> præter commune jusjurandum hæc a-arent, L.; affirmat, non esse periculum: a-at, C.; per deos, Ter.; Stygii fontis caput, Vg.; a-at, non posse se perdurare, Ter.; a-as, te id me invito non esse facturum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjūro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gemensamt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillsammans swärja; inbördes genom ed förbinda, -pligta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig till ngt:</text:span> inter se, Pt.; senatus consultum - ut omnes juniores Italiæ c-arent <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(swärja fanan),</text:span> Cs.; trecenti c-vimus principes juventutis Romanæ, ut in te hac via grassaremur; c-ant, nisi victores se non redituros; in arma, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanswärja sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i hemlighet för ett brottsligt l. farligt </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ändamål; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bilda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">deltaga i sammanswärjning:</text:span></text:span> contra rempublicam c-vit Catilina, C., Sa.; de interficiendo Pompejo; tantum habeo æris alieni, ut cupiam c-re, C.; c-vere nobilissimi cives patriam incendere, Sa.; in omne facinus, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sluta sig tillsammans, förbinda, förena sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ett ändamål:</text:span> omne Latium trepido tumultu c-at (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rusar till strid),</text:span> Vg.; Græcia c-ta rumpere nuptias (Paridis), Hor.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> (natura et ars) c-ant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(samwerka)</text:span> amice, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjūrātus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanswuren,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> deltagare i sammanswärjning l. complott:</text:span> manus c-orum; c-i Catilinæ, C.; ibi c-i multa inter se de novo consilio egerant, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Conjūrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanswärjning, -gaddning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för brottsligt l. upproriskt ändamål:</text:span> si omnia facienda sint, quæ amici velint, non amicitiæ tales, sed c-es putandæ sunt; facere c-em; deprehendere; c. perditorum hominum, C., c-em patefacere; princeps, populares <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(deltagare)</text:span> c-is; esse in c-e, extra c-em; c. Catilinæ, Sa.; Capuæ occultæ principum c-es factæ, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förening</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ett ändamål:</text:span> Orgetorix c-em nobilitatis fecit, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dējūro</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dējĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swärja dyrt:</text:span></text:span> Pt.; se non vidisse, Ter.; Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dējūrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ed:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ējūro</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ējĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">swärja sig från ngt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jäfwa:</text:span></text:span> judicem; forum; ejero, iniquus est; e-o illum mihi iniquum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ss. partisk mot mig),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">edeligen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förneka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> något såsom sitt; i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förneka, ej erkänna, wägra:</text:span></text:span> patrem; liberos, Sen.; gens Germanicæ originis e-tā patriā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med förnekande af -)</text:span> Agrippinenses vocabantur, T.; militiam e., Sen.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">edeligen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förneka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig ega ngt:</text:span> e. bonam copiam (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sig ega tillgångar att betala med),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>d. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedlägga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett embete, hwarwid ed aflades, att det lagligt förwaltats:</text:span> magistratum, Pn., T.; dixit Pallantem ire, ut e-aret, T. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">afstå från:</text:span></text:span> bonam spem, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ējūrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedläggande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (afswärjande) af embete:</text:span> consulum ignominiosa, Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Perjūrus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Menedig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (menedare), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lögnaktig, trolös:</text:span></text:span> p-ior et gloriarum plenior, Pt.; mendax et p., C.; leno p-simus, C., Catl.; domus Priami; fides, Hor.; vir; os, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Perjūrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mened, edsbrott:</text:span></text:span> quod ex animi sententia juraris, id non facere p. est: quod aliter, id si non feceris, nullum p. est; quærere latebram p-o; condiciones pactionesque bellicas p-o perturbare; facere p.; Jovem lædere p-o, C.; inæstimabile, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Perjūriōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">full af mened:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Perjūro</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pejĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swärja falskt, begå mened, bryta sin ed; ljuga:</text:span></text:span> optime hercle p-as, Pt.; non enim falsum jurare p-re est, sed quod ex animi <text:soft-page-break/>sententia juraris, id non facere perjurium est; semel pejeravit, C.; per consulatum, Catl.; Stygias undas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid),</text:span> Luc.; jus pejeratum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bruten ed),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Perjūrātiuncŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Imperjūrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwarwid aldrig swärjes falskt:</text:span> aquæ i-æ amnis (Styx), Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Justĭtium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> jus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> sisto): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppehåll, stillestånd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i lagskipning, en rätts hwila l. ferier:</text:span> edicere, C.; indicere, servare, remittere, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Justus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i juridisk men.) = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">laglig, lag-gill, behörig:</text:span></text:span> pecuniarum a j-is dominis ad alienos translatio; j-a uxor; dies; j-o sacramento contendere cum aliquo; j. rogator comitiorum; nullum bellum j-um est, nisi quod rebus repetitis geritur, C.; res j-a et legitima; bellum j-um piumque, L.; tempus, Vg.; tyrannus, N.; imperium, Cs. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> justa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nedanföre.</text:span><text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i moralisk men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rättrådig, rättwis, rättfärdig:</text:span></text:span> j. homo isque, quem virum bonum dicimus; id ipsum, quod recte fit, ita est j-um, si est necessarium; rebus injustis j-i maxime dolent, C.; Aristides j. appellatus est, N.; eo j-ior alter non fuit, Vg.; j. et tenax propositi vir, Hor.; princeps j., Vell.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Billig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om personer och saker); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skälig:</text:span></text:span> servitus, Ter.; iis j-oribus utimur (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">de äro emot oß rättwisare i sitt omdöme),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rättmätig, grundad, skälig, tillbörlig:</text:span></text:span> j-a reprehensio; poena; honores; magna discidia et plerumque j-a nascuntur, quum -; non j-a causa, cur tanta Laomedonti fieret injuria, C.; causa, Cs.; querella, Ov.; plus j-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mer än tillbörligt),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ordentlig, weder-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillbörlig, behörig, riktig, tillräcklig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sådant ngt bör wara till beskaffenhet l. storhet, antal o. s. w.):</text:span> j-a itinera; j-a victoria; eloquentia; palam jam cum hoste j-um bellum geremus, C.; muri altitudo; funera, Cs.; nusquam adiri ad j-i cursum amnis poterat; proelium; equitatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fulltalig),</text:span> L.; naves instabiles sine j-o pondere, Ov.; acies, Qu.; opus, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Justa</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">någons </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rättigheter, rätt:</text:span></text:span> an judex - possit noscere tua j-a, ubi - verbum non respondeas?, Ter.; (a servis) opera exigenda, j-a præbenda, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillbörlig heder</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt en afliden, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sista hederstjensten, begrafningsbruk, -högtidligheter:</text:span></text:span> j-a facere alicui; funeri j-a solvere; j. exsequiarum, C.; j-a funebria (edoceret Pontifex), L.; peragere; reddere, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Juste</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lagligt; rättwist; med skäl:</text:span></text:span> imperare; facere; vivere, C.; succensere, Sa.; reprehendi, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Justĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rättwisa öfwande, rättwis:</text:span></text:span> mens deorum, Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Justĭtia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rättwisa, rättrådighet, -skaffenshet, rättfärdighet:</text:span></text:span> j-æ primum munus est, ut ne cui quis noceat: deinde ut communibus utatur pro communibus, privatis ut suis; colere j-am; j. in suum cuique tribuendo cernitur, C.; incluta fuit Numæ j., L.; cognoverat <text:soft-page-break/>Divitiaci summam fidem, j-am, temperantiam, Cs.; j-ā gentes frenare superbas, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injustus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Olaglig:</text:span></text:span> fenus, L.; amor, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Orättwis, obillig, hård:</text:span></text:span> vir; res i-æ; pax; incommoda nostra i-sima et acerbissima, C.; hoc nihil i-ius, Ter.; res i-a in pace, L.; noverca, Vg. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oskälig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = oskäligt, omåttligt stor, swår:</text:span> onus, C.; fascis, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injuste</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Orättwist, med orätt:</text:span></text:span> i. impetum facere in alqm; poterat videri facere i., C.; i-sime - pessimæ artes illis, qui coluere, nihil officiunt, reip. cladi sunt, Sa.; versus concinnior - i. totum vendit poēma, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injustĭtia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Orättwisa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. egenskap), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">orättrådighet:</text:span></text:span> Ter.; i-æ duo genera sunt; in omni i-a interest, utrum - -; totius i-æ nulla capitalior est, quam eorum -, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Jūs,</text:span> jūris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sås, soppa:</text:span></text:span> multa j-a confundit coquus, Pt.; hesternum, Ter.; nigrum; fervens, C.; male condītum; tepidum ligurrire, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūreus</text:span>. <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af sås, soppa:</text:span> Pt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūrŭlentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Såsig, smord:</text:span></text:span> Ce.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Juscŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: sorbere, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Jusjurandum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Jus 5.<text:line-break/>Juss . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Jubeo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">J</text:span>ustīnus, <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">J</text:span>ustīniānus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Just . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se för öfrigt</text:span> I. Jus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">J</text:span>ūturna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">källa i Latium och denna källas nymph.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">J</text:span>ŭvĕnālis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personnamn</text:span> (D. Junius Juvenalis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">satirförfattare † under Trajani tid).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jŭvĕnis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">m. f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst. m. f.</text:span>: (<text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span> j-e, <text:span text:style-name="T2">gen. pl.</text:span> j-num) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ung; wuxen; ung man, yngling, ung qwinna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (enl. Varro emellan</text:span> 29—45 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">år; ej alltid strängt skildt från</text:span> adolescens: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">egentl. utm.</text:span> j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mera den unge ss. kraftig, ej ännu förswagad af ålder;</text:span> adolescens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den, s. ej ännu hunnit mogen ålder, jfr</text:span> adolescens): <text:span text:style-name="T2">Comp.</text:span> jūnior (juvenior, T.; Pn.): ovis j., Col.; anni, Ov.; filius j., T.; comitatus nobilium j-um; non facit senectus ea, quæ j-es, sed multo et majora et meliora facit; et infirmitas puerorum et ferocitas j-um et gravitas jam constantis ætatis et senectutis maturitas naturale quiddam habet, C.; cum his, crescente in dies grege j-um, seria ac jocos celebrare; mitis ingenii j.; j-is evasit vere regiæ indolis Serv. Tullius, L.; fervidus j.; imberbus j., tandem custode remoto, Hor.; <text:span text:style-name="T2">Comp.</text:span>: vel mense brevi vel toto j-ior anno, Hor. -; centuriæ j-orum et seniorum; j-ores patrum, L. - mundus j. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i sin ungdom),</text:span> Sen. Oct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭvĕnālis</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭvĕnīlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ungdomlig, ungdomsfrisk:</text:span></text:span> corpus j-ale, Vg.; diem adjecit Saturnalibus appellavitque j-alem; ludi j-ales, Su.; J-alia, id., <text:soft-page-break/>T.; - j-ilis licentia, redundantia, C.; ludus, L.; ætas, Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭvĕnīlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ungdomligt, s. en yngling:</text:span></text:span> exsultare, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭvencus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭvenca</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(juvenicus, -ca):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adj.</text:span>: equus, Lucr.; gallinæ, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ungstut; qwiga:</text:span></text:span> cæsis de more j-is; formosa j., Vg.; votiva, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Yngling, jungfru:</text:span></text:span> te matres suis metuunt j-is, Hor.; Graja, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭvĕnesco</text:span>, (vĕnui), 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bli stor, wäxa upp:</text:span></text:span> vitulus, Hor.; rosa, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bli ung på nytt, föryngras:</text:span></text:span> Pylius, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭvĕnix</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūnix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Qwiga:</text:span></text:span> recipit se ad stabulum, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭvĕnor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bete sig som en ungherre (junker), sprätta:</text:span> Fauni ne nimium j-entur teneris versibus neve immunda crepent dicta, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭventa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ungdom:</text:span></text:span> non ego hoc ferrem calidus j-ā; imbellis, Hor.; membra decora j-ā; audax j-ā, Vg.; senilis, Pn.; pro j-a et errore filii veniam precor, T. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">de unge:</text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭventas</text:span>, ātis <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ungdom:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> Lucr.; fugit j., Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personificerad = ungdomens gudinna:</text:span> ludi J-is; J. pocula diis ministrat (Hebe), C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jŭventus</text:span>, ūtis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ungdomsålder, ungdom, ungdomskraft:</text:span></text:span> ibi j-em suam exercuit, Sa.; ea, quæ j-e geruntur et viribus, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">collectivt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ungdom</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">de unge:</text:span></text:span> omnis j. eo convenerat, Cs.; j. pæne dediscebat discendo; erudire j-em laboribus, C.<text:span text:style-name="T2">;</text:span> erant in j-e Romana adolescentes aliquot; hoc tibi Romana j. indicimus bellum, L.; Trojana j., Vg.; Antinoique in cute curanda plus æquo operata j., Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jŭvo,</text:span> jūvi, jūtum (Sa.; <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. fut.</text:span> juvaturus, Sa. Jug. 47. Pn. ep.), 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hjelpa, bistå:</text:span></text:span> alqm auxilio, consilio; num Sp. Mælium amici debuerunt j-re?; in hominibus j-dis aut mores spectari aut fortuna solet; ne impediant divitiæ, quo minus quis j-etur, modo ne adjuvent; proscriptum j-re lex vetat, C.; alqm aliqua re, Cs., N.; avide in libertatem ruendo in servitutem lapsos j-re nolebant; ite, diis bene j-antibus; classem commeatu j., L.; auxilio tutos dimittam opibusque j-bo; nihil illos Herculis arma juvere, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gagna</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hafwa nytta af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">befordra, befrämja:</text:span></text:span> nihil me j-at, quod edo, Pt.; id j-at, si facis, Ter.; res - quibus et se possint j-re et suos; nullam eruditionem esse duxit Epicurus, nisi quæ beatæ vitæ disciplinam j-ret; Peripatetici omne, quo j-remur in vita, bonum decreverunt, C.; imbres arva j-antes, Ov.; multum j-at arva, qui frangit inertes glebas -, Vg.; facundia causam j-at, Qu.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fägna, förnöja, glädja, hugna;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i synn. impersonelt:</text:span> aures j-antur, C.; non me j-at vita invisa civibus, L.; Martem j-at clamor galeæque leves, Hor.; (si tibi ita j-at, vale, Pt. d. l.); te esse hilari animo valde <text:soft-page-break/>me j-at; juvit me, humanitatem tuam tibi profuisse, C.; forsan et hæc olim meminisse j-bit, Vg.; sunt, quos curriculo pulverem Olympicum collegisse j-at; j-at immemorata ferentem ingenuis oculisque legi manibusque teneri, Hor.; me j-et in gremio doctæ legisse puellæ, Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūcundus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(jocundus), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: (in utroque, et in animo et in corpore, dicitur juvare ex eoque j-um dicitur, C.):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hugnelig, fägnesam, glädjande, ljuf, behaglig, omtyckt:</text:span></text:span> est mihi j-a in malis et grata in dolore vestra erga me voluntas; literæ; memoria præteritorum malorum; vicissitudine studiorum nihil j-ius; comes populo carus et j., C.; is est ei j., N.; nihil ego prætulerim j-o sanus amico, Hor.; o jocunda quies, primo quum testis amori adfueram vestris conscius in lacrimis, Ppt.; error, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nöjsam, roande, rolig, treflig, underhållande:</text:span></text:span> virtus ista non j-a, sed tamen grata <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tacknämlig);</text:span> in omni sermone affabilis et j.; j-um auditu cognituque, C. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för sinnena </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Angenäm, behaglig:</text:span></text:span> agri j-i; odor suavis et j.; C.; sapor, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūcunde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Angenämt; nöjsamt, trefligt; ljufligt, med god smak:</text:span></text:span> vivere; cum remissis j. vivere, cum tristibus severe; narrare, C.; coenam j. producere, Hor.; bibere j-ius, C.; olet, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jūcundĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Angenämhet; känsla af behag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">nöje:</text:span></text:span> vitæ j.; j-e quadam perfundi; dare se j-i, C.; j-e permulceri, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trefnad, treflighet, angenämt sätt:</text:span></text:span> agri; ea erat in homine j. et tantus in jocando lepos, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injūcundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Obehaglig, otreflig:</text:span></text:span> labor nobis minime i., C.; adversus alqm <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(barsk),</text:span> T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injūcunde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: agi, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Injūcundĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: oratio habet i-em, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Perjūcundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Högst nöjsam, underhållande, angenäm:</text:span></text:span> disputatio, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Perjūcunde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Adjŭvo</text:span>, jūvi, jūtum (<text:span text:style-name="T2">part. fut.</text:span> adjuvaturus, Petr.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanligt är</text:span> adjuturus, C., L. XXI. 50. 9.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Kühnast, die Hauptpunkte der livian. Syntax</text:span> p. 40.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Neue,</text:span> II. p. 459), 1.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med personl. obj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bistå, understödja, hjelpa, gagna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (stärka):</text:span> comiter aliquem; fortes fortuna; alqm aliqua re, in aliqua re, Ter.; vicinum in percipiendis fructibus; juventutem et maxime rempublicam consilio et prudentia quam plurimum a-re; alqm ad colendam virtutem; nihil te a-at judicium Neronis; hesterna disputatione (magnopere) a-tus sum, C.; ad hanc spem multum a-bat eos (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i detta hopp styrkte dem),</text:span> quod Liger ex nivibus creverat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det att),</text:span> Cs.; a-at (eum) et magna proclamat voce Diores, Vg.<text:line-break/>2.<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hjelpa till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med ngt,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquid</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wara till hjelp, gagn, nytta:</text:span></text:span> si quid ego adju(v)ero, ecquid erit præmi?, Enn. ap. C.; ne impediant divitiæ, modo ne a-ent; solitudo alqd a-at; si tempora a-<text:soft-page-break/>bunt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(omständigheterna göra sitt till -),</text:span> mutationem facilius faciemus, C.; Boji quod nullo studio agebant, non multum a-bant, Cs.; gloria in rebus administrandis plurimum a-at, C.; a-at hoc quoque, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T2">rem</text:span> a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Främja, befrämja, befordra, understödja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en sak:</text:span> spero, id a-turos deos, Ter.; errorem; delectum; amicorum voluntates; lacrimis suis mærorem orationis, C.; rem proclinatam, Cs.; ignem, L.; formam curā, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. a. <text:span text:style-name="T2">ad aliquid</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara af nytta, förhjelpa, bidraga till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> honos et gloria a-ant aliquantum quum ad cetera, tum ad amicitias comparandas C.; ad eam rem humilitas multum a-at, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Adjūmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hjelpmedel, befordringsmedel, medel; hjelp:</text:span></text:span> externa et adventicia; a natura a-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(anlag, egenskaper, s. göra skicklig till)</text:span> rerum gerendarum habere; ab aliqua re petere a-a rei; ajunt, præsidii a-ique causa amicitias esse expetendas; esse alicui a-o ad victoriam, in causis; ad rem afferre aliquantum a-i, C.; a-a ignaviæ tollere, Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Adjūto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hjelpa, hjelpa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">befordra:</text:span></text:span> alqm; funus; alicui alqd; id, amabo, a-a me, quo fiat facilius, Ter. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Adjūtor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: Pacuv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Adjūtābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hjelpande, hjelprik:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Adjūtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Adjūtrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hjelpare, -rinna, befrämjare, understödjare, medhjelpare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (biträde):</text:span> his a-tor contra patriam inventus est nemo: itaque mortem sibi uterque conscivit; a. meus et monitor; honoris; his obsoletis floret Epicurus ejusdem fere a. auctorque sententiæ; a-em esse ad injuriam; habere alqm a-em ad bene faciendum; a-em esse alicui in aliqua re; te a-re hoc feci; a. imperii, negotiorum publicorum, C.; is a. consuli datur, N.; a. (rhetoris = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">biträde, hjelp-lärare),</text:span> Qu.; industriæ a-ix; alicui in peccatis a-cem esse, Ter.; assentatio, vitiorum a-ix, procul amoveatur, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Adjūtōrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hjelpmedel, biträde, hjelp:</text:span></text:span> senectutis, Col.; juris; egere, uti a-o, Qu.; trahere alqm in a-um belli, Vell.; is fecit ei in rem a-um, Poll. ap. Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">(<text:span text:style-name="T3">Adjūtus</text:span>), <text:span text:style-name="T2">abl.</text:span> u: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hjelp:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dējŭvo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lemna ohulpen; swika:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Præjŭvo</text:span>, jūvi, 1.: fidem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(credit)</text:span> patris præjuvisse (videbatur) (ἁπαξ λεγ.; ”juvisse antequam rueret”, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Orelli;</text:span> alii conj.: parum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> precio juvisse), T. Hist. III. 65.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Juxta, Juxtim <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Jungo, Jugum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I</text:span>xīon, ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ixīŏnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ixīŏnĭdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">son af I.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Bokstafwen</text:span> K <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">brukades i lat. skrift endast såsom abbreviation (ss.</text:span> = Kæso, Kalendæ, Kalumnia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">samt i namnet</text:span> Karthago): aliæ literæ redundant, ut K, quæ et ipsa quorundam nominum nota est; Qu. I. 4. 9.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Koppa,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bokstaf i det gamla grekiska alphabetet, motswarande latinets</text:span> Q.: Koppa similis nostræ Q. effectu specieque, nisi quod paulum a nostris obliquatur, apud Græcos nunc tantum in numero <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ss. siffra</text:span> 90) manet, Qu. I. 4. 9.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. taltecken = 50.; ss. abbreviation för namn</text:span> = Lucius.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Labasco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Labo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>abdăcus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăbea,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> labium, labrum, lambo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Läpp:</text:span></text:span> ad l-eas referre tibias, Pt.; postrema l-ia, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbeo</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som har stora läppar:</text:span> Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">n. pr.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbeōsus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Storläppig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med tjocka läppar:</text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>abeātes, ium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Labeātæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslag norr om Macedonien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Labeātis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A. f.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Labecula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Labes, Lābor.<text:line-break/>Labefacio, Labefact . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Labo.<text:line-break/>Labellum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Labrum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Labrum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">under</text:span> Lavo. <text:line-break/>Labeo, -beosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Labea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ăbĕrius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lăbĕriānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Labes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lābor.<text:line-break/>Labia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Labea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ăbīci, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Latium.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lăbīcānus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lăvīcānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ābiēnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lābiēniānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Labilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lābor.<text:line-break/>Labiosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Labea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăbium,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Läpp:</text:span></text:span> demissis l-is, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăbo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Luta till fall, wackla, wagga:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> signum (statua) nulla ex parte, C.; genua; janua; juncturæ (tabulatorum) l-antes, Vg.; pedes dubii; naves instabiles sine justo pondere, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> partes reipublicæ ægræ et l-antes, C.; l-antem populi Romani fortunam sustinere; memoria l-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(slår fel);</text:span> l-at causa decemvirorum, L.; sermone l-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stamma),</text:span> Pn.; spiritus l-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tager af),</text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om l. till modet, i tänkesätt l. beslut: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wackla:</text:span></text:span> cohortes l-re dicuntur; l-amus mutamusque sententiam; consilium meum l-at, C.; animi; socii, L.; corda, Vg.; l-antes patres (Regulus) firmavit, Hor.; <text:soft-page-break/>spes l-at metu, Ov.; l-antem ordinem (senatum) confirmavit Catonis oratio, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbasco</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Lăbascor, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.,</text:span> Varr. ap. Non.), ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Börja wackla,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i eg. och oeg. men.:</text:span> crebro quod tunditur ictu, vincitur - atque l-it, Lucr.; salvus sum, l-it <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gifwer tappt),</text:span> Pt.; l-it victus uno verbo, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbĕfăcio</text:span>, fēci, factum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> - (labefio) factus, fieri: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra wacklande, komma att wackla, rubba, skaka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> dentes alicui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(slå lösa),</text:span> Ter.; pars muri l-ta, Cs.; munimenta concussu arietis labefieri, Sen.; l-ta movet robustus jugera (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jordtorfwor),</text:span> Vg.; arbor ictibus innumeris l-ta corruit, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra wacklande, bringa på fall:</text:span></text:span> jura plebis, L.; fidem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(crediten),</text:span> Su.; hunc Sejani amicitia, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tänkesätt, sinne, mod: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra wacklande, rubba:</text:span></text:span> hunc nulla usquam vis, nullæ minæ, nulla invidia l-fecit, C.; animum l-tus amore, Vg.; classiarios l-re, T. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kroppsligen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förderfwa, -swaga:</text:span></text:span> membra l-ta liquescunt, Lucr.; contagione aliquem, Col.; corpora - æstus impatientia, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbĕfactio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: al. - factatio, q. v.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbĕfacto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Komma att wackla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (bringa på fall); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skaka lös, rubba:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> vectibus signum l-re conantur; ruere illa non possunt, ut non hæc eodem l-ata motu concidant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i bild),</text:span> C.; animam sedibus intus, Lucr.; onus ventris gravidi, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> astute ab aliquo l-ri, Ter.; rempublicam; fundamenta reipublicæ; leges ac jura; urbes et vitas hominum malitia; conspirationem bonorum perfringere et l.; superior annus aratores l-verat, proximus everterat, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngns öfwertygelse </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wacklande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wederlägga); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rubba</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngns trohet:</text:span> opinionem alicujus; oratio mea l-atur; fidem alicujus pretio, C.; aliquam munere, Catl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbĕfactātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skakning, rubbning:</text:span></text:span> Pn., Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collăbasco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wackla med:</text:span></text:span> si res labet, itidem amici c-unt, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collăbefīo</text:span>, factus, fieri: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">helt och hållet bringas att </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wackla, wagga, (upplösas):</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. naves totæ, Cs.; omnia - igni c-ta, Lucr. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Störtas:</text:span></text:span> testulā (ɔ: ostracismo): N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collăbĕfacto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bringa att wackla; upplösa, smälta:</text:span></text:span> vastum onus motu, Ov.; aurum æstu c-tum, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illăbĕfactus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Orubbad, -lig:</text:span></text:span> concordia: Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lābor,</text:span> lapsus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glida, halka:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">glida, skjuta </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fram, hän,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om hwarje jemnt fortskridande rörelse (s. ej sker i steg), ss. swäfwa, fara, flyga, kräla, rinna, simma:</text:span> sidera - l-untur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sw.: röra sig, wandra),</text:span> C.; cæli l-entia signa, Lucr.; pennis l-i; flumina sub terra, Vg.; l-untur altis ripis aquæ; l-itur et l-etur in <text:soft-page-break/>omne ævum (amnis), Hor.; l-itur uncta carina, Enn.; per æquora; medio amne, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">glida, swäfwa, halka, slinta, sjunka, segna, digna, rasa </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ned,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> omkull, utföre (falla):</text:span> arma ipsa l-sa (al.: delapsa) de manibus ceciderunt; aliquis l-sus de cælo; in rivo labi C.; Jovis ales æthere l-sa; levi sanguine l-itur infelix Nisus; per funem demissum l-si (de equo Trojano); stella de cælo l-sa; turris l-a repente ruinam trahit, Vg.; l-ens equo Parthus; humor et in genas furtim l-itur, Hor.; ex oculis guttæ; domus l-sura, Ov.; arma super corpus moribundi, L.; ex rupe l-sus, Ct.; somno l-si ocelli, Ppt. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. l. oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rent bildliga uttryck: glida hän, bort, undan, utföre, ned:</text:span> vitia sunt in lubrico incitataque semel proclivi l-untur sustinerique nullo modo possunt; res proclivius ad perniciem, quum semel coepit, l-itur; l-sa consuetudo deflexit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(småningom glidit af, från)</text:span> de via; verba proclivius; circuitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(period),</text:span> C.; (sequatur animo) velut desidentes primo mores, deinde ut magis magisque l-si sint <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(glidit utföre),</text:span> L.; dolor l-sus ad ossa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(smyger sig på),</text:span> Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(småningom) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwergå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ett tillstånd (en åsigt), wanl. till ett sämre, sål. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förfalla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till -:</text:span> l-or eo, ut assentiar Epicuro; l-or ad eos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwergår till deras parti);</text:span> mores l-si ad mollitiam, C.; in vitium, Hor.; in adulationem, T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i talet glida, låta sig föras bort, d. ä. förirra sig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afwika</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från ämnet:</text:span> l-or longius: ad propositum revertar, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tid, saker, tillstånd, förhållanden: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förgå, förrinna; förfalla, råka i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">på förfall, sjunka:</text:span></text:span> tot jam l-entibus annis; dies l-itur, Vg.; tempora l-untur tacitisque senescimus annis; ætas l-itur, Ov.; cetera nasci, occidere, fluere, labi, nec diutius esse uno eodemque statu, C.; generis l-si <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förminskade)</text:span> sarciunt ruinas (apes); res l-sæ, Vg.; l-ente disciplina; res (decemviratus) l-sa est, L.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mißtaga sig, taga fel, fela</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (döma, uttrycka sig, handla orätt):</text:span> l-i, errare, nescire, decipi et turpe et malum ducimus; consilio; opinione; in officio; imprudentiā in aliqua re; non cupiditate aut ambitione, sed opinione officii; in minimis tenuissimisque rebus, C.; spe l-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gå miste om -),</text:span> Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lābes</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fall:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: fall, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ras, instörtande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jordfall):</text:span> agri Privernatis; multis locis l-es factæ sunt terræque desederunt, C.; dextra pars l-e terræ in aliquantum altitudinis derupta erat, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>α. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Begynnelse, orsak</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till en olycka:</text:span> hinc <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> mihi prima mali, Vg.; hujus mali l. ex Etruria Romam velut contagione morbi penetravit, L.<text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förderf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ruin), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">undergång:</text:span></text:span> innocentiæ l. et ruina; reipublicæ l. et flamma; provinciæ l. et pernicies, C.; corporis, Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fläck</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. faller, stänker på ngt; stänk?), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">smutsfläck, smitta:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> atramenta tractata notam l-emque remittunt, Hor.; sine l-e toga, Ov. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg., moralisk mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fläck,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> orenlighet, smitta, pestfläck, skamfläck (i själen, på wandel, rykte o. s. w.):</text:span> animi l. nec diuturnitate evanescere nec amnibus ullis elui potest; l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sw. med </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">annan bild: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sår)</text:span></text:span> conscientiæ, C.; mores carent l-e, Ov.; inferre integris l-em; aspergere alqm l-e; seculi l. est virtuti invidere; l-em sceleris relinquere in familia, C.; aut conficti aut admissi criminis l-em apud meos inventurus -, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lābēcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: alicui l-am (verbis) aspergere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slipprig:</text:span></text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedstörtande:</text:span></text:span> Acc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lapsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">glidande ned, utföre:</text:span> hæc in malis proclivitas nominetur, ut significet l-em, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lapso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snafwa, slinta, halka:</text:span></text:span> equus, Ter.; in sanguine l., Vg. - verba uvida et l-antia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. tanklöst undfalla ngn, tanklösa),</text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lapsus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glidning, glidande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om hwarje jemn rörelse: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rullande, swäfwande, flygt, krälande, slingrande, rinnande:</text:span></text:span> l-us rotarum subjicimus equo (Trojano), Vg.; stellæ certo l-u <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lopp)</text:span> feruntur; volucrum; vitem serpentem multiplici l-u et erratico ars agricolarum coërcet; lacus emissus l-u <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fart)</text:span> et cursu suo ad mare profluit, C.; medio volvuntur sidera l-u; dracones ad delubra l-u effugiunt, Vg.; Orpheus rapidos fluminum l-us <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lopp)</text:span> moratus, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedglidande, fall:</text:span></text:span> scalarum, Pn.; a l-u se sustinere; terræ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jordras),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mißtag, förirring:</text:span></text:span> multi sunt variique populares l-us <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sätt att stöta folket);</text:span> continere temeritatem a l-u, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allābor</text:span>, lapsus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glida,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> flyta, strömma, flyga, slingra sig, rinna, sjunka; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">till:</text:span></text:span> humor a-sus extrinsecus, C.; mare crescenti a-itur æstu, Vg.; anguis ad exta, L.; sagitta; fama ad aures, Vg.; et tandem Euboicis Curetum a-imur oris, Vg.; genibus alicujus a., Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allapsus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">slingrande anfall:</text:span> serpentis a-um timere, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collābor</text:span>, lapsus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Falla, störta, sjunka tillsammans:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om döda ting:</text:span> moenia ruinā c-sa, C.; urbes motu terræ, T.; ædes vetustate, Su.; ossa morbo, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sjunka, segna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ned:</text:span> ferro c-sa Dido, Vg.; dolore, Ov.; saxo ictus, Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlābor</text:span>, lapsus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glida ned, hän:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men. = glida, swäfwa, rinna, falla ned; råka hän:</text:span> de cælo in terram; signum cælo d-sum; in flumen d.; ex utraque tecti parte aqua d-itur, C.; ex equo, L.; equo, Cs., Vg.; flumen in mare, Hor.; medios d-sus in hostes, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om ofriwillig öfwergång till ngt sämre) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sjunka ned; förirra sig till; falla, råka i, förfalla till:</text:span></text:span> oratio a sapientium amicitiis ad vulgares familiaritates; in morbum; in vitium; in aliquam turpitudinem; in difficultates; in insidias, C.; ad impatientiam, T. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Föras, dragas hän, hänföras, öfwergå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt:</text:span> ad æquitatem; in sermonem; in idem genus; in istum sermonem; eo, illuc, ut -; ad Clodiam (i. e. ad emenda prædia C-æ), C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Härflyta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> utweckla sig:</text:span> ab his - plura genera d-sa sunt, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlapsus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlābor</text:span>, lapsus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om fasta ämnen) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Falla åtskils, itu, i sönder; ramla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om byggnader):</text:span> ædem vetustate d-sam refecit; navis putris d-itur, L.; vestis situ, Col.; fax in cinerem d-sa, Hor. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bild.: -</text:span> mundus ita aptus est, - ut hic ornatus nunquam d-sus occidat, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sönderflyta, upplösa sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i watten; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">dela, sprida sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om watten l. lågor):</text:span> aqua conglaciata frigoribus - calore admixto se d-sa diffundit, C.; Proteus in aquas, Vg.; Fibrenus rapide d-sus rursus in unum confunditur, C.; Vulcano per veterem culinam d-so, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om menniskor (härar o. s. w.): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skingra sig, förskingras, förströs, upplösa sig, fly</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (åt skilda håll):</text:span> multitudo in agros, ad prædam; ab ordinibus hostes, L.; exercitus cito, Sa.; deserto bello ad sua tuenda d-i; domum, Js.; alicui, Vfl.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om förmögenhet, samhällen och deras ordning, och om abstracta subj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förskingras, upplösas, förrinna, förswinna, -gå:</text:span></text:span> male parta male d-untur, C.; concordiā res parvæ crescunt, discordiā maximæ d-untur, Sa.; vectigalia negligentiā, L.; - ut præclarissime constituta respublica d-retur; omnia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(samhällsband, -förhållanden),</text:span> quæ d-sa fluxerunt, severius vincienda sunt; simul ac fortuna d-sa est, devolant omnes, C.; tempus; vis corporis et alia hujusmodi brevi d-untur, Sa.; bella, Js.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om det, s. i tanken l. minnet sammanhålles: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förflyga:</text:span></text:span> intento opus est animo, ne omnia d-antur, si unum diffugerit; ea meā memoriā d-untur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlābĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skör, lös:</text:span></text:span> vestis: Pn. .</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlābor</text:span>, lapsus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glida, slinta, halka undan, ut; falla ut:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> anguilla - e-itur, Pt.; alqd e manibus, ex utero, C.; anguis ex columna lignea e-sus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. krälat fram),</text:span> L.; tabellæ manibus e-sæ sunt, Ov.; liber seni, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rent bildl. uttryck:</text:span> mihi causa e-sa est (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">segren i målet frånrycktes mig); -</text:span> si hæc <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dessa företag)</text:span> e-sa de manibus nostris in (proximum) annum reciderint -; is status civitatis nobis de manibus e-sus est, C.; tibi vita imperfecta e-sa est, Lucr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undfly, undkomma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i eg. och oeg. men.), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">gå fri,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> isynn. från laga dom och straff):</text:span> ex alicujus manibus ac ferro, C.; ex proelio, Cs.; mediis e-sus Achivis; de cæde; telis, Vg.; inter tela et gladios, L.; ex criminibus; ex judicio; omni suspicione; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.:</text:span> Tito fratre e-sus erat (nota censoria); reus e-sus est, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gå ur</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngns sinne l. minne, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">undfalla, förflyga, förswinna:</text:span></text:span> omnis assensio illa; memoriā alqd, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Falla, råka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i, förfalla till:</text:span> in servitutem, L.; in pravum, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illābor</text:span>, lapsus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glida, flyta in:</text:span></text:span> urbi i-itur (rotis equus Trojanus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rullar in),</text:span> Vg.; in stomachum alqd, C.; amni alqd, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Falla, störta på,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer:</text:span> si fractus i-atur orbis (justo viro), <text:soft-page-break/>impavidum feriant ruinæ, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tränga in till, sänka sig ned</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ngns sinnen l. sinne:</text:span> ad sensus; in animos, C.; animis i-ere nostris, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illapsus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: humoris, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Interlābor</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rinna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tränga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> in </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">emellan:</text:span></text:span> inter enim labentur aquæ, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Perlābor</text:span>, lapsus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glida, fara öfwer, igenom:</text:span></text:span> levibus rotis summas p-itur undas, Vg.; volucris auras, Tib.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tränga, hinna fram</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> a Græcis p-sus ad nos et usque ad Oceanum Hercules, C.; ad nos vix tenuis famæ p-itur aura, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prælābor</text:span>, lapsus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glida, flyta, ila förut, förbi:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> piscis, C.; flumina, Vg.; Tibris moenia, Luc.; in insulam - gladiatores navibus, Germani nando p-bantur, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> tempus, Col.; ira men tem, Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Præterlābor</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(glida), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (strömma, segla) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förbi:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> Tibris tumulum Marcelli; tellurem Ausoniam pelago p-are necesse est, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> ante p-itur (definitio aures), quam percepta est, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōlābor</text:span>, lapsus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glida, snafwa, falla framåt, framstupa:</text:span></text:span> serpens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(krälar fram),</text:span> C.; elephanti - clunibus subsidentes p-bantur; velut si p-sus cecidisset, terram osculo tetigit; ex equo; equus regem per caput p-sum effudit, L.; equus, Ppt.; ex arbore, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gå långt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">widt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i handling l. framställning; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utswäfwa; låta sig dragas, föras, lockas, ledas:</text:span></text:span> longius p-sus sum, quam ratio judicii postulabat; libenter ad istam orationem tecum p-rer; verbum a cupiditate p-sum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(framlockadt; s. är en oförsigtig yttring af -)</text:span> C.; in misericordiam; cupiditate regni, L.; dites olim familiæ - studio magnificentiæ p-bantur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utswäfwade i -),</text:span> T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förgå sig:</text:span></text:span> timore in multis rebus, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förirra sig; falla, sjunka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i moraliskt l. yttre hänseende, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">urarta, förfalla, bringas på fall:</text:span></text:span> his temporibus juventus ita p-sa est, ut omnium opibus coërcenda et refrenanda sit; huc mulieris lubido p-sa est, ut -, C.; rem p-sam negligentiā consulis restituit, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōlapsio</text:span>, ōnis. <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snafwande, fall:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕlābor</text:span>, lapsus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glida, strömma, swäfwa, falla tillbaka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> unda, Vg.; rivi montibus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppåt b.),</text:span> Hor.; Eurydice r-sa est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(swäfwade tillbaka till underjorden),</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> in Aristippi furtim præcepta r-or; mens et sonus r-sus est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(återkom hos Ulyssis till swin förwandlade folk),</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sublābor</text:span>, lapsus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glida, smyga sig under, inunder, in:</text:span></text:span> lues; vetustas, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glida, sjunka undan; falla;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förswinna, -gå:</text:span></text:span> ex illo (tempore) fluere ac retro s-sa referri spes Danaûm, Vg.; vetustate ædificia s-sa, Pn.; memoria, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Subterlābor</text:span>, lapsus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(glida), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Strömma under:</text:span></text:span> fluctūs Arethusa; muros aqua, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sŭperlābor</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span> sidera alqm <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wandra öfwer),</text:span> Sen. - navem celeritate sua s-entem rostro ferire non poterant, L. d. l. (alii Edd.: subterlabentem = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">undflyende,</text:span> alii c-e sua prælabentem).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Translābor</text:span>, lapsus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ila framom:</text:span></text:span> Cd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăbor</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăbos,</text:span> ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Arbete, möda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom handling: arbete, med l. utan den bibetydelse s. ligger i möda, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">beswär, ansträngning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (strapas):</text:span> l. est functio quædam vel animi vel corporis gravioris operis et muneris; l-es pacis ac belli; summos l-es diurnos nocturnosque domi militiæque suscipere; senibus l-es corporis minuendi; iniens ætas in l-e exercenda est; infinitus rerum forensium l.; l. necessarius, utilis, magnus, multus, puerilis; sine ullo l-e et contentione vitam traducere; l. nobis minime injucundus; l-em subire, capere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(åtaga sig),</text:span> ferre, perferre, sustinere, tolerare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utstå),</text:span> insumere in rem, in re ponere, consumere, sibi sumere; l-bus perfungi; alicui imponere; frangere se l-bus; l-em alicujus levare, mitigare; quantum potes l-e contendere, si discendi l. est potius, quam voluptas, tantum fac ut efficias, C.; l. remigandi; l-i succumbere; ex l-e (proelii) se reficere; cohortes præsidio castris relictæ et ab l-e intritæ; l-em aut belli aut fugæ ferre non poterat, Cs.; res est magni, majoris l-is; vastus l., L.; Dido operum l-em partibus æquabat justis; l. improbus omnia vincit, Vg.; adire l-es, N., Vg.; l-um præmia; animi capitisque l.; Hercules fatali l-e portenta subegit; limæ l., Hor.; - quem l-or assiduus vicino terreat hoste, Tib.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. egenskap = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Arbetsamhet:</text:span></text:span> in eo fuit tantus l., ut naturæ impedimenta diligentiā superaret, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fulländadt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Arbete, werk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (poet.):</text:span> rapidus torrens sternit sata læta boumque l-es, Vg.; lamentamur, non apparere l-es nostros et tenui deducta poēmata filo, Hor.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wedermöda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lidande, nöd, wånda, strapas:</text:span></text:span> accrescit l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(den sjukes),</text:span> Pt.; ejus benevolentiam vel in l-e meo vel in honore perspexi; supersedere itineris l-e, C.; Iliaci l-es; supremus Trojæ l., Vg.; Lucinæ l-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(barnsnöd),</text:span> Vg.; solis, lunæ l-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sol-, månförmörkelser),</text:span> Vg., l-es a convivio, T.; nervorum, Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbōrĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. bär l. utstår mödor; s. bringar arbet e:</text:span> Hercules, Ov.; currus Auroræ, St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbōriōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Arbetsam, sträfsam, oförtruten:</text:span></text:span> homo; l-simus arator, C.; fuit disertus, impiger, l., N.; bos l-simus hominis socius in agricultura, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerhopad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af arbete, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">nedtryckt af beswärligheter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lidanden; lidande:</text:span></text:span> quid nobis duobus l-ius?; qui ex morbi gravitate dolores perferunt, l-os dicere solemus, C.; Ulixes, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Beswärlig, mödosam, full af mödor:</text:span></text:span> l-a exercitatio corporis; nihil provinciā l-ius; vitæ ratio, C.; fabula, Ter.; id utrum ei fuerit l-ius an gloriosius, (nescio), N.; operum longe maximum et l-simum, L.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbōriōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med arbete, ansträngning, beswär; oförtrutet; beswärligt:</text:span></text:span> docere iracundius et l-ius; accusare diligentissime et l-sime, C.; jus dicere l-sime et severissime, Su.; l. est alicui, Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbōro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Arbeta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T2">intr.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om kroppsliga l. andliga sysslor: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">arbeta, hafwa möda; anstränga, möda sig:</text:span></text:span> rastros appone: ne l-ra, Ter.; aliud est dolere, aliud l-re. Quum varices secabantur C. Mario, dolebat: quum æstu magno ducebat agmen, l-bat; si delectamur, quum scribimus, quis est tam invidus, qui ab eo nos deducat: sin l-amus, quis et cet.?; alicui serere, impendere, l-re; vellem hoc esset l-re, C.; sudare multum frustraque l-re, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T2">transit.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>aa. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Arbeta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillwerka,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> genom arbete </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">frambringa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bereda:</text:span></text:span> manus alqd, Hor.; arte l-tæ vestes, Vg.; frumentum ceterosque fructus, T.; alicui arma, St.; libri l-ti, Mt.<text:line-break/>bb. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomarbeta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utstå, genomgå:</text:span></text:span> vita l-ta, St.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra sig möda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">omak;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">arbeta för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> någon = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lägga sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ut för någon</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">pro aliquo</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sträfwa, göra sig beswär, bekymmer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngt, (i handling) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">låta sig angeläget wara,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> o. s. w.:</text:span> pro bonis viris; pro salute alicujus; amici causa; de alicujus re non minus, quam de sua; meæ curæ ac vigiliæ ad id l-ant; non in eo nunc l-o, C.; in rem, circa rem, Qu.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> ut <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> ne <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. indirect frågesats:</text:span> l-vi, ut vos decerneretis; nihil l-o, nisi ut salvus sis; ea ne frustra subierim, valde l-o; Græci numquam l-ant, quomodo probent, quod dicant, C.; id se contendere ac l-re, ne ea, quæ dixissent, enunciarentur, Cs.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">inf.</text:span>: brevis esse l-o: obscurus fio, Hor.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i sinnet) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara bekymrad, ängslig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bry sig om</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i synn. med negation = ej fråga efter), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wara angelägen, mån om:</text:span></text:span> non l-at de pecunia; de fama; de verbo; de quibus antea l-bam, nunc sum animo æquissimo; l-o idem, quod tu; noli l-re, quod -; quem ad modum socii tractentur, non l-atis; ampulla sit necne sit, quis - l-et?, C.; quærere de tanta re non l-bant, N.; ubi Claudius - militet, scire l-o, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dragas, kämpa med, beswäras</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af wedermöda l. plåga:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i kroppsligt (mechaniskt l. physiskt) hänseende: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara nedtyngd, betungad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sucka under tyngden af -), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kämpa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lida,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wara </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ansatt, anfäktas, plågas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hafwa ondt; wåndas, wara sjuk</text:span></text:span> [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">aliqua re,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om orsaken till plågan, l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">ex</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i)</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">aliqua re</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om den del af kroppen, s. lider</text:span>)]: vix sustinent onus (nivis) silvæ l-antes; l-ant aquilonibus querceta, Hor.; ramus, Ov.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">så bildl.:</text:span> res eo crevit, ut jam magnitudine l-et sua <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(suckar under, knappt förmår uppbära, lider af),</text:span> L.; dolore, Ter.; sine febri; artus l-ant; morbo l., C.; fame; frigore, Col.; quartanā; torminibus, Pn.; ex <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i)</text:span> intestinis; ex pedibus; ex renibus, C.; utero puellæ, Hor. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i andra hänseenden: absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara i betryck, trångmål, nöd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i klämman); om handlingar: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">gå trögt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">med nöd, beswär</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (stå hårdt)</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="T2">aliqua re</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">ex aliqua re</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lida, hafwa beswär, olägenhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wara i förlägenhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ansättas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af l. wara </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utsatt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för:</text:span> succurrere l-antibus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i drabbning),</text:span> Sa.; l-antibus tertiam aciem subsidio misit; nostri l-bant et gravius premebantur, Cs.; veritatem l-re sæpe ajunt, exstingui <text:soft-page-break/>nunquam, L.; porrectio digitorum propter molles commissuras nullo in motu l-at; spiritus l-at, C.; oratio quasi l-at, Qu.; domestica crudelitate; ita respublica ex vobis, vos ex invidia minus l-aretis; ex inscitia; ex desiderio; quem ad modum illa minora opera facere discat, non l-bit, C.; ex ære alieno; a re frumentaria, Cs.; fenore; odio; pestilentiā (civitas); vitiis; annona, L.; jam contento, jam laxo fune l-at, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allăbōro</text:span> <text:line-break/>(adlăbōro), 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Arbeta, hjelpa till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med:</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">genom arbete l. beswär lägga till:</text:span> simplici myrto (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>) nihil a-es, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlăbōro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Arbeta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med, på, i, för; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">anwända arbete</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">omsorg, sträfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt l. för ett mål</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">in re</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bemöda, beflita sig, winnlägga sig om:</text:span></text:span> quod est tam asperum saxetum, in quo agricolarum cultus non e-et?; in petitione Milonis mihi est non solum contentione, sed etiam dimicatione e-dum; res digna, in qua e-etur; desudare et e-re in aliqua re; ii non aliqua in re una separatim e-arunt, (sed omnia comprehenderunt); ad alicujus judicium e.; e-bo, ut prosim, ut omnes intelligant -; in eo quoque debeo e-re, ut sint labore meo doctiores cives, C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">inf.</text:span>: facere - e-vit, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">intr.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med framgång </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Arbeta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">arbeta sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt, med arbete (sträfwa) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">winna, utwerka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (tillkämpa sig), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förwärfwa, bereda:</text:span></text:span> id Græcorum nemini contigit, ut idem in utroque e-aret; ut cogitata præclare eloqui possent, nonnulli - e-verunt; id ejus causa e-vi; quidquid e-ri et effici potest ad benevolentiam conciliandam -; omne curriculum industriæ meæ in foro, in curia, in causis civilibus e-tum est, C.; dulcem e-bunt saporem, Hor.; imperium e-tum a parentibus, Js.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">genom arbete </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fullkomna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">, (sorgfälligt, stundom = med allt för sorgfällig, pedantisk omsorg) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utarbeta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (isynn. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pf. part.</text:span>): oratio diligenter e-ta; versus ornati e-tique; e-ta concinnitas (= nimis el.), C.; ars e-ta, Pn.; arcessitum et e-tum, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlăbōrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utarbetning:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ĭnēlăbōrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ej utarbetad:</text:span></text:span> oratio, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illăbōro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Arbeta, göra sig beswär,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> möda med ngt:</text:span> domibus i.; ingemere agris, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illăbōrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ej bearbetad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utarbetad; utan arbete tillkommen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">frambragt:</text:span></text:span> terra, Sen.; scripta; oratio, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> = laboriosus: Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Labratus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Labrum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ābro, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hamn i Etrurien (Livorno).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Labrosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Labrum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăbrum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> labium, labea, lambo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Läpp:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> l-is primoribus, Pt.; in l-is Platonis consederunt apes, C.; superius, Cs.; admovere l-a poculis, Vg.; l-a movere, <text:soft-page-break/>comprimere, Hor.; astringere, diducere, distorquere, Qu.; - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttryck (för: befatta sig med o. s. w.):</text:span> attingere, gustare aliquid primoribus, primis l-is, C.; a summis l-is (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blott från läpparne)</text:span> venit aliquid, Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brädd, rand</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ett kärl, en graf o. d.:</text:span> doliorum, Cato; fossæ, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbellum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten läpp:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbrātus</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbrōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. har stora läppar:</text:span> Charis., Ce.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. Labrum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lavo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lābrusca,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adj.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wildt winträd; wild-drufwa:</text:span></text:span> vitis, Pn.; uva, Col.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(subst.),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lābruscum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wilddrufwa:</text:span></text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Labundus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lābor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Laburnum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags bön-buske:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăby̆rinthus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Labyrinth</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (byggnad med irrgångar i Aegypten, på Creta o. s. w.):</text:span> Vg., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăby̆rinthēus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Labyrinthisk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. är i l. sådan som i en labyrinth):</text:span> Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lāc</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. (eg. och arch.)</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lacte</text:span>, lactis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">acc.</text:span> lactem, Ap., Gell.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mjölk:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">animalisk (mjölk, di):</text:span> tam similis, quam lacte lactist, Pt.; l. nutricis; l-e ali; villa abundat l-e, caseo etc.; l-is imber, C.; l-e et pecore vivere, Cs.; pressi copia l-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ost);</text:span> l. concretum, Vg.; l-is massa coacti <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ost),</text:span> Ov.; l. vaccinum, equinum, caprinum, ovillum, suillum, bubulum, humanum, maternum, recens, pingue; l. acescit, coit, coagulatur, densatur, Pn.; - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. till beteckning af hwithet l. mild, närande föda:</text:span> una fuit labes (corporis): cetera l-is erant, Ov.; (facies candida) ut rosæ puro l-e natant folia, Ppt.; jucundioris disciplinæ l-e satiari, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">vegetabilisk mjölk, saft:</text:span> herbæ, Vg.; ficulnum, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lactes</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Småtarmar:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lactārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. ger l. innehåller mjölk:</text:span> bos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mjölkeko),</text:span> Varr., herba, Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. består af mjölk:</text:span> Lpd.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lactārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mjölkrätt:</text:span> Ce.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lactārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. tillagar sådan:</text:span> Lpd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lacteo</text:span>, ēre:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. præs.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. diar, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Diande, däggande:</text:span></text:span> puer parvus et l-ens, C.; agna, Ov.; porcus, Varr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hafwa mjölk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">saft i sig;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">part.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. adj. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">saftfull, mjölkfull:</text:span></text:span> viridia pabula, Col.; frumenta, Vg.; sata, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lactesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Få mjölk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i kroppen), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fyllas med mjölk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">saft; - öfwergå till mjölk:</text:span></text:span> asinæ prægnantes; sata, Pn.; - omnis matrum cibus l-it, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lacteus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. består af l. innehåller mjölk, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mjölk-, mjölkaktig:</text:span></text:span> liquor, Tib.; <text:soft-page-break/>sucus; herbæ, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. diar:</text:span> porcus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(digris),</text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mjölk-hwit, skär:</text:span></text:span> colla, Vg.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. om wintergatan:</text:span> orbis l., C.; circulus l., Pn.; via l-a, Ov.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ren, skär, klar:</text:span></text:span> l-a ubertas Livii, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lacteŏlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(smekord): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mjölk-, mjällhwit:</text:span></text:span> puella, Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lactĭcĭnium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mjölkrätt:</text:span></text:span> Apic. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lactĭcŏlor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mjölkhwit:</text:span></text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lacto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dia:</text:span></text:span> Aus. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">pt.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lactans</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">s. ger di, digifwande:</text:span></text:span> ubera, Lucr., Ov.; femina, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lactĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ifrigt dia:</text:span></text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ăcæna, ae, (<text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till</text:span> Laco, ōnis): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lacedæmonisk qwinna.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ăcĕdæmon, ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">staden Lacedæmon l. Sparta.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lăcĕdæmŏnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(Lăcer),</text:span> ĕra, ĕrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sönderrifwen, -sliten, -slagen, sargad, stympad, söndrig, rifwen:</text:span></text:span> l-um corpus (Metti, in diversum concitatis quadrigis), L.; serpentem seminecem saxo l-umque reliquit viator; funus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lik),</text:span> Vg.; artus; currus; puppis; vestis, Ov.; comæ, Luc.; crines, St.; corpora; exsangues aut l-os (milites) prosternere; tectorum vestigia l-a, T. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> regnum, Cd. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sargande:</text:span></text:span> l-o morsu artus divellere, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sönderslita, sönderrifwa, sarga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> l-at lacertum Largi mordax Memmius; unguibus alqd; corpus mortui; viscera morsu, C.; nautas canibus marinis; loricam revulsam alicujus valida manu l., Vg.; vestem, Ct.; ferro alqm; cornua alicujus, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sönderslita</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ngns sinne, hjerta), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fräta, plåga:</text:span></text:span> ægritudo l-at, exest animum planeque conficit; obtrectatio invidiæ l-at plerosque; hæc oratio te, si ullam partem sensus habes, l-et; l-ri mærore, dolore, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Såra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngns rykte, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">smäda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">belacka, utskämma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (-skälla):</text:span> famam alicujus, L.; existimatio l-ta, Su.; contumeliis optimum virum, C.; probris alqm, L.; sermone vulgi, T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sönderslita</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = factiskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förderfwa, -störa, utplundra;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om egendom) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förskingra:</text:span></text:span> patriam omni scelere; rempublicam; pecuniam, C.; homines fenore, lustris -, Pt., Ter.; bona patria manu, ventre, Sa.; opes, Ov.; diem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förspilla),</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcĕrābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: objicere corpus l-e morbis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(att uppfrätas),</text:span> Aus. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sönderslitning, sargande:</text:span></text:span> corporis (cruci suffixi); genarum muliebres l-es, C.; corporum, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collăcĕro</text:span>, 1.: c-atus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">alldeles söndersliten,</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlăcĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sönderslita, -stycka, -rifwa:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> feræ alqm, Catl.; dominum canes, Ov.; artus Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> animus sævitia, libidine d-atus, T.; rempublicam, C., Sa.; opes, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăcerna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">res- l. regn-</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kappa, mantel:</text:span></text:span> cum toga et calceis, nullis nec Gallicis nec l-a, C.; l-ā caput totum obscurare, Hor.; l. tegit togam, Mt.; pinguis, Juv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcernātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">klädd i</text:span> lacerna: Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lacero <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lacer.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăcerta,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcertus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ödla:</text:span></text:span> Hor., Pn., Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăcertus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en fisk (makrill):</text:span> Juv. XIV. 151.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăcertus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerarm, öfwerbog</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (serskildt ss. muskulös l. ansträngd); i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">arm:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> Milo - aspexisse l-os suos dicitur et dixisse: At hi - mortui sunt, C.; brachia apta ex validis l-is, Lucr.; brachia l-is subjecta sunt; amplecti alqm cupidis l-is, Ov.; pignus dereptum l-is; vincula excidere l-is; lævo suspensi loculos tabulamque l-o, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om kämpande bins lemmar l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">krafter:</text:span></text:span> spiculaque exacuunt rostris aptantque l-os, Vg. G. IV. 74. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttr. för kroppslig l. andlig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Styrka:</text:span></text:span> pugnare non consilio et auctoritate, sed viribus et l-is; oratoris l-i; in Lysia sunt sæpe etiam l-i, C.; populus movet l-os (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">pröfwar sin styrka),</text:span> Fl. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcertōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Armstark, -styf; bogstark:</text:span></text:span> centurio, C.; equus, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lacess . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lacio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>acĕtāni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslag i Hispanien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lacĕtānia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Lacetanien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăchănisso,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> lăchăna, ōrum = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grönsaker):</text:span> v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara slapp:</text:span></text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ăches, ētis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ăchĕsis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en af Parcerna.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lachrima <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lacrima.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ăcĭădes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är från den laciske demos i Attica:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăcĭnia</text:span>,ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stycke; flik:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tygstycke,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (näsduk, swettduk), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">klut:</text:span></text:span> servare ex mensa alqd in l-a, C.; sume l-am atque absterge sudorem tibi, Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klädesplagg, skört:</text:span></text:span> lintea l.; l-as exuere, Ap. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flik</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af mantel l. klädnad öfwerhufwud:</text:span> tenere, detinere, obtinere alqm l-ā, Pt., Su., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bildl.),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flik, stycke, frans:</text:span></text:span> brevis l. (terræ), Pn.; binæ l-æ a cervice (capræ) dependentes, Pn.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">afdelning af en hjord:</text:span> pecus in l-as distribuere, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcĭniātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">styckewis, i spridda afdelningar:</text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcĭniōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">full af flikar, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fransig;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. går i weck l. fållar; lappad, styckad:</text:span> folia; Alexandria urbs ad effigiem chlamydis orbe gyrato l-a, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med plagg l. pjaltor </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Belastad, behängd:</text:span></text:span> animi sanitas expedita <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lätt utstyrd),</text:span> imbecillitas l-a est, Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcĭniōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fransigt, krusigt:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ăcīnĭum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Stor-Grekland.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lăcīnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(Lăcio,</text:span> 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Locka:</text:span></text:span> vox obsoleta: lacit i. e. in fraudem inducit (lax enim fraus est). Inde est allicere et lacessere, et lactat, illectat, delectat, oblectat, Fs.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcesso</text:span>, sīvi, sītum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Framlocka, -mana</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med personl. obj.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i fiendtlig afsigt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utfordra, utmana, reta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (först) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">angripa, antasta:</text:span></text:span> desinat l-re, Ter.; arma, quibus l-tus, te ulcisci possis, C.; - Germanos - non recusare, si l-antur, quin armis contendant; ad l-dum et ad committendum proelium alienum esse tempus arbitrabatur, Cs.; ad pugnam l., L.; bello, ferro, injuriā, maledictis, sponsione l-re alqm, C.; bello, proelio, Cs.; jurgiis, L., Sa.; dente cruento, Hor.; irritat telis et voce l-it; missilibus et clamore, Vg. - stimulo pecudem, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i wänlig l. åtm. icke owänlig afsigt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppfordra, mana, utfordra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fordra):</text:span> epistolis alqm ad scribendum, ad scriptiones; sic igitur facies meque - scripto aliquo l-es, C.; cursuque ictuque l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till täfling i -),</text:span> Vg.; nihil supra deos l-o, Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sakl. object:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Angripa, trotsa, beröra, reta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (afficiera, kittla), träffa; med abstr. obj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fresta, pröfwa:</text:span></text:span> vindemia pluviis et ventis l-ta, Col.; pelagus carina, Hor.; æra sole l-ta, Vg.; res l-it visum, aures, nares, Lucr.; corpus fomentis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(pigga, incitera),</text:span> Sen.; pugnam, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Framlocka, reta:</text:span></text:span> sermones, C.; risum, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcessītio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utmaning:</text:span></text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illăcessītus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ej utmanad, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oantastad, ostörd:</text:span></text:span> pars Britanniæ; pax, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lacto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Locka, tjusa, förleda:</text:span></text:span> amor me, Pt., Ter.; dictis lenibus, Acc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allĭcio</text:span>, lexi, lectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Locka till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt (l. till sig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillocka,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tillwinna sig), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">winna för ngt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg., om lefwande föremål och deras sinnen, känslor:</text:span> virtus ad diligendum a-it; delectatione a. lectorem; mentes a.; benevolentiam alicujus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> alqm ad benevolentiam; oratio auditorem permulcet et a-it; multorum opes ad misericordiam; hominum studia a.; in hunc sensum beneficiis hominum a-or, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med andra obj.:</text:span> magnes ferrum ad se a-it, C.; tempus merumque a-unt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(framkallar)</text:span> somnos, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allecto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ideligen l. ifrigt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Locka till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, till sig:</text:span> ad aquam sibilo bovem, Col.; ad agrum fruendum invitat et a-at senectus; blanda ista vanitas apud eos tantummodo valet, qui ipsi illam a-ant, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allectātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lockande:</text:span></text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allector</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lockfågel:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allĭcĕfăcio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Locka:</text:span></text:span> Sen., Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlĭcio</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">locka bort, förleda:</text:span> poë<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">t.</text:span> ap. Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlecto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Locka bort, förleda:</text:span></text:span> oves, Cato; me Apollo, Enn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förnöja, tjusa, roa, glädja; behaga;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> isynn.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">refl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>: se d-re <text:span text:style-name="T2">aliqua re</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">cum aliquo,</text:span> d-ri <text:span text:style-name="T2">aliqua re, ab aliquo, re, in re</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">finna nöje, glädje i, hafwa sin lust i, älska</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om all slags förnöjelse, äfwen af allwarliga saker, icke blott förströelse, ss.</text:span> oblectare): pulcritudo corporis movet oculos et d-at hoc ipso, quod -; d-ant apparatus magnifici vitæque cultus cum elegantia et copia; cantibus suis d-re alqm; non utilitas parta per amicum, sed ipse amor d-at; Herodotus me magnopere d-at; quam me d-at Theramenes!; is assentatoribus patefacit aures maxime, qui ipse sibi assentatur et se maxime ipse d-at; se cum Musis; se literis; ludis vulgus magnopere d-atur; uterque suo studio d-tus contempsit alterum; inanibus rebus, victu tenui, rerum cognitione d-ri; d-ri re sua familiari, criminibus inferendis, assentatione, altero æque ac se ipso; me ab eo d-ri facilius quam decipi puto posse; - ab altero (genere orationis) non d-ere, alterum oderis; in hoc d-or, C.; herba spe agrestes d-at, Ov.; alqm d-at equitare in arundine longa; vir bonus dici d-or, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">Depon.,</text:span> Petr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlectābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är egnad att förnöja, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Angenäm:</text:span></text:span> cibus, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlectābĭlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förnöjeligt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ett förnöjande sätt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">behagligt:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlectāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Leksak, lekwerk:</text:span></text:span> putat me sibi pro ridiculo et d-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(narr),</text:span> Ter.; inania puerorum d-a, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlectātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nöje, förnöjelse:</text:span></text:span> d. est voluptas suavitate sensus animum deleniens; d-e affici; conviviorum d-em non voluptalibus corporis metiebar; animadvertendum est, quatenus sermo d-em habeat; fabulæ, literæ habent multum d-is; res affert nullam d-em; agere alqd d-is causa; duci videndi et audiendi d-e; a d-e omni negotiis impedimur et in ipsa occupatione d-es alias multas habere possumus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlĭcātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">objectivt:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sinlig, wällustig, läcker, kräslig, förfinad:</text:span></text:span> versus; voluptates d-æ, molles, obscoenæ; convivium; cibus, C.; cultus d-ior, Su. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjusande, intagande:</text:span></text:span> ubi tu es, d-a?, Pt.; puer lepidus et d.; litus, C.; amnis, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>: d-ati = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sköne gossar, älsklingar (i dålig men.),</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">subj.: om personer och deras egenskaper l. handlingar:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wällustig, sinlig:</text:span></text:span> adolescens; filius d-ior; sermo; disciplina (Epicuri); juventus libidinosa et d-a, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Weklig, fin, ömtålig, förwand; granntyckt:</text:span></text:span> vita umbratilis et d-a; d-us ancillarum et puerorum comitatus, C.; fastidium (literarum) d-simum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlĭcāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sinligt, wällustigt; sirligt, smakfullt, fint; makligt; lent:</text:span></text:span> d. et molliter vivere, C.; vestiri, Col.; odiosa multa d. jocoseque fecit, C.; iter conficere, Su.; tractare alqm d-ius, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlĭcia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlĭciæ</text:span>, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">objectivt: i allm.: hwad som, lockar, roar, förnöjer; i god, oftast sämre mening; dock mindre hwad s. retar sinligheten, än det s. roar </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det barnsliga l. flärdfulla sinnet, lättsinnet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lust, lek, flärd,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lyx) (wekliga) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">nöjen, förlustelser:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i abstract men.:</text:span> ludo et d-æ operam dabo, Pt.; d-as facere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(drifwa upptåg),</text:span> Pt.; d-arum causā cum mitella esse; multarum d-arum comes est extrema saltatio; homines d-is diffluentes; amores et d-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(galanterier);</text:span> nulla cogitatio aut supellectilis ad d-as aut epularum ad voluptates; in amore et in d-is esse alicui, habere alqd, alqm in d-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wara någons lust l. fägnad, hafwa ngt till sin lust),</text:span> C.; fortis omissis hoc age d-is, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om concreta saker och om lefwande warelser: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lust-, flärdsaker</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lyxartiklar), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sirater</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (agrementer), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">leksaker, lekwerk;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om personer: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">älskling,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> någons </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lust, fägnad:</text:span></text:span> non est tibi animus d-arum (pretiosæ supellectilis) egens, Hor.; excussis d-is (i. e. emblematis); pueriles d-æ; a talibus d-is (orationis) Herodotus et Thucydides longissime abfuerunt; mel et d-æ tuæ Clio; amores et d-æ tuæ Roscius, C.; Alexis, d-æ domini, Vg.; Titus amor et d-æ generis humani, Su.; passer d-æ meæ puellæ, Catl.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rent subjectivt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nycker, tycken, wurm</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (liebhaberi):</text:span> ecce aliæ d-æ publicanorum vix ferendæ; (Verris) studia et d-æ, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlĭcium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Älskling</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (”juvel”), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lust:</text:span></text:span> asinus, d. domini, Phdr.; fons domus gloria et d.; dorcas, Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlĭciŏlæ</text:span>, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Tullia d-æ meæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(min lilla älskling, ”hjertunge”,),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlĭciŏlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: id.: Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlĭcio</text:span>, cui, cĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utlocka, framlocka, locka, frammana, aflocka, -twinga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquem</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">aliquid</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T2">ab</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">ex aliquo</text:span>): alqm foras, domo, Pt.; inferorum animas; præmio alqm ad alqd; verbum ex aliquo; multa ab aliquo; responsum, sententiam alicujus, C.; alqm in insidias, Cs.; epistolas alicujus, N.; alqm ad colloquium, ad pugnam; arcana alicujus, L.; hostem extra muros, Ct.; veritatem, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i mechanisk l. physisk men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Framdraga, -bringa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ofriwilligt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">-drifwa, aftwinga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">framtwinga:</text:span></text:span> ferrum e terra, C.; alqm e coeno, Pt.; terra ex semine e-it herbescentem viriditatem; ignem conflictu lapidum; sanguinem emungendo; sonos nervorum, C.; id sudorem, alvum e-it, Pn.; lacrimas alicui, Pt.; ardor animi etiam ex infantium ingeniis voces et querelas e-re solet, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utröna, -forska:</text:span></text:span> causam rei; quidquid probabile est in re, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlĕcĕbra</text:span> <text:line-break/>(exlĕcĕbra) ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aflockerska:</text:span></text:span> argeutariæ e-æ (meretrices), Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlecto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utlocka, locka:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illĭcio</text:span>, lexi, lectum: 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Locka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i snara, till ondt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tubba, förföra, -leda:</text:span></text:span> blande ad se; in fraudem, Pt.; in stuprum, C.; ad bellum spe rapinarum, Su.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kalla:</text:span></text:span> populum ad magistratus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> illicium), Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illĕcĕbra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.,</text:span> <text:line-break/>Illĕcĕbræ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lockelse, lockmedel,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wanl. i dålig mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">medel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förmåga att förföra; förförelse, retelse:</text:span></text:span> virtutis i-æ, C.; i-<text:soft-page-break/>is morari spectatorem, Hor.; spes impunitatis est i-a peccandi; quæ tanta in ullo homine i-a juventutis (quanta in Catilina) fuit?; sunt apud eum i-æ libidinum; is delinitur voluptatis i-is; dedere se vitiorum i-is; i-is excitantur flagitia, C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om person:</text:span> Pt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illĕcĕbrōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lockande, förförisk:</text:span></text:span> Pt., <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illĕcĕbrōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">(<text:span text:style-name="T3">Illecto</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förföra:</text:span></text:span> Tert.) <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illectāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lockmedel, retelse:</text:span></text:span> lenonia i-a, Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illectātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lockelse:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lockelse:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illex</text:span>, ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lockande, förförande; lockfågel, förförande:</text:span></text:span> oculi, Ap.; esca, i., aves, Pt.; ejus rei i-es fuimus, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illĭcium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lockmedel</text:span></text:span> (avium): Varr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kallelse:</text:span></text:span> (populi ad prætorem): voca i-um populum ad me, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oblecto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Roa, förströ, förnöja, muntra:</text:span></text:span> hæc studia juventutem agunt, senectutem o-ant; alqm opinione -; se in hortis sine interpellatoribus; se cum libellis, cum aliquo; se agri cultione; ludis o-ri, C.; aleā se, Su.; fabula o-at populum, Hor.: tempus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förströ, angenämt fördrifwa),</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oblectābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Roande:</text:span></text:span> Aus. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oblectāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: Ov. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oblectāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">medel att förnöja, roa: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nöje, förströelse, wederqwickelse; tidsfördrif:</text:span></text:span> meæ senectutis requies et o-ta; possum persequi multa o-ta rerum rusticarum; o-ta et solatia servitutis; o-ta puerorum, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oblectātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nöje, förströelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i mots. till arbete):</text:span> non utilitas quæritur, sed libera animi o.; o. animi requiesque curarum; requies plena o-is; afferre negotiis hominum o-em otii, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oblectātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som förnöjer, roar:</text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oblectātōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Roande, rolig:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pellĭcio</text:span> <text:line-break/>(perlicio), (-lĭcui, Liv. Andr.), lexi, lectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Locka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer till sig, på sin sida; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">locka, förleda, tubba:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med personl. obj.:</text:span> senem per epistolas, Ter.; animum adolescentis; mulierem imbecilli consilii ad se, C.; populum in servitutem, L.; militem donis; - cunctos dulcedine otii (Augustus), T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sakl. obj.:</text:span> majorem partem sententiarum judicum sale suo et lepore, C.; alienas fruges veneficiis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(trolla till sig -),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pellĕcĕbræ</text:span> <text:line-break/>(perlĕcĕbræ), ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lock, tubbningar, lockelser:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōlĭcio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Locka fram; locka:</text:span></text:span> ad fenestram alqm, Pt.; ad spem, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōlecto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Framlocka; locka, förleda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ett steg:</text:span> oviculas; gaudium lacrimas, Ap.; spe largitionis alqm, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sublecto</text:span>, l: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: os alicui, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kittla munnen på ngn) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gäcka:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ăco, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Lacedæmonier.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lăcōnĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Laconien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lăcōnĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Lăcōnĭca, ae, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lăcōnĭcē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Laconien.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcōnĭcum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swettbad:</text:span></text:span> C. <text:line-break/>Lăcōnis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A. f.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăcrĭma,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(lacruma, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">arch.;</text:span> <text:line-break/>dacrima, Liv. Andr.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tår:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> l-æ cadunt alicui, Ter.; nihil citius l-ā arescit; l-as profundere, effundere; tradere se l-is et tristitiæ; confici l-is; jacere in l-is; multis cum l-is loqui; quid in Scipione effecerint, sine l-is non queo dicere; tenere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillbakahålla)</text:span> l-as, C.; multis cum l-is obsecrare aliquem, Cs.; l-is oculos suffusa nitentes; eos l-is solabar obortis; ire in l-as, Vg.; l-æ manant; l-ā spargere favillam amici, Hor.; l-is temperare, Ct.; adventu suorum l-æ obortæ (Lucretiæ), L.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Saft</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af blommor, träd:</text:span> Narcissi, Vg.; vitium, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcrĭmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gråta, fälla tårar:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gråta; begråta:</text:span></text:span> l-o gaudio, Ter.; multo sæpius l-asse Priamum, quam Troilum; oculis l-antibus intueri alqm, C.; multa, multum l-re, Vg.; casum alicujus l-re, N. (illacrimare, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Nipperdey).</text:span><text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tåras,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ned-droppa, utswettas (wätska, om träd m. m.):</text:span> calamus, Pn.; ebur, Ov.; myrrhæ l-tæ cortice, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcrĭmābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är att gråta öfwer, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sorglig, jemmerlig:</text:span></text:span> gemitus, Vg.; bellum; tempus, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcrĭmābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gråtande:</text:span></text:span> L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcrĭmātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gråt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ögonens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rinnande:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collăcrĭmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gråta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tillsammans l. häftigt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utgjuta sig i tårar; begråta:</text:span></text:span> simul omnes, Næv.; is; casum suum, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collăcrĭmātio</text:span>, ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Häftig gråt:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlăcrĭmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drypa, fälla droppar:</text:span></text:span> vitis, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlăcrĭmātio</text:span>, ōnis; <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: (oculorum), Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illăcrĭmo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illăcrĭmor</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gråta, utbrista i tårar öfwer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> i-ans dixit; morti alicujus i-ri, C.; ut urbem vidit, i-vit, L.; malis i-re, Ov.; mortem alcjs, Js. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> lacrimo).<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drypa, swettas, rinna:</text:span></text:span> ebur, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illăcrĭmābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Obegråten:</text:span></text:span> i-es premi longa nocte, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af tårar obeweklig, s. ej röres af tårar:</text:span> Pluto, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sŭperlăcrĭmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gråta = drypa öfwer, på ngt - -:</text:span> palmes, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcrĭmōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Försänkt i tårar, tårefull, gråtande:</text:span></text:span> oculi, Pn.; voces, Vg.; mater, Ap.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som förorsakar tårar:</text:span></text:span> fumus, Hor.; cæpa, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som wäcker tårar = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sorglig, ömklig:</text:span></text:span> funus; bellum; poēmata Fufi, <text:soft-page-break/>Hor.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drypande, wätskefull:</text:span></text:span> radices vitium, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcrĭmōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">under många tårar:</text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcrĭmŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten tår:</text:span></text:span> exprimere falsam l-am, Ter.; C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lacta . . ., Lacte . . ., Lacti . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lac. <text:line-break/>Lacto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lac <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Lacio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lactūca,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> lac; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mjölk- l. saftrik wäxt,</text:span> Varr.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lactuk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (en wäxt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">salat:</text:span></text:span> Pn., Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lactūcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lacuatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Laquear, Lacus. <text:line-break/>Lacun . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lacus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăcus,</text:span> us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: fördjupning, i synn. för watten:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af naturen bildad </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sjö, insjö, dam:</text:span></text:span> l. Albanus, Averni, C.; l. Lemanus, Cs.; Stygii l., Vg.; l. Curtius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dam l. träsk på</text:span> forum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i Rom),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af menniskohand danad):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dam;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öppen och i jordbrynet liggande </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">brunn, bassin,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fontaine), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">reservoir</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för regnwatten eller för watten från en wattenledning, såwäl af enklare som af praktfullare inrättning, sådan som t. ex. Fontana di Trevi m. fl. större l. mindre i nuw. Rom:</text:span> si (in villa) non est aqua viva, faciendi sunt - l-us sub dio, - ut pecus uti possit, Varr.; omnes a furno l-uque redeuntes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som komma från bageri l. wattenhemtningsställe),</text:span> Hor.; (Romæ sunt) l-us i. e. putei mille trecenti quinquaginta duo, Not. Urbis.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i jorden muradt l. bygdt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i en win- l. oljepreß l. i en</text:span> cella vinaria <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> olearia; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwenså i en smedja för jernets afkylande o. s. w.:</text:span> l. vinarius; l. in cella, Cato.; l. vinarii et torcularii, Col.; (Messalina) simulacrum vindemiæ celebrabat: urgeri prela, fluere l-us, T. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> oratio de - l-u fervida, C.; stridentia æra tingere l-u, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sädesbing:</text:span></text:span> Col.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fördjupning, fält, ruta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ett paneladt tak:</text:span> Lucil. ap. Serv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcūna</text:span> <text:line-break/>(lŭcūna), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fördjupning, håla, grop:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> l-æ auri et argenti <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(grufwor),</text:span> Lucr.; aratrum l-am facit (i. e. sulcum), Varr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: fördjupning med watten uti:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poet. om hafwets </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Djup, afgrund:</text:span></text:span> salsæ l-æ; aquæ vastæ l-æ, Lucr. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åkerdike, aflopps-graf:</text:span></text:span> cavæ l-æ sudant humore, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lucka, brist</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ngt:</text:span> l-am rei familiaris explere; vide, ne qua l. in auro sit, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcūnar</text:span>, āris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tak med rutor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fält, plafond:</text:span></text:span> gladium e l-i setā equinā aptum demitti jussit, C.; non aureum mea renidet in domo l-ar, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcūnārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: id.: Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcūno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra fördjupning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">panela,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sira ned panelning:</text:span> Pn., Ov. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcūnōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">full af fördjupningar, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fördjupad:</text:span></text:span> sphæra nihil eminens, nihil l-um habet, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcuscŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten fördjupning, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grop:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăquear</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> ablaqueo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och ortsnamnet</text:span> Sublaqueum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Subiaco)</text:span> = oppidum sub lacubus situm, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adj.</text:span> Sublacensis), āris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Paneladt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i fördjupade fält l. rutor siradt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tak; plafond:</text:span></text:span> dependent lychni l-bus aureis, Vg.; auro teguntur l-ia, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăqueātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăcuātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Panelad;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> prydd med paneladt tak:</text:span> tectum, Hor.; templum pulcherrime l-um, C.; auro l-um, L.; antra tophis et pumice l-a, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ablăqueo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oblăqueo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gräfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lossa) kring träd, helst winträd;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kring-gräfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> dem (för att befordra deras fruktbarhet):</text:span> circum oleas, Cato; vites, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ablăqueātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kringgräfning:</text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ăcȳdes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ādē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö wid ioniska kusten.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ādon, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. flodnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>æca, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romerskt cognomen.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lædo,</text:span> læsi, læsum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg., ss. sammansättningarne antyda, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stöta, klämma); Skada, göra men:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i kroppslig men.: skada, såra, förgripa sig på, beswära:</text:span> per summa volaret gramina nec l-isset aristas; te l-it frigus, nos via <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uttröttar);</text:span> læsum robigine ferrum, Vg.; quæ l-unt oculos, festinas demere; barbare l. oscula alicujus; signum lagenæ; collum pendulum zonā l-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(strypa, jfr</text:span> elido, oblido); (si) te pulvis strepitusque rotarum l-it, Hor.; ferro alqd, Pn.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> os l. alicui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förtreta ngn),</text:span> Ter.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skada, angripa, förorätta, göra för när;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> isynn. moraliskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förolämpa, förnärma, kränka:</text:span></text:span> dicto, facto aliquem, Pt.; nullā læsus injuriā; sæpe testis non l-it, nisi lacessatur, C.; neminem l-bat, N.; dignitatem; famam alicujus obscuris suspicionibus; in aliqua re l. alqm, C.; alqm, Sa., Cs.; tristi versu l. alqm; numen deorum (perjurio), Hor.; linguā aliquem, Tib.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stöta;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> göra ondt = wäcka medömkan:</text:span> si te fuga (servi) nihil l-it (emptorem); tunc tua me infortunia l-ent, Telephe, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bryta; bryta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot (tro, löfte o. d.):</text:span> fidem (suam), C., Cs., Hor.; foedus læsum, Vg.; pudicitia læsa, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Læsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personligt angrepp (i ett tal):</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allīdo</text:span>, līsi, līsum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slå, stöta, drifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot -:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentl. men.:</text:span> ad scopulos a-si interficiuntur, Cs.; cretea persona <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mask)</text:span> trabi a-sa, Lucr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. (bilden från ett skepp, s. stöter på l. går i qwaf; jfr</text:span> affligo): Servius (in judicio) a-sus est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fått en hård stöt),</text:span> C.; dominus fundi a-itur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(går under),</text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allīsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slag, stöt:</text:span></text:span> Treb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collīdo</text:span>, līsi, līsum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slå, stöta, tränga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (klämma) i hop, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillsamman:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">egentl.:</text:span> navigia inter se c-it mare; naves inter se c-untur, Ct.; manus c-re, Qu.; dentes, Sen.; humor facile comprimi c-ique <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(packas)</text:span> potest, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">prægnant: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stöta; slå itu; krossa:</text:span></text:span> vasa, C.; nasus c-sus, Sen.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med medial betyd. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drabba tillsammans, komma i strid</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (komma i collision):</text:span> Græcia Barbariæ lento c-sa duello, Hor.; capita reipublicæ inter se; Vell.; leges, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collīsīo</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collīsus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanstötning:</text:span></text:span> Js., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlīdo</text:span>, līsi, līsum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utslå, utstöta, -tränga, utpressa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> oculos alicui, Pt., Vg.; aurigam e curru, C.; spuma e-sa, Vg.; ignes nubibus e-si, Ov.; ignem e silice, Pn.; navis e-itur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kastas på grund),</text:span> Cs.; corpora e-sa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skeppsbrutna, på land uppwräkta),</text:span> T.; vox e-sa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(frampressad),</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utdrifwa, -pressa; framkrysta:</text:span></text:span> morbum venis, Hor.; magnas sententias (et barbari) e-unt, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stöta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">klämma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sönder (till döds); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">krossa, bryta; qwäfwa, förqwäfwa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> caput Pt.; caput alicujus saxo, L.; stipite alqm, Ct.; imago in speculo e-itur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(brytes),</text:span> Lucr.; anguem, Vg.; fetum, Col.; fauces, Ov. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> nervos virtutis; stirpes ægritudinis e-re; e-i ægritudine, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlīsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utpressande:</text:span></text:span> lacrimæ, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illæsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oskadd:</text:span></text:span> corpus, Ov.; i-um evadere, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illīdo</text:span>, līsi, līsum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stöta, slå, drifwa, tränga emot, på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> ad vulnus manus, C.; Notus - navem vadis (<text:span text:style-name="T2">dat.</text:span>), Vg.; navis in vadum i-itur, Ct.; fluctus litori i-itur, Qu.; is litori i-tur cum classe, Vell.; caput foribus i-re, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Krossa, söndertrampa:</text:span></text:span> serpens i-sa, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illīsus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stötande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stöt emot:</text:span></text:span> Pn., Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oblīdo</text:span>, līsi, līsum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trycka till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">för; qwäfwa, förqwäfwa:</text:span></text:span> gulam alicujus digitulis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(strypa),</text:span> C.; fauces, T.; fetum, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ælius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på en romersk</text:span> gens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och deß medlemmar.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Læliānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Læna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr. (χλαῖνα): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kappa, mantel:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ænas, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cognomen i</text:span> gens Porcia. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>āertes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lāerta, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">n. pr.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lāertĭădes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Laertes’ son Ulysses.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lāertĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Læsio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lædo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>æstrȳgon ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">plur.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Læstrȳgŏnes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mythiskt folkslag i Campanien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Læstrȳgŏnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ætōrius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Subst.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. gentilnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Lætus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glad:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg., subjectiv men., i synnerhet om en glädje, som röjer sig i ansigte och åtbörder: glad, leende, förnöjd, nöjd:</text:span> alacrem l-que volitare; vultus l.; vagantur l-i atque erecti passim toto foro, C.; l-i pacem agitabamus; civitas, trepida antea, l-a agere, Sa.; l-i ut explorata victoria - ad castra pergunt, Cs.; l. in præsens animus; aspice, si l-us donata reponere possum, Hor.; l. de amica, Ter.; l-us origine novæ urbis, L.; l. sorte tua vives sapienter, Hor.; l. in adversis, Luc.; victoriā l., Ct.; l-us animi, Vell.; - ore, vultu, Val.; l. laborum, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i obj. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">glädje-, fröjdefull, fägnesam, lyckosam:</text:span></text:span> illic res l-æ - partæ tibi -; dies, Vg., Hor.; æstas, Vg.; omnia fiunt in dies l-ora, C.; pax; libertas, L.; victoria, Sa., Hor.; l-is sedibus pios reponis, Hor.; nuntius, Ct.; prodigium; l-um est id fieri, Pn.; exta l-ora. Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. har ett gladt, leende, prydligt, rikt utseende; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prydd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med -; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skön, leende, blomstrande:</text:span></text:span> Romulus l-us nutricis lupæ fulvo tegmine, Vg.; l-um genus dicendi et nitidum, C.; copia dicendi floribus l-a, Qu.; oculis (Aeneæ Venus) l-os afflarat honores, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i synn. om jordmon, wäxter, djur) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rik, fruktbar, (trefwen), treflig, frodig:</text:span></text:span> ager, Varr.; segetes, C., Vg.; tellus justo l-ior; armenta, Vg.: pascua, Hor.; solum, Col.; lucus l-simus umbræ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skuggrik),</text:span> Vg.; vite quid est aut fructu l-ius aut aspectu pulcrius?, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Læte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gladt, med glädje; i glad, förnöjd ton</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> o. s. w.:</text:span> ferre alqd, C.; dicere, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. dicere, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i prydlig, blomstrande stil),</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rikligt; frodigt:</text:span></text:span> l-ius humescere poculis, Hor.; fruticat laurus, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lætĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. gör glad, fröjdar sinnet; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ljuflig, ljuf:</text:span></text:span> vites l-æ pampinis pubescere, poēt. ap. C.; plausus, St.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lætĭfĭco</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra glad:</text:span></text:span> Pt.; gloria pulsi Magni (Pompeji) alqm, Luc.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppfriska;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> befordra fruktbarhet hos ngt; (gödsla):</text:span> sol terram, C.; Laërtes agrum suis manibus, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lætĭfĭcor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jubla:</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. pr.</text:span>: malo alterius, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lætĭtia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glädje, förnöjelse,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (isynn. sådan, som utbrister och wisas); glädtighet, glad stämning, munterhet, glad hänryckning l. hänförelse:</text:span> l. est præsentium bonorum, libido futurorum; illud judicium hilaritatis ac l-æ plenum fuit; l. gestiens vel nimia; efferri l. se efferre l-ā; alqm effert l.; exsultare l-ā; gestire nimia l-ā; perfrui l-ā; ex aliqua re percipere l-am; facere, afferre, objicere alicui l-am; <text:soft-page-break/>afficere, extollere alqm l-ā, C.; omnibus l-is lætum incedere, poēt. ap. C.; l. victoriæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwer seger);</text:span> l-am præcipere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i förwäg känna),</text:span> Cs.; ex summa l-a et lascivia ingens tristitia civitatem invasit; l-am agitare, Sa.; Bacchus l-æ dator, Vg.; nati in usum l-æ scyphi, Hor.; l. conjugum, liberorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwer -),</text:span> Ct.; est mihi l-æ alqd, N.; l. convivii, T. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skönhet; blomstrande utseende</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (stil):</text:span> membrorum, St.; orationis, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Riklighet, bördighet:</text:span></text:span> pabuli, Js.; loci, Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lætĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> = lætitia 1.: Acc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lætor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glädjas, fröjdas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (uttr. enl.</text:span> Cic. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mera häftig glädje än</text:span> gaudeo): impense, vehementer l.; l. triumphis suis; malo alieno; utrumque l-or, et te sine corporis dolore fuisse et animo valuisse; in omnium gemitu l-batur; in hoc semper l-tus est, quod ea faceret, quæ sibi objici non possent; de communi salute l-ri; Scipionem natum esse hæc civitas, dum erit, l-bitur; l-anti animo et spe optima, C.; barbari suo more l-ri, exsultare, strepere, Sa.; toto pectore l., Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trifwas;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hafwa ett gladt, leende utseende:</text:span> vitis tepore potius quam frigore, Col.; loca l-tia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(leende),</text:span> Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lætābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är att glädjas öfwer; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fägnesam:</text:span></text:span> quid habet ista res l-e?, C.; factum cunctis diis l-e, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lætābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glad:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lætāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwad s. befordrar frodighet och trefnad); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gödsel:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lætanter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med glädje:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lætātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glädje, jubel:</text:span></text:span> nec hostibus diutina l. nec ipsis longior dolor relinquitur, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illætābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. ej är att fröjda sig åt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sorglig:</text:span></text:span> ora; murmur, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Perlætus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mycket glad, fröjdefull:</text:span></text:span> supplicatio, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Lætus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lif-egen:</text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Læve <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lævus.<text:line-break/>Lævig . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lævis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lævis</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lēvis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glatt, fin, slät, blank:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. och eg. men.:</text:span> corpuscula alia l-ia, alia aspera, C.; clupeus, Vg.; galea; ames, Hor.; l-ior conchis, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fin</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i hyn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mjäll, finhylld</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots. hår- l. skäggbewuxen, sträf), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ungdoms-skön:</text:span></text:span> frons; pectus, Vg.; fugit retro l. juventas; l. Agyieus (Apollo, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> intonsus), Hor. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fin, putsad:</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om föredraget (serskildt med afseende på ordens sammanställning): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glatt, jemn; fin, putsad, polerad:</text:span></text:span> concursus verborum l. quodammodo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> hiulcus), C.; l. compositio, Qu.; sectantem l-ia nervi deficiunt, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lævĭgo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lēvĭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glatta, polera; stöta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i mortel), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">pulverisera:</text:span></text:span> parietes, Varr.; cote alqd, Pn.; Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lævĭgātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lævĭtas</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lēvĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glatthet; finhet:</text:span></text:span> l. et mollitudo, C.; compositionis (verborum), Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lævo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lēvo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glatta, polera, putsa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i eg. och oeg. men.:</text:span> ligna, Lucr.; mensam, St.; corpus, C.; nimis aspera (in sermone et versibus) l-re cultu, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allævo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allēvo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glatta, släta (släthugga):</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collævo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collēvo</text:span>, 1.: id.: Col., Pn., Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlævo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlēvo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Släta, släthugga:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lævor</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lēvor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> = lævitas: Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ævīnus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognom.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lævitas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lævis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ævius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. nomen.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Læviānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lævo, Lævor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lævis.<text:line-break/>Lævorsum, -sus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lævus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lævus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wenster,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. är) till wenster l. på wenstra sidan l. handen:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> l-a manus, C.; undæ, Vg.; latus; corpus; picus, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> augurium, omen) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gynnsam, lyckosam:</text:span></text:span> numina, Vg.; fulmina, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förwänd, galen:</text:span></text:span> mens, Vg.; o. ego l., qui -, Hor. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Obeqwäm, otjenlig; förderflig:</text:span></text:span> tempus, Hor.; numen, Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Læva</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: (sc. manus; pars): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wenstra handen; wenstra sidan:</text:span></text:span> concurrit dextera l-æ; inani l-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utan ring),</text:span> Hor.; a l-a, Enn. ap. C.; ad l-am, C.; paululum descendere ad l-am, Sa.; petere l-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gå åt w.),</text:span> Vg., Pn.: l-ā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på wenstra sidan, till wenster),</text:span> L., Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lævum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: in l-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(åt w.),</text:span> Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lævum</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: intonuit l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till wenster),</text:span> Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Læve</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oskickligt, oriktigt:</text:span></text:span> puer jussa haud l. accepit, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lævorsus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lævorsum</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åt wenster:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăgănum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bakelse:</text:span></text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lagēa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lageos.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăgēna</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăgōna</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Lăgoena), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flaska,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wanl. af lera och med lång, smal hals (foglietta):</text:span> inanes obsignare, C.; signum l-æ læsum, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăguncŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăgēos,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăgēa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en winsort (har-win):</text:span> Vg., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lagēus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lagus.<text:line-break/>Lagoena, -gona <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lagena.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăgōis,</text:span> ĭdis <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: peregrina l., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags fågel, enl.</text:span> Isid. = fulica, Hor. Sat. II. 2. 22.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăgŏnŏpŏnus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr. (λαγών <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">buk,</text:span> πόνος <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wånda): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bukref, magplåga:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăgōpus,</text:span> ŏdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. harfotad): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snöripa:</text:span></text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Laguncula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lagena.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăguncŭlus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en sort bakelse:</text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>āgus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">n. pr.</text:span> (Ptolemæus L-i f.). <text:line-break/>Lāgēus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>āis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>āĭus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lāĭădes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">son af L. (Oedipus).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ălăgē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>aletāni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Laletānia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk och land i Hispanien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lallus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lallum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lallande, waggsång:</text:span></text:span> Aus.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lallo</text:span>, 1.: Ps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Lāma,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pöl, puß:</text:span></text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Lāma,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en trädart:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lambĕro,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sönderslita;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">nedgöra, tilltyga:</text:span></text:span> Fs., Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lambo,</text:span> bi, bĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> labium, labrum): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Läppja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">slicka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> canes alqd, C.; vulnera linguā, Ov.; musca alqd, Mt.; cibos l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lapa, slicka i sig),</text:span> quia caret dentibus, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lätt öfwerfara, genomfara, beröra, nå:</text:span></text:span> quæ loca fabulosus l-it Hydaspes, Hor.; flamma comas l-it; Aetna attollit globos flammarum et sidera l-it, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lambĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: Sol.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allambo</text:span>, 3.: flumen terram lymphis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sköljer, bespolar),</text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Circumlambo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rundtomkring slicka:</text:span> ora: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlambo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afslicka:</text:span></text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prælambo</text:span>, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förut läppja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på:</text:span> omne, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. Tiberis Romam (præfluit): Av.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lamella, -mellula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lamina.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lāmenta,</text:span> ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Lāmentæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: Pac.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klagolåt, -rop, -skrän, jämmer, jämmer-, werop</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (isynnerhet öfwer döda):</text:span> mors ejus l-is vacat; de - l-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid likbegängelser)</text:span> expressa verba sunt: mulieres genas ne radunto etc.; in l-is luctuque jacere; l-is se muliebriter dedere, C.; l-a et lacrimas cito, dolorem atque tristitiam tarde ponunt (Germani), T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lāmentārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: ædes l-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sorgehus),</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lāmentor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Lāmento, 1.: Ap., St.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klaga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (högljudt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">jämra sig; beklaga, begråta:</text:span></text:span> ea mulier mihi præter ceteras l-ri visa est, Ter.; flebiliter, C.; l-amur, nostros non apparere labores, Hor.; matrem mortuam l-ri, Ter.; cæcitatem alicujus l-ri; calamitas l-da reipublicæ, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lāmentābĭlĭs</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Beklaganswärd, beklaglig:</text:span></text:span> (Trojæ) l-e regnum, Vg.; tributum, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jämmerfull, jämrande, klagande:</text:span></text:span> gemitus; funus; voce l-i deplorare, C.; comploratio, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lāmentātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klagan, klagolåt, -skrän; jämmer, gråt:</text:span></text:span> complere ædem plangore et l-e; lugubris l.; funeris, mulieris, C.; inutilis, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlāmentor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Häftigt jämra sig öfwer; begråta:</text:span></text:span> alqd, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlāmentābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jämrande:</text:span></text:span> C. Tusc. II. 24. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Seyff.).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Lămĭa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hexa, trollpacka;</text:span></text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en fisk:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ămia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cognomen i</text:span> gens Aelia. <text:line-break/>Lămiānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">III. <text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ămĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Thessalien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lāmĭna</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sammandr.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lamna</text:span>), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: tunn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af metall l. träd, sål.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">plåt, bleck; klinga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af swärd, såg o. d.):</text:span> C.; tigna religare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fästa)</text:span> l-is et clavis, Cs.; aēnea, L.; argenti, Ov.<text:span text:style-name="T2">;</text:span> plumbi; aceris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af lönn),</text:span> Pn.; l. argutæ serræ, Vg.; ensis, Ov. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. l-æ ardentes, candentes, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags pinoredskap:</text:span> ardentes l-as ceterosque cruciatus admovere, C.; lamna candente uri, Hor.; candescat l. vernæ, Ppt.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mynt:</text:span></text:span> inimicus lamnæ, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lāmella</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lāmellŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: argenti, Sen., Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlāmĭno</text:span>, 1.: nuces ictu, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">spränga:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sublāmĭna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Underplåt, -bleck:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lamium,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en wäxt:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ampădiŏ, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lampas,</text:span> ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fackla:</text:span></text:span> Cupido argenteus cum l-e, C.; in cursu l-da tradere alicui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bildl. = lemna sin plats, syssla åt ngn),</text:span> Varr.; corusca l.; l. vacat igne, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lampa:</text:span></text:span> ignifera, Lucr.; aēnea, Juv.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: om solen, månen och deras </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ljus,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om meteorer o. s. w.:</text:span> Phoebea l. (sol); dies prima l-e lustrabat terras, Vg.; nona l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dagen),</text:span> Lucr.; it. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">månad,</text:span> Vfl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ampĕtĭē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ampis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: it.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ampridius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ampsăcus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lampsăcum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad wid Hellesponten.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lampsăcēnus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lampsăcĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ămus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lāna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ull:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> alba, Vg.; mollis, Ov.; l-am carĕre <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(karda),</text:span> Pt.; ducere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(spinna),</text:span> Ov.; trahere (id.), Juv.; l-am facere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(spinna),</text:span> Lucr., Inscr.; l-ā victum quæritare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(medelst spånad),</text:span> Ter.; rixari de l-ā caprinā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om något, som icke finnes till),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dun</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på fågel; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fjun</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på wäxter:</text:span> interior cygni; simili l-a celantur ventura Cydonia (mala), Mt.; nemora Aethiopum molli canentia l-ā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bomull),</text:span> Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lätt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Moln:</text:span></text:span> l-æ vellera feruntur per cælum, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lānāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: pecus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ull-boskap),</text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lānārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. har ull; ullig:</text:span> herba, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lānārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. arbetar i ull,</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lānātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ullig, fjunbetäckt:</text:span></text:span> ovis; vitis, Col.; l-ore canitie folia, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lānestris</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lāneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är af ull, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Yllen:</text:span></text:span> pallium, Vop., C.<text:line-break/>b. (laneus) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fin</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som ull:</text:span> Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lānĭcium</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lānĭtium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ull:</text:span></text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lānĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ull-bärande:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lānĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som arbetar med ull, spinner:</text:span> manus, Tib.; ars, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lānĭfĭcium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ull-spånad:</text:span></text:span> assuescebant l-o filiæ et neptes Augusti, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lānĭger</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ullbärande, ullklädd:</text:span></text:span> greges <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(får);</text:span> bidentes, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lānĭger</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wädur:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lānōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ullrik:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lānūgo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(samling af) ull, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fjun, fnugg,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> isynn.: det första </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skäggfjunet,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fint) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skägg:</text:span></text:span> foliorum, Pn.; māla cana l-e, Vg.; ætas primæ l-is, Ov.; rara, Pn.; vultus sordet l-e, Mt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sågspån:</text:span></text:span> Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lānūgĭnōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ullig, fjunig, ull-lik:</text:span></text:span> folia; vermiculus, Pn. - Comp. l-ior, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lancea,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">långt spjut, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lans:</text:span></text:span> lata, Vg.; infigere pectori l-am, Ct.; rari gladiis aut majoribus l-is utuntur (Germani): hastas - gerunt, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lanceārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lansbewäpnad, lancier:</text:span> Amm.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lanceŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten lans:</text:span> Cp.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lancĭno,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sönderslita:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> morsu alqm, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förskingra:</text:span></text:span> bona, Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlancĭno</text:span>, 1.: Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lancula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lanx.<text:line-break/>Lanestris, Laneus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lana.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>angŏbardi, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk i norra Germanien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Langueo,</text:span> gŭi, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> kroppsligen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">matt, utmattad, orklös, wanmäktig, maktlös; wara swag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sjuk):</text:span> e via; facilius est currentem incitare, quam l-entem commovere; vox nec l-ens nec canora, C.; corpus morbo, Vg.; vires in corpore, Ov.; auditor, Qu.; ter omnino l-uit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(war sjuk);</text:span> Augustus sub natalem suum l-bat, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wara </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slapp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (håg- l. modlös), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förslappad, dåsig, owerksam, likgiltig:</text:span></text:span> otio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> in otio l-re; meum otium l-re non patior; populi l-entis incitatio et effrenati moderatio, C.; l-entibus aliis impetum facere; si vos l-re viderint, feroces aderunt, Sa.; plenus l-et amator, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Languĕfăcio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">göra matt, (lugna):</text:span> vis sonorum incitat languentes et l-cit excitatos, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Languesco</text:span>, gŭi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blifwa matt, mattas; blifwa slapp, swag:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i kroppslig men.:</text:span> corpore l-it; orator senectute, C.; moriens, Vg.; fiuctus, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mattas, slappas:</text:span></text:span> industria; consensus populi - si nos l-imus, debilitetur necesse est, C.; cupido, Pn. ep.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Languĭdus</text:span>, -ior, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Matt, maktlös, slapp, swag:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i kroppslig men., om lefwande l. liflösa subj.:</text:span> labore et æstu, Sa.; vino l-us, C.; aqua (Tiberis), L.; conviva; vina, Hor.; color; ignis; ictus, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till håg, sinne, själskraft): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slapp, slö,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (långsam, owerksam):</text:span> pecus tarda et l-a ad pastum nata; senectus non modo non l-a et iners, sed etiam operosa; consilia; philosophus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till grundsatserna)</text:span> <text:soft-page-break/>mollis, l-us, enervatus, C.; nihil l-i patiebatur, Sa.; l-oribus nostris acrius instare hostes, Cs.; auctoritas; ira, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Languĭde</text:span>, -ius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Matt, slappt, swagt:</text:span></text:span> procedere, Col.; lucet, Pn.; in opere l-ius versari, Cs.; l. dictum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(omanligt),</text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Languĭdŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Något slapp, matt, wißnad:</text:span></text:span> coronæ, C.; somnus, Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Languĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. utmattar, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utmattande:</text:span></text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Languor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kroppslig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Matthet, slapphet, wanmakt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sjukdom):</text:span> corporis, C.; ad l-em dare, ducere alqm, Pt., Ter.; militum l-or et vigiliæ, Cs.; corpora habet l., Ov.; aquosus l-or <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om wattensot),</text:span> Hor.; coloris, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">andlig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slapphet, dåsighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (owerksamhet):</text:span> quæ ceteris l-em afferunt, illum acuebant (otium et solitudo); l-i et desidiæ se dare; bonorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(de wälsinnades),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlanguesco</text:span>, gui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mattas, slappas:</text:span></text:span> cura; res, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oblanguesco</text:span>, gui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slappas:</text:span></text:span> literæ nostræ desiderio tui e-runt, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕlanguesco</text:span>, gui, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åter mattas; wanmäktig sjunka tillbaka:</text:span></text:span> venti, Sen.; moribunda r-uit, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åter slappas; lugnas:</text:span></text:span> impetus regis, L.; vino animos r-re et virtutem remitti existimant, Cs.; dicit se r-isse, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Langŭla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bredt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fat:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Languor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Langueo.<text:line-break/>Laniarium, Laniat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lanius.<text:line-break/>Lanicium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lana. <text:line-break/>Laniena <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lanius.<text:line-break/>Lanif . . ., Laniger <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lana.<text:line-break/>Lanio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lanius.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lănista,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fäktmästare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. inöfwar gladiatorer:</text:span> C., Juv.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Banditanförare, upprors-stiftare, uppwiglare:</text:span></text:span> C., L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lănistĭcius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: familia (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af gladiatorer),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lanitium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lana.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lănius,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lănio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slagtare, köttmånglare:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bödel:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăniārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slagtarebod:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăniēna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slagtarebod, -hus:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slagtande, sönderslitande:</text:span></text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lănio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sönderhugga, -slita, sarga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> a bestia valentissima homo imbecillus; a feris l-antur corpora (mortuorum), C.; viscera, hostem dentibus; lupi obvios, L.; os unguibus, Ct.; vestem, T. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> carmina sacrilegæ linguæ, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăniatio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: Sch.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăniātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slagtande, sönderslitande:</text:span></text:span> cædes et l-io, Sen.; l-tus ferarum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlănio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sönderslita, slita i stycken:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> canes cadaver Clodii, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> anima morientis d-ta dispargitur, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăniōnius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. tillhör slagtare, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slagtare-:</text:span></text:span> mensa, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lanosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lana.<text:line-break/>Lantern . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Laterna.<text:line-break/>Lanug . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lana.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ānŭvium, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Latium.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lānŭvīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lanx,</text:span> cis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fat</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för kött; offerfat):</text:span> l-bus pascere alqm, C.; detergere l-es, Pt.; cælata, Ov.; onerant cumulatis l-bus aras, Vg.; tura plena l-e dare, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wåg-, wigtskål:</text:span></text:span> ponere alqd in l-e libræ, C.; duas l-es sustinet Juppiter, Vg.; gemina, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lancŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>āŏcŏon, ontis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>āŏdămīa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>āŏdĭcē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grekiska personnamn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>āŏdĭcēa <text:line-break/>(Lāŏdĭcīa), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på städer i Asien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lāŏdĭcēensis <text:line-break/>(Lāŏdĭcensis), <text:line-break/>Lāŏdĭcēnus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>āŏmĕdon, ontis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lāŏmĕdontēus, <text:line-break/>Lāŏmĕdontĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lāŏmĕdontĭădes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">patronym.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăpăthum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăpăthus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăpăthĭum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Syra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wäxt):</text:span> C., Pn., Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lapicid . . ., Lapid . . ., Lapill . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lapis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăpis,</text:span> ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wanl. bearbetad sten, mindre än</text:span> saxum):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> l-e percussus; l-bus cooperiri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stenas),</text:span> C.; l-es jacere, conjicere, mittere, Cs.; l-e ictus; l-em attulit (mater Pausaniæ) ad introitum ædis, N.; modicus l., qui mittitur fundā, L.; l-um jactus, Ov.; l. molaris, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Milsten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mil = 1000 steg):</text:span> ad quintum l-em (ab urbe) sepultus est, N.; uno l-e distamus, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Råsten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">gränssten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (på egor):</text:span> vetus, Tib.; sacer, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Minnes-sten, grafsten:</text:span></text:span> Su., Ppt.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Auctionssten</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sten, hwarpå utroparen stod wid auctionen:</text:span> emptus de l-e, C.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dyrbar sten (spec. marmor); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ädelsten:</text:span></text:span> Parius, Vg.; Thasius, Numidicus, Su.; clarus, Hor. <text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildliga uttryck:</text:span> quid stas, l.? <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stock, nöt),</text:span> Ter.; l-es loqui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hårda ord),</text:span> Pt.; l-es omnes flere cogere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om en talare),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăpĭcīda</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: (cædo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stenhuggare:</text:span></text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăpĭcīdīnæ</text:span>, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stenbrott:</text:span></text:span> C., Pt., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăpĭdārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sten, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sten-:</text:span></text:span> latomiæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stenbrott),</text:span> Pt.; campus, Sol. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăpĭdārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stenhuggare:</text:span></text:span> Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăpĭdesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förstenas:</text:span></text:span> glans, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăpĭdeus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Af sten, sten-; stenig:</text:span></text:span> imber, C., L.; murus, L.; pons, Ct.; sum l-us <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som förstenad),</text:span> Pt.; campus, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăpĭdo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stena:</text:span></text:span> alqm: Cs., Fl. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">impers.</text:span> l-at: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">det regnar sten:</text:span></text:span> L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăpĭdātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stenkastning, stenande; stenregn:</text:span></text:span> facta est l. saxis, C.; Fl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăpĭdātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stenkastare:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlăpĭdo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rensa från sten:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlăpĭdo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kasta stenar omkring), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Strö omkring sig, förskingra, -slösa, förstöra:</text:span></text:span> triginta minas, Ter.; pecuniam publicam, C.; grandine alqd, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlăpĭdātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: Jct. (Liv.?).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlăpĭdo</text:span> = delapido: <text:span text:style-name="T2">pf. part.,</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăpĭdōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stenig:</text:span></text:span> terra, Varr.; locus, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stenhård:</text:span></text:span> panis, Hor.; corna, Vg.; chiragra, Ps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăpillus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten sten:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> numerare diem meliore <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(den hwite)</text:span> l-o, Ps., signare, Mt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dyrbar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ädel sten:</text:span></text:span> Libyci l-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i mosaik),</text:span> Hor.; Indici, Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăpillŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: Sol.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ăpĭtha, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> -æ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslag i Thessalien.</text:span><text:line-break/>Lăpĭthæus, <text:line-break/>Lăpĭthēĭus, <text:line-break/>Lăpĭthōnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(thessalisk),</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lappa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kardborre:</text:span></text:span> Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lappāceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af k. l. lik k.:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lappāgo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en wäxt, s. liknar k.:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lapsăna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wildkål:</text:span></text:span> l-ā vivere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(torftigt),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lapsio, Lapso, Lapsus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lābor. <text:line-break/>Laquear, -queatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lacus.<text:line-break/>Laqueatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se äfwen</text:span> Laqueus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăqueus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snara, streck, rännsnara, giller:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> inserere collum in l-um, C.; l-is falces averterunt (ii, <text:soft-page-break/>qui obsidebantur), Cs.; saxa et radices l-is vinciebat (quibus allevati milites ascenderent), Sa.; l-o gulam alicujus frangere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(strypa),</text:span> Sa.; l-o interimere alqm, Hor.; l-o feras, gruem captare, Vg., Hor.; animam l-o claudere, Ov.; l-o vitam, infamiam finire, Sen., T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Band, snara:</text:span></text:span> legum l-is constringere; judicii l-is irretitus; disputationum atque interrogationum l-is irretiri; verbi l-o capi, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăqueātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snärd:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlăqueo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lösa ur band:</text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illăqueo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snärja, locka i snara:</text:span></text:span> munera alqm, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Lār,</text:span> lăris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skydds-gud:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> lucos in agris habento et Larum sedes; ædes Larum, C.; mille L-es geniumque ducis (Augusti) habet urbs; exagitant et Lar et turba Diania fures; gemini L-es, qui compita servant (compitales); præstites, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Husgud</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (tomte):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.</text:span> L-em corona nostrum decorari volo, Pt.; nobis L. familiaris nusquam est, Sa. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> b.); L-es placare ture et horna fruge, Hor.; L-em venerari farre pio et plenā acerrā, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">meton. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hem, härd, hus och hem;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om djur: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bo, näste:</text:span></text:span> ad suum l-em reverti, C.; l. certus, Hor.; l-e suo recipere alqm, L.; ante l-em proprium vesci, Hor.; nunc avis in ramo tecta l-emque parat, Ov.; sub terra apes fovere l-em, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ăra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ărunda, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl. sagan Larernes moder:</text:span> Ov., Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lărārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kapell</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för husgudar:</text:span> Lpd.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lărĭfŭga</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. flyr hemmet, kringstrykare:</text:span> Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ār <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ars, <text:line-break/>Lartis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">etruriskt förnamn:</text:span> L. Tolumuius, L. Porsenna.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lardum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Laridum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ārentia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Romuli fostermor.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lārentālia, -ium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lārentīnal, ālis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Larentias festdag:</text:span> Ov., Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Largus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Riklig, frikostig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. är riklig l. gifwes l. gifwer rikligt:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Riklig, rund, rundlig, ymnig, frikostig:</text:span></text:span> sol l-a luce terras complet, C.; imber; l-o fletu ora rigabat; l-ior hic campos æther et lumine vestit purpureo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i Elysium),</text:span> Vg.; vino l-ore uti, L.; munera, Hor.; messis, Ov.; alimentum, Pn.; epulum l-simum, Su.; cadus vini spes donare novas l-us, Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rik:</text:span></text:span> l-us opum, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frikostig, gifmild, rundhändt:</text:span></text:span> duo sunt genera l-orum, quorum alteri prodigi, alteri liberales; l-um esse in alqm, C.; animo l-us, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Large</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Largĭter</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>(Largĭtus, Afr.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rikt, rikligt, ymnigt; frikostigt, rundligen, liberalt:</text:span></text:span> pastum animantibus l-e natura comparavit; l-e effuseque, munifice et l-e dare; l-sime copia facta; de judicio l-ter remissum esse, C.; non solum domi, sed etiam apud finitimas civitates l-ter poterat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förmådde mycket),</text:span> Cs.; l-e bibere, Col.; I-e sufficere, Pn.; l-ter vini (= abunde), Pt.; potus l-ius æquo, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Largĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Riklig:</text:span></text:span> Lucr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Largĭfluus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rikligt flödande:</text:span></text:span> imber, Pacuv ap. C.; fons, Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Largĭlŏquus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pratsam:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Largio</text:span>, 4. = largior <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(arch. och poet.):</text:span> Acc., Tib.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Largior</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skänka; gifwa rundligt, frikostigt; slösa på; beskära:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> coenam esurientibus, Pt.; de se <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af sitt),</text:span> Ter.; de alieno; inconsulte; illud genus l-di, quod a liberalitate proficiscitur; sunt multi, qui eripiunt aliis, quod aliis l-antur; Hortensio natura summam copiam facultatemque dicendi l-ta est, C.; honores alicui, Hor.; munera alicui, Ppt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra utdelningar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (åt folket):</text:span> nonnumquam est l-dum, C.; plebem l-do incendere, Sa. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Erbjuda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af godhet, nåd), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">unna, förunna, tillstädja:</text:span></text:span> se ultro (amanti), Pt.; amori nostro plus, quam concedit veritas, largiare; istam libertatem alicui, ut - -; si quis deus mihi l-atur, ut ex hac ætate repuerascam, recusem, C.; habenas equo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fria tyglar),</text:span> Sil. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Efterskänka, medgifwa frihet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från ngt:</text:span> duo illa relinquamus et l-amur inertiæ nostræ, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Largītio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skänkande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frikostigt gifwande, frikostighet:</text:span></text:span> l., quæ fit ex re familiari, fontem ipsum benignitatis exhaurit; l. fundum non habet, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skänker, utdelning, spendering,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ändamål att winna ngn för sina intressen; äfwen i sämsta mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mutande, mutor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wid röstgifning):</text:span> redimere militum voluntates l-e, Cs.; consectari benevolentiam alicujus l-e,; l. munerum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af fester, trakteringar o. d. åt folket);</text:span> res major et utilior populari l-e acquiritur; tota ratio talium l-um genere vitiosa est, temporibus necessaria; l-is suspicionem recipere, C.; l. vigebat, Sa.; populus corruptus est l-e magistratuum, N.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Largītor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rund gifware,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. gifwer l. utdelar frikostigt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> prædæ, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. gör utdelningar (i egennyttigt syfte, spenderare, mutare):</text:span> in republica exsistunt l-es et factiosi; prodigi et l-es, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Largītor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frikostigt gifwa:</text:span></text:span> Pt. Ps. III. 3. 14. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Ritschl läser</text:span> largiri).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Largĭtas</text:span>, ātis <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ymnighet, frikostighet, rundhet:</text:span></text:span> nimia, Ter.; terra fundit fruges cum maxima l-e; l. muneris tui, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Largĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: id.: N. ap. Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlargior</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slösaktigt utdela, kringkasta, bortskänka:</text:span></text:span> omnia, C.; foedera sociis, T. - bonis d-itis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i pass. bet.),</text:span> Gracch. ap. Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlargior</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bortskänka:</text:span></text:span> Ps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prælargus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mycket ymnig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stor:</text:span></text:span> pulmo, Ps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>argus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cognomen i</text:span> gens Scribonia. <text:line-break/>Largiānus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lārĭdum</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lardum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fläsk:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Larifuga <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lar.<text:line-break/>Larignus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Larix.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ārīnum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Italien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lārīnas, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ārissa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. stadsnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lārissæus, <text:line-break/>Lārissensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ārius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sjö (Como-sjön).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lărix,</text:span> ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">c.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lärkträd:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lărignus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>artius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>arcius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Larva,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mask, skråpuksansigte:</text:span></text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spöke, gast:</text:span></text:span> Pt.; l-as, sagas, insomnia vatum ridere, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Larvālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spöklik:</text:span></text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Larvātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förhexad:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăsănum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kärl</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för köket l. andra ändamål:</text:span> Hor., Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lascīvus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Yr, lekfull, leksen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (kelen); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lös, lössläppt:</text:span></text:span> mālo me Galatea petit, l-a puella; l-a capella, Vg.; grex (capellarum); hedera <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. liks. lekfullt l. kelet slingrar sig kring träden);</text:span> ætas decentius l-a; ludentem decent verba l-a, Hor.; l-ior hædo, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. och oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kitslig, näswis, sjelfswåldig, framfusig;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">munwig, lösmunt:</text:span></text:span> tibi vellunt barbari l-i pueri, Hor.; viator, Varr.; Siculi, Qu. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lättfärdig, lösaktig, liderlig:</text:span></text:span> l-a licentia, Hor.; amor, Tib.; pagina l-a est mihi, vita proba, Mt.; picturæ l-simæ, Su.; l. in vino; jocus, Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om språk och stil: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utswäfwande:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lascīve</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lössluppet, fritt, lättfärdigt:</text:span></text:span> loqui, Mt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lascīvia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Yrhet, lekfullhet, lös-släppt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fritt skämt; yra upptåg; lustighet:</text:span></text:span> piscium, Pacuv. ap. C.; delphini, Pn. ep.; hilaritas, l., risus, jocus, C.; (Lupercalibus) nudi juvenes - per lusum ac l-am currebant, L.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerdåd, sjelfswåld, fräckhet:</text:span></text:span> militum, L.; populi theatralis l. T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lösaktighet, utswäfning, otukt:</text:span></text:span> Veneris, Ov.; l-æ recentes notæ, Su.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i fråga om stil: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Yppighet,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwerdrifwen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sirlighet:</text:span></text:span> recentis hujus l-æ flosculi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> antiquitatis horridum et jejunum genus), Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lascīvio</text:span>, 4.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara yr</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hoppa), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">leksen; leka, skalkas, rasa:</text:span></text:span> pecudes, Col.; agnus, Ov.; pisces, L.; capellæ, Ap.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Leka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">öfwa sjelfswåld, yra, wara wild:</text:span></text:span> (populo) licet l-re in pace et in otio, - ut in navi ac sæpe etiam in morbo levi, C.; l-re plebem magis quam sævire, L.; districtis non vacat l-re, Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i fråga om stil: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pjollra, leka, utswäfwa:</text:span></text:span> puerilibus sententiolis l-re aut immodico tumore turgescere; licentiā, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lascīvībundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Yr:</text:span></text:span> Pt. (al.: lixabundus).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lascīvŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: manus, Læv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăser,</text:span> ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăserpītium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en wiß wäxt och deß saft (dyfwelsträck):</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăserpītiātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: acetum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(försatt med l.),</text:span> Cato.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăserpītĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: Cyrenæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. frambringar l.),</text:span> Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lassus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trött, uttröttad:</text:span></text:span> opere; de via, Pt.; animus, Ter.; aures; l. maris et viarum, Hor.; l-a resedit Creūsa; papavera l-o collo demisere caput, Vg.; l. studio venandi; viā, Ov.; terra l-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utsugad),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lassesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bli trött, uttärd:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlassesco</text:span>, 3.: id.: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lassĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trötthet:</text:span></text:span> ex l-e arctius dormire; nulla l. officium et fidem impedire debet, C.; l-em sedare; acquiescere a l-e, N.; l-e exanimatus, Cs.; ira ac spes prædæ plus quam l. poterat, Sa.; recreare l-em, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lasso</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trötta, uttrötta:</text:span></text:span> labor me; sequendo l-ta; Ov.; numina precibus, Luc.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T2">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bli trött) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sjunka:</text:span></text:span> fundamenta domus, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlasso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uttrötta:</text:span></text:span> loquacem Fabium, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prædēlasso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I förwäg trötta, förswaga:</text:span></text:span> incursus aquarum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bryta),</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prælassātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på förhand uttröttad:</text:span> Frontin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lassŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Något trött:</text:span></text:span> Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lastaurus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">otuktig person:</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Late <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lātus.<text:line-break/>Latebr . . ., Latens, -tenter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lateo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăteo,</text:span> ui, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ligga dold, förborgad:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wara osynlig, gömd, osedd:</text:span> in tenebris l.; inclusum atque abditum l-re in occulto, C.; sub tecto, Pt.; in alvo matris, Hor.; in silvis abditum l-re, Cs.; anguis in herba, Vg.; apud amicum l-uit Atticus; res in conspectu exercitus gerebatur, ut nullum paulo fortius factum l-re posset, C.; N.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blifwa obekant, okänd; ej röjas:</text:span></text:span> verum in occulto l-et; causæ; scelus in diuturna obscuritate; sensus in aliquo, C.; causa l-et, Vg.; res patrem l-et, Ov.; res l-et alqm, N.; alicui, Luc.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">impers.:</text:span> l-et, qua ratione id consecutus sit, N.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lefwa obemärkt:</text:span></text:span> bene qui l-uit, bene vixit, Ov. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dölja sig = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Söka skydd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> under:</text:span> sub umbra amicitiæ Romanæ l., L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hålla sig undan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från en rättegång:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om en mening, afsigt o. d.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ligga dold, dölja sig, ligga under:</text:span></text:span> sub nomine pacis bellum l-et; insidiæ l-ent in simulatione officii, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förborgad:</text:span></text:span> res, C.; causa, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătĕbra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gömställe, gömsle, smyghål, lön-rum,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> undangömd </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wrå:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> non intelligo, quæ in balneis l. togatis hominibus esse possit; Mithridates se l-is Cappadociæ occultare non vult; conjuratio ex tenebris atque ex l-is erupit, C.; cavæ l-æ (equi Trojani), Vg.; l-æ dulces (ɔ: Sabinum meum), Hor.; ferarum, L.; silvarum, Ct.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smyghål, mörk wrå:</text:span></text:span> videant, ne quæratur l-a perjurio; in l-am se conjicere; adhibere l-am obscuritatis; dare l-am populo (i. e. tabellam), qua occultaret vitiosum suffragium; in animis hominum magnæ l-æ sunt; l-æ suspicionum, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătĕbrĭcŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. håller sig på mörka (mißtänkta) ställen:</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătĕbrōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Full af smyghål</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">gömställen;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lönlig:</text:span></text:span> locus, L.; pumex, Vg.; via, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătĕbrōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lönligt:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hemligen, oförmärkt:</text:span></text:span> amare, Ov.; res l. efficitur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hålla sig dold:</text:span> C. poēt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătĭbŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gömställe, mörk wrå:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> l. occultorum locorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för skepp);</text:span> volo emere aliquod l., perfugium doloris mei, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: djurs </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Håla, kula, bo:</text:span></text:span> feræ l-is se tegunt; serpens e l-is se infert; ea, quæ ad vivendum sunt necessaria, ut pastus, l-a, alia generis ejusdem, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătĭbŭlo</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătĭbŭlor</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hålla sig dold:</text:span> Acc., Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hålla sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hållas dold; smyga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hålla sig undan:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> alicui, Pt.; errans l-ansque extremas Galliæ regiones petivit, Cs.; rupe, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: hålla sig l. smyga undan från rättegång:</text:span> l-vit, procuratorem nullum reliquit; l. ac ludificare, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătĭtĭtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>(<text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlĭteo</text:span>, inc. l. Pn., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och)</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlĭtesco</text:span>, tui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gömma sig undan, hålla sig dold:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> bestiæ in cubilibus, C.; hostes in silvis, Cs.; in ulva d-ui, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = söka undflykt, förswar:</text:span> in tam frigida calumnia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ordrytteri);</text:span> in auctoritate alicujus, C.; sub umbra alicujus, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Interlăteo</text:span>, ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara dold emellan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oblĭtesco</text:span>, tui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dölja, gömma sig bakom</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> sidera a nostro aspectu, C.; in rimis, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Perlăteo</text:span>, ui, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förblifwa dold:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăter,</text:span> ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wanl. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span>):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tegelsten, bränd sten:</text:span></text:span> in l-e, ex quo urbs effecta est, C.; coquere, Cato; ducere, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Guld-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">siilfwertackor:</text:span></text:span> aurei, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătĕrāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fogning (eg. af tegelsten), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Structur:</text:span></text:span> calor rarefacit l-a vasis, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătĕrārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: terra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tegelstensjord),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătĕrāria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tegelbruk:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătĕrārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tegelslagare:</text:span></text:span> Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătercŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tegelsten:</text:span></text:span> facere l-os, Cato; struere alqd coctili l-o, Ct.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bakelse:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătĕrĭcius</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Lătĕrĭtius), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är af tegelsten, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tegel-, tegelmurad:</text:span></text:span> murus, Cs.; paries, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lateralis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lătus.<text:line-break/>Lateramen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Later.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ătĕrānus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på en romersk familj.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Laterarius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Later <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Lătus. <text:line-break/>Laterculus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Later.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ătĕrensis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Latericius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Later.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lātĕrīna</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lātĕritiāna</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags päron:</text:span> Pn., Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lāterna</text:span> <text:line-break/>(lanterna), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lykta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> lantarna:</text:span> C., Pt., Mt., Juv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lāternārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lyktbärare</text:span></text:span> (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">drabant):</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Latesco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lateo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lătex,</text:span> ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: (poēt. fere): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wätska</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (watten, win, mjölk, saft):</text:span> calidus; sacri; l-um honorem libavit in mensam, Vg.; meri, Ov.; gelidi, C.; absinthii, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Latialis, -aris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Latium.<text:line-break/>Latibul . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lateo.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Laticlavius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Clavus. <text:line-break/>Latifundium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lātus.<text:line-break/>Latin . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Latium. <text:line-break/>Latio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fero.<text:line-break/>Latitatio, -tito <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lateo.<text:line-break/>Latitudo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lātus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ătium, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den del af Italien (mellan Etrurien och Campanien), hwari Rom är beläget; meton.</text:span> =<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">latinskt språk (i mots. till hufwudstadens, Roms):</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. = jus Latii, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">de politiska rättigheter, s. urspr. tillhörde Latinarne:</text:span> T. <text:line-break/>Lătiālis, <text:line-break/>Lătiāris, <text:line-break/>Lătius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ătīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: lingua, sermo, literæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(latinskt språk och romersk literatur,</text:span> C.; via L-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. gick öfwer Albanerbergen),</text:span> L.; in L-um convertere aliquid, C. <text:line-break/>Lătīni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Latinarne l. de, s. åtnjöto deras politiska rättigheter (i mots. till Romarne):</text:span> nostri minus student literis quam L-i; senatus populusque Romanus, socii atque L-i, C.<text:line-break/>Lătīnæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span> = Latinæ feriæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fest på</text:span> Mons Albanus): C.<text:line-break/>Lătīne, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: scire, nescire <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kunna</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förstå och tala rätt latin);</text:span> l. loqui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rent, correct, stundom = tydligt),</text:span> C. <text:line-break/>Lătīnĭtas, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(latinskhet i språket), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rent, correct latin:</text:span></text:span> l. est, quæ sermonem purum conservat ab omni vitio remotum; auctor l-is, C.<text:line-break/>b. = jus Latii: C., Su. <text:line-break/>Lătīniensis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">latinsk.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ătīnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. konung i Latium.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>atmus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Latmos, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Carien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Latmĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>āto, us (Varr.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ātōna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Apollos och Dianas moder.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lātŏĭdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lātōis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">patronymica.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lātōĭus, <text:line-break/>Lātōnĭus, <text:line-break/>Lātōus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lātōnĭgĕna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">c.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Latonas son l. dotter.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>atobrīgi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Latovīci, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">galliskt folk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Latomiæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lautumiæ.<text:line-break/>Lator <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fero. <text:line-break/>Latrat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lātro.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lātrīna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg.</text:span> lavatrina?):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bad-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">twättställe:</text:span></text:span> Lucil.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afträde:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lātro,</text:span> 1.: [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">första stafwelsen är lång, utom</text:span> Phdr. V. 10. 7, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">der L. Mueller</text:span> (Ed. 1870) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">läser</text:span> Lăcon, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Avien. Arat. 283]: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skälla, gläfsa; skälla på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. om hunds läte:</text:span> luce l-ant canes; canes, qui et l-re et mordere possunt; l-ant jam quidam oratores, non loquuntur, C.; multum lātrante Lycisca, Vg.; canes senem, Hor.; is l-atur a canibus, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om mskor: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skria:</text:span></text:span> clamator, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om döda ting: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bullra, tjuta:</text:span></text:span> lātrantibus undis, Vg.; undæ, Sil.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Storma;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">pocka på, fordra:</text:span></text:span> stomachus, Hor.; pectus, St.; nil aliud l-at natura, Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lātrans</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hund:</text:span></text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lātrātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. skäller, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skällande; skräflare, smädare:</text:span></text:span> lātrator Anubis, Vg.; rabula l-que, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lātrātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skällande, skall:</text:span></text:span> lātratu trifauci; canum, Vg., Ct.; l-bus canum agi, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allātro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skälla på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brusa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot:</text:span> Oceanus interna maria, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skälla på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utfara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot:</text:span> alqm l. alqd, Col., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Circumlātro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kringskälla; skälla omkring:</text:span></text:span> aliquem, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collātro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skälla på, nedskälla:</text:span></text:span> philosophiam, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlātro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(framskälla), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Säga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ropa ut,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (klämma fram med):</text:span> quod placet; acriter elātrem, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illātro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skälla), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skria, ropa till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> per terræ rimas Mānibus illātrat, Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oblātro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skälla, bjebba, ropa emot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> alicui, Sen.; oblātrat vulgus - senatum, Sil.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oblātrātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som skäller l. bjebbar mot ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Byracka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om en hustru),</text:span> Pt. Mil. 681.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lătro,</text:span> ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lego-)</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Soldat, knekt;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">legotrupper:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> cogere l-es alicui, Pt. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Knektar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = pjeser l. brickor i ett slags - brädspel:</text:span> l-um proelia ludere, Ov.; vitreus l., Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stråtröfware, bandit, fribytare:</text:span></text:span> viator a l-e occiditur; Bardylis, Illyrius l., C.; ut jugulent hominem, surgunt de nocte lătrones; (leges scriptæ) ne quis fur esset neu lātro, neu quis adulter, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătrōcĭnium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">krigstjenst med friskaror l. ss. legd knekt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Krig:</text:span></text:span> Pt. ap. Non.; imago l-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i brädspel),</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stråtröfweri, fribyteri:</text:span></text:span> ex insidiis occultis ad apertum l-um conjecimus (Catilinam); id, quod a te scelerate susceptum est, l. potius quam bellum nominatur; tueri fines a l-is, C. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Röfware-band:</text:span></text:span> ex tanto l-o unus tollitur, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bofstreck, wåldsbragd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (plundring):</text:span> furtim et per l-a ad imperia et honores niti, Sa.; l., non judicium (in causa S. Roscii), C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătrōcĭnālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Röfware-:</text:span></text:span> castra, Amm.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătrōcĭnor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjena för sold:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drifwa stråt-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sjöröfweri; röfwa, råna:</text:span></text:span> in via Appia impune, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om djur:</text:span> pisces, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătrōcĭnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stråtröfweri:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătruncŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Soldat</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">knekt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i brädspelet:</text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(usel) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stråtröfware:</text:span></text:span> mastrucati Sardiniæ l-i, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătruncŭ</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T3">ārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: tabula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för brädspel):</text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Latumiæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lautumiæ.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lătus,</text:span> ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af l. om ngt:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. del af en mskas l. ett djurs kropp:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> in equi l-bus fores erant; l. alicujus mucrone petere; l-i ensem accingere, C.; l. haurire alicujus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(genomborra),</text:span> L.; l-i (suo) ensem accommodare; mutare fessum l. (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wända sig);</text:span> l-i alicujus ensem abdere, Vg.; l. alicujus fodicare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stöta - i);</text:span> l. alicujus tegere (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gå till wenster om -);</text:span> l-um dolor, Hor.; claudere l. alicujus, Juv.; discedere tecto l-e, Ter.; præbere apertum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> nudum l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gifwa hugg på sig),</text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lungor, bröst,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (röst), serskildt med afseende på styrkan deraf:</text:span> legem suadere bonis l-bus; hæc sunt valentiorum l-um; ex l-bus nobilitari, C.; vox et l., Qu., Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af döda ting:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> insulæ, Cs.; Fibrenus hæc l-a (insulæ) alluit; terræ l-a, C.; haud procul a l-e castelli, Sa.; montem impulit in l-us; l-um (navis) compages; dextrum Scylla l., lævum - Charybdis tenet, Vg.; campi, Ov.; quod l. mundi nebulæ malusque Jupiter urget, Hor. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af en här: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flank, flygel:</text:span></text:span> equites ad l-a disponere; naves ad l-us constituere; l-e aperto aggredi, Cs.; agminis, L.; l-bus circumvenire, Sa.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sida,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm. i beteckningar för en saks ställning till en annan; för närhet, omgifning förtrolighet o. d.:</text:span> sedere ad l. alicujus; a l-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från sidan, mots.</text:span> a fronte, tergo), C., Cs; ab omni l-e perspici, Pn.; ex l-bus aggredi, ab l-e alicui incurrere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(falla i flanken),</text:span> Sa.; a l-e alicujus nunquam discedere, C.; adhærere l-i alicujus, L.; a l-e alicujus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ngns wän, förtrogne),</text:span> L., Ct.; meum l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(min wän),</text:span> Mt. <text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i fråga om slägtskap:</text:span> a meo tuoque l-e, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătĕrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: dolor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i sidan, bröstet),</text:span> Lucil.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătĕrārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: tigna <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sidobjelkar),</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lătuscŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: laneum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wek)</text:span> l. manusque mollicellæ, Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lātus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bred:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bred:</text:span></text:span> via; fossa; mare; unguem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> digitum l-um a recta conscientia non discedere, C.; l-i humeri; l-um os fenestræ, Vg.; l-us pectore, Ov.; murus quinquaginta pedes l., Pn.; clavus, Su.; vir <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skuldre-bred),</text:span> Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Widsträckt, wid:</text:span></text:span> fines; agri, Cs.; campus; fundi; regna, Vg.; regnum, L. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bred</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om uttalet):</text:span> verba, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Widlyftig, omfattande; widt utbredd:</text:span></text:span> oratio; locus; disputatio, C.; gloria, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Widt och bredt, wida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> omkring:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentl. uttryck:</text:span> l. longeque peregrinari; ager l-sime continuatus; nomen l. manat, vagatur; laus l. longeque diffusa, C.; prædæ l-ius actæ, L.; imperium l. valet; l. ire fuga et formido <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sprider sig),</text:span> Sa.; l. patent fines; fama l-ius percrebruit, Cs.; litora fervere l. vidit, Vg.; l. tyrannus, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. uttr.:</text:span> ars (juris civilis) l. patet; ea patent l-sime <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hafwa den widsträcktaste practiska anwändning l. betydelse),</text:span> quæ a philosophis de officiis tradita sunt; decorum l. fusum est, C.; l. perscribere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(widlyftigt),</text:span> Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lātĭfundium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: (fundus): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stort landtgods:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lātĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bredd, bredhet:</text:span></text:span> lineamentum sine ulla l-e; humerorum (boum) l-es ad aratra extrahenda natæ, C.; fines Helvetiorum in l-em CLXXX milia passuum patebant, Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utsträckning, widsträckthet:</text:span></text:span> possessionum, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bredhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i uttal:</text:span> verborum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Widlyftighet:</text:span></text:span> Platonica, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collātātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utwidgad, widlyftig:</text:span></text:span> C. (inc. l.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlāto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utbreda, utwidga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> manum; pulmones spiritu se d-ant; imperium; fines imperii, C.; aciem, L. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bredt uttala:</text:span></text:span> literas, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Widlyftigt framställa, utbreda:</text:span></text:span> hæc, quæ d-antur a nobis, Zeno sic premebat; orationem; argumentum, C.<text:line-break/>c. virtus crescere non potest, d-ari <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till graden l. till omfånget af sin werksamhet utbreda sig)</text:span> potest, C.<text:line-break/>d. legem in cunctum ordinem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utwidga, utsträcka),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illātābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som saknar bredd:</text:span> (linea), Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Perlāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: vis verbi p. patet, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Latusculum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lătus.<text:line-break/>Lavacrum, Lavatio, -vatrina <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lavo.<text:line-break/>Laud . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Laus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăver,</text:span> ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en wattenwäxt:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ăverna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romersk gndomlighet.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lavici <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Labici.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>āvīnia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">n. pr.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>āvīnium, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Latium.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lāvīniensis, <text:line-break/>Lāvīnius, <text:line-break/>Lāvīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lăvo,</text:span> lāvi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> lăvāvi, lōtum (lautum), lăvātum, lăvāre <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> lăvĕre,<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och 3.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twå, twätta, bada, skölja:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> <text:line-break/>1. i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twätta:</text:span></text:span> lavito, Cato; manus l-a et coena; l-tum accumbere, C.; alqd in fonte, Vg.; alqd aquā, Ov.; corpus frigentis l., Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bada, bada sig:</text:span></text:span> lavari (<text:span text:style-name="T2">refl.</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> lavare (<text:span text:style-name="T2">intr.</text:span>): l-ri in fluminibus, Cs.; lavatum ire, Hor.; l-antem aggredi alqm, Su.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skölja, bespola, afskölja:</text:span></text:span> ora lacrimis, Vg.; mare lavit arenas, Ov.; cruorem; vulnera, Vg. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bortskölja; afskölja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (försona):</text:span> mala vino lavere, Hor.; peccatum, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lautus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snygg:</text:span></text:span> cibus, Ter.; homo; servi l-ores, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Riklig, präktig, ståtlig;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om personer: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rik, fin, förnäm</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (gentil),:</text:span> coena magnifica et l-a; l-a supellex; l-a patrimonia; l-a civitas, C.; esse in re aucta et bene l-a, Ter.; convivium, Pn.; valde jam l. es, C.; eques, N. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i moralisk men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ädel, wacker:</text:span></text:span> liberalitas l-ior et viro claro dignior, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lābrum</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> lau-brum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> lavabrum), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rund</text:span>t) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twättbäcken</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">-fat,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarur man öfwergöt sig efter warmt bad:</text:span> l. si in balneo non est, fac ut sit, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">abstr.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bad, badning:</text:span></text:span> nec Dryadas nec nos videamus l-a Dianæ, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bäcken, kittel, rundt kar:</text:span></text:span> marmoreum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(under ett springwatten),</text:span> Pn.; l-a ahena, Vg.; spumat plenis vindemia l-is, Vg.; ficos in l-a fictilia vel lapidea congerere, Col.; l. olearium, vinarium; oleum (pressum) in l-um indito: inde in dolium, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăbellum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Litet badkar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bäcken:</text:span></text:span> C. de Leg. II. 26.; fictile, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăvācrum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bad:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăvātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twättning; bad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> och </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillbehör dertill:</text:span></text:span> Cic. ap. Col.; certiorem me facias, ut l. parata sit, C.; Phdr.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bad-ort:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lăvātrīna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">inrättning för bad:</text:span></text:span> ubi lavatur, antiqui non balneum, sed l-am appellare consueverant, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laute</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ståtligt, förnämt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (gentilt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">praktfullt:</text:span></text:span> vestitus, Pt.; villa ædificata l-ius; deversari l., C.; vivere, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ståtligt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förträffligt; ädelt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (nobelt):</text:span> ludificari et emungere alqm l-sime, poēt. ap. C.; munus administrare, Ter.; res domesticas et familiares et melius et l-ius nos tuemur (quam Græci), C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lautia</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Underhåll</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt främmande makters sändebud i Rom:</text:span> loca, l. præbere legatis, L.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lautĭtia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ståt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (gentillesse) (i mat, kläder o. s. w.):</text:span> mea nova l.; tua illa vetus l., C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lautiuscŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">temligen präktig:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lōmentum</text:span> (lav-mentum), i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skur-, twätt-, reningsmedel;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec. ett slags </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mjöl af bönor:</text:span></text:span> Mt. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: -</text:span> Appius censor acerrime agit. - Persuasum ei est, censuram l. et nitrum esse. Errare mihi videtur: nam, dum sordes eluere vult, viscera aperit, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ett färgämne:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lōtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twätt, twättning:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lōtūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twätt, bad:</text:span></text:span> Pn., Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Circumlăvo</text:span>, 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och 3.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kring-skölja:</text:span></text:span> insula fluctibus c-itur, Sa.; Nilus Aegyptum c-at, Hyg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlăvo</text:span>, lāvi, (lautum), lōtum, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aftwå, rentwå:</text:span></text:span> alqd, Col.<text:line-break/>b. se aliqua re = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förlora:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illautus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illōtus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(illūtus, Cato), <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Otwagen:</text:span></text:span> manibus i-otis tractare alqd, Pt.; i-ota toralia, Hor.; i-autus, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prælăvo</text:span>, 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och 3.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förut skölja:</text:span></text:span> Ap. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prælautus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">owanligt ståtlig, fin:</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Laurea, -reatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Laurus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>aurens, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">pl.</text:span> -rentes, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">laurentisk, Laurenter, inwånare i</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>aurentum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Latium.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Laurentīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Laurentīnum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">landställe wid L.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Laurentius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Laurus,</text:span> i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lager:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">träd:</text:span></text:span> fessum latus depone sub l-u mea, Hor.; arbor simillima l-o, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lager</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = l-krans l. -qwist:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. symbol af seger:</text:span> hæc mea l. incurrit in oculos malevolorum, C.; tibi l. peperit æternos honores, Hor.; victrices l-i, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. helgad åt Apollo (ss. poesiens, reningens gud):</text:span> arbor eris certe, dixit (Apollo), mea: semper habebunt te coma, te citharæ, te nostræ, laure, pharetræ, Ov.; l-um momordisse <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hafwa rönt poetisk inspiration);</text:span> lustrari l-o, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laurētum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lagerlund:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laureus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är af lager, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lager-:</text:span></text:span> corona, L.; ramus, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deraf</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laurea</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lagerträd:</text:span></text:span> l. ramis annuit; cana l., Ov. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lager</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = lagerkrans l. -qwist ss. symbol af triumph l. för Apollos makt och skydd:</text:span> concedat l. linguæ (cedant arma togæ); l-æ cupidus; in Capitolium invehi cum insigni l-a, C.; l-am (= triumphum) deportare, T.; l-ā donandus Apollinari, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laureātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lagerbekransad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. prydd med lager ss. tecken till seger, glädje:</text:span> lictor; fasces; imagines l-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(anbilder, med anledning af utnämning till consul),</text:span> C.; literæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bref om seger),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laureŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten lager</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (triumph):</text:span> tantum habui negotii, quod esset ad l-am satis; - in mustaceo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i småsaker)</text:span> l-am quærere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laurĭcŏmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: (coma): montes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med hår af lager, lagerhöljda, jfr</text:span> comæ silvarum), Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laurĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. bär lager:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. terra, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lagerbekransad, lagerprydd:</text:span> Luc.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laurĭger</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: Apollo, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laurīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är af lager, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lager-:</text:span></text:span> oleum; folium, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Laus,</text:span> laudis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Beröm, loford</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (erkännande), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">pris, lof, berömmelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ära):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg., i subj. men.:</text:span> omnes trahimur studio l-is; l-em quærere, comparare aliqua re; assequi, consequi, adipisci ex re; l-em tribuere alicui; l-e afficere; l-bus efferre, ornare, illustrare, ad cælum extollere alqm; res habet l-em, est l-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(är föremål för, förtjenar);</text:span> in l-e ponere alqd; dare alicui alqd l-i; l. continentiæ, dignitatis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för);</text:span> l-um mearum adversarius et obtrectator, C.; l-em ferre <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(winna),</text:span> parere (id.); l-bus ferre, prosequi alqm; l. bellica, Cs.; l-is avidus, Sa.; semper honos nomenque tuum l-esque manebunt, Vg.; obterere l-em alicujus, N.; petere l-em; principibus placuisse viris non ultima l. est, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">obj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wärde; förtjenst; berömlig handling</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bragd:</text:span></text:span> virtutis omnis l. in actione consistit; brevitas l. est interdum; bellicis l-bus abundare; l-i honores habiti sunt, C.; sunt hic etiam sua præmia l-i, Vg.; suas l-es concedere alicui, L.; esse <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(höra till)</text:span> in magnis l-bus, N.; casei, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laudĭcoenus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: (coena: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sammansättningen enligt grekisk form): (s. prisar måltiden), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snyltgäst:</text:span></text:span> Pn. ep.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laudo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Berömma, prisa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med ord) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">upphöja; utweckla ngns förtjenster:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. och i allm.:</text:span> l. Platonem; jure l. propter virtutem; l. philosophiam et, quanta ejus vis sit, expromere; l. alqd pro dignitate; pleno ore; cum exceptione; l-ri a laudato viro, C.; virtutem alicujus, Cs.; l-do extollere suum studium; et qui fecere et qui facta aliorum scripsere, l-antur, Sa.; l-bunt alii claram Rhodon aut Mitylenen; brachia alicujus, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. l. oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hålla loftal,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sersk. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">liktal,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer någon:</text:span> pater l-vit filium scripto meo; a te l-ta est Popilia; patruum l., C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">officielt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Yttra sig, wittna till förmon för, anbefalla:</text:span></text:span> legem; sententiam alicujus, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åberopa, nämna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. wittne, sagesman l. auctoritet:</text:span> Jovem testem, Pt.; auctores certissimos; rerum Romanarum auctorem religiosissimum l-re alqm, C. - l. priscā linguā est nominare, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laudātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(berömd), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Berömlig, priswärd, lofwärd; utmärkt, herrlig:</text:span></text:span> vir; artes, C.; forma, virgo l-sima, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laudāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Berömligt:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laudābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Berömlig, berömwärd; god:</text:span></text:span> honestum, etiamsi a nullo laudatur, naturā est l-e; res; vir l-ior, C.; vinum, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laudābĭlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: vivere, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laudātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Berömmande, prisande; beröm:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> quam lauream cum tua l-e conferrem?, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Berömmande wittnesmål, intyg, yttrande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (adreß) för ngn, serskildt en sakegande:</text:span> civitates ad judicium legationem cum gravissima l-e miserunt; l. Cluentii ex decurionum Larinatium decreto, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Loftal,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> isynn. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">liktal:</text:span></text:span> mortuorum l-es; ornare l-e; funebris l.; efferri spoliatum imaginibus, pompa, l-e, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laudātīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. innehåller l. går ut på beröm, berömmande:</text:span> Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laudātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prisare, lofordare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (förordare): </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> pacis; voluptatis l., C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. prisar ngn, wittnar till ngns förmon, i synn. i uppdrag från en provins l. commun:</text:span> populus Gaditanus ad judicium legavit hujus testes juris, vitæ l-es, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Loftalare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer en afliden:</text:span> funera duo ducit, idem in utroque l., L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laudātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: virtutis l. fama popularis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allaudo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prisa:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allaudābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Berömlig:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collaudo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Samfäldt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">högt berömma, öfwerhopa med loford:</text:span></text:span> non cohortandus, sed magis c-dus videtur; alqd, C.; virtutem alicujus; milites c-ti sunt, Cs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collaudātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlaudo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwerdrifwet prisa?):</text:span> C. Ep. ad Att. VI. 2. 9. (inc. l.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illaudātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oberömd; oberömlig:</text:span></text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illaudābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oberömlig:</text:span></text:span> G ell., St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>aus, Laudis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad (Lodi).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>āus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Laute, -tia, -titia, -tiusculus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lavo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>autŭlæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ort i Latium.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lautŭmĭæ</text:span> <text:line-break/>(lātomiæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>lātumiæ), ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: v. gr. (λατομίαι): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stenbrott,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec. ss. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">straff-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">arbetshus; fängelse:</text:span></text:span> in l-as ire, Pt.; in l-as conjici, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lautŭmĭus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: carcer, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lautus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lavo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Laxus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slak, lös</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. ej sitter åt l. hårdt):</text:span> modo contento, modo l-o fune laborat, Hor.; l-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(loßnad)</text:span> compages laterum navis; et premere et dare l-as habenas, Vg.; l. arcus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(afspänd),</text:span> Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wid, rymlig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i eg. men.:</text:span> ager; spatia, Col.; calceus, Hor.; <text:soft-page-break/>domus, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> quam l-simas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wida, ej hårdt åtdragne)</text:span> habere habenas amicitiæ, quas aut adducas aut remittas, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. om tid l. saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lös, slapp, rymlig, riklig:</text:span></text:span> imperium, Sa.; fides, Sil.; statuere alicui diem satis l-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(termin),</text:span> C.; annona l-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> arta), L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laxe</text:span>, -ius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Löst; rymligt:</text:span></text:span> fluitare, Luc.; habitare, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slappt:</text:span></text:span> Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Långt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i tiden), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rikligt:</text:span></text:span> diem l-ius proferre, C.; l-ius vivere, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laxĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slakhet, slapphet; rymlighet:</text:span></text:span> fidium, C.; in domo principis viri adhibenda est cura l-is, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laxo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra slapp, släppa efter; lossa, lösa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (öppna);</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> habenas, Ct.; nervos, Pn.; compages se l-ant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(loßna),</text:span> Ct.; vincula epistolæ, N.; catenas, Luc.; claustra, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> habenas cupiditatibus l-re; vincla conjunctionis l-ri alqd velim; a libidinum vinculis l-re, C.; via vix tandem voci l-ta dolori, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Widga, göra rymlig, utwidga, utrymma</text:span></text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skaffa plats åt ngn någorstädes:</text:span> forum, C.; foros (navis), Vg.; ordines l-ti <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öppnade),</text:span> T. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om saker) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slappa; lindra, lätta, förswaga, göra mindre sträng</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">knapp:</text:span></text:span> custodia, pugna l-atur; alqd laboris fesso; annonam, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tiden: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppskjuta:</text:span></text:span> fugæ tempus, Sen.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer l. deras kropp l. sinne: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lösa, wederqwicka; förströ, muntra:</text:span></text:span> curis l-ri; se molestiis, C.; artus quies l-at; membra quiete l-antur, Vg.; animum a laboribus, L.; argute illuso adversario l-re judicum animos et a severitate ad risum traducere, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laxātus</text:span>, -ior, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lossad, lös:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laxāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lösning, -het; rymlighet:</text:span></text:span> ventris, Mcb.; Vitr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Eftergift; lättnad, lindring:</text:span></text:span> ne legi quidem l-i quidquam per tribunos datur, C.; lex non habet l., L.; in navigatione nactus sum pusillum l-i, C.; curarum l-a, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laxātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utwidgning:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collaxo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Widga:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōlixus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Comp.</text:span> -ior: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lång, widsträckt, utsträckt, långsträckt, widlyftig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> capillus, Ter.; barba, Vg. (d. l.); arator, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tid: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lång:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frikostig, rund, rundhändt, liberal:</text:span></text:span> de tua p-a beneficaque natura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> angusta) alqd limavit hic annus propter tristitiam temporum; Ariobarzanes non est p-ior in Pompejum per ipsum, quam per me in Brutum. Est autem perpauper, C. (Ep. ad Att. II. 3.).<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om förhållanden: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gynnsam:</text:span></text:span> Cato, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōlixe</text:span>, -ius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Långsträckt; widlyftigt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rundt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rikligt, frikostigt, wälwilligt:</text:span></text:span> arbores p. foliatæ, Ap. - accipere alqm, Ter.; facere; promittere, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prōlixĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Längd:</text:span></text:span> Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕlaxo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra lös igen; göra slapp, slak</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (nedspänna), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lossa; göra rymlig, utwidga:</text:span></text:span> alvus tum constringitur, tum r-atur, C.; humum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(upplösa, göra lucker),</text:span> Col.; arcum, Sen.; vincula, Ov.; vias, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lösgöra, göra lös</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ledig; wederqwicka, förströ, mildra;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">gifwa efter:</text:span></text:span> se occupationibus, corporis vinculis; animum somno, doctrinā; r. animum et dare se jucunditati; severitatem r., C.; dolor dat intervalla et r-at, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕlaxātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wederqwickelse, lindring:</text:span></text:span> animi; (curæ), C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lea, Leæna <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Leo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ēander, dri, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ĕarchus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lĕarchēus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ĕbădēa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lĕbădīa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Boeotien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ĕbĕdos, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Ionien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lĕbes,</text:span> ētis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kittel:</text:span></text:span> gemini ex ære, Vg.; fulvus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ĕchæum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hamnstad till Corinth.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lecte, Lectio, -tito, -tiuncula, -tor, Lectus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(adj.) se</text:span> Lĕgo.<text:line-break/>Lectic . . ., Lectistern . . ., Lectulus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lectus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lectus,</text:span> i, (us, Pt.), <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af stammen i</text:span> lĕgo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Säng, soffa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af mångahanda form och bestämmelse, sål. hwarpå man sof, studerade, låg till bords, utbars ss. död o. s. w.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Säng:</text:span></text:span> cubicularis l-i fasciæ; l. ad quietem datus; esse in l-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ligga, ligga sjuk);</text:span> l. genialis filiæ nubenti stratus, C.; in l-o quiescere fessum, Sa.; l. jugalis, Vg.; l. genialis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äkta säng)</text:span> in aula est, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bordsoffa;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec. för gudabilder</text:span> (pulvinar) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid</text:span> lectisternia (q. v.): l. aureus, stratus pulcherrime textili stragulo; in medio foro l-os sternere, C.; l. eburnus; l-i imi derisor, Hor.; deorum capita, quæ in l-is erant; l-um senatores straverunt, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwilo-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">studersoffa:</text:span></text:span> C., Pn.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Säng,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarpå en död utbars och s. brändes med honom:</text:span> uni mortuo - plures l-i insternebantur, C.; l-o arsuro imponere alqm, Tib.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lectīca</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bärsoffa, -stol</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (portechaise):</text:span> octophoros <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. bäres af 8 man);</text:span> apertā, opertā l-ā ferri, portari; in aversam l-am caput inferre, C.; l-ā gestare alqm, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lectīcārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bärare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af bärsoffa:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lectīcāriŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Portchäsbärarinna</text:span></text:span> (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bärares älskarinna):</text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lectīcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bärsoffa:</text:span></text:span> l-ā concursare, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Soffa:</text:span></text:span> Su.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Likbår:</text:span></text:span> N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lectisternium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: (sterno): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. soffbäddning), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lectisternium,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> romerskt religionsbruk, s. bestod deri, att gudarnes bilder sattes på</text:span> lecti (tricliniares, pulvinaria) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">framför dukade bord; sådana guda-</text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">måltider anställdes dels i templen, dels - serskildt enligt sibyllinska böckernas anwisning och i swåra tider -</text:span> in foro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> in foris publicis: res divinas facere - in omnibus fanis, in quibus l. majorem partem anni fieri solet; Junoni Reginæ - ad ædem Saturni - Juventati l. factum est; (gravi pestilentique æstate) libri Sibyllini ex senatus consulto aditi sunt. Duumviri sacris faciundis, l-o tunc primum in urbe facto, Herculem, Mercurium atque Neptunum tribus quam amplissime - stratis l-is placavere, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lectisterniātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. ordnar ett lectisternium:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lectŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Säng</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för sofwande l. död):</text:span> philosophi in suis l-is plerumque moriuntur; liber l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ungkarls-),</text:span> C.; tres l-os ad suprema retineri, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Soffa, studersoffa:</text:span></text:span> in exedra Crassus l-o posito quiescebat, C.; quum l. aut porticus me excepit -, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bordsoffa:</text:span></text:span> sternere l-os pellibus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">L</text:span>ēda, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. personn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lēdæus, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Legalis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lex.<text:line-break/>Legat . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lēgo. <text:line-break/>Legifer <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lex.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lĕgio,</text:span> ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sannolikt af</text:span> lĕgo, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wälja, sål. eg.</text:span> = delectus = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">urwal, utskrifning,</text:span> (Varr.)]: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Legion,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> afdelning af en romersk här (brigad), utgörande en skara af</text:span> 4200— 6000 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">man:</text:span> l-em scribere, contrahere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppsätta),</text:span> ducere, dimittere, C.; (dŭci) decernere; ex urbe educere; deducere aliquo; supplere, L.; conscribere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utskrifwa);</text:span> ex hibernis educere; constituere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(postera),</text:span> Cs.; l. prima, decima, rapax, adjutrix, Martia etc., T.; imperitare l-bus, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĕgiōnārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. tjenar i legion</text:span> [ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romersk soldat, i mots. till</text:span> socialis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> auxiliaris, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwensom (i sednare tider, då intet rytteri fanns af romerske borgare) till</text:span> equites]: miles, C.; cohors, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĕgiuncŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Legirup . . ., Legislator, Legitim . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lex.<text:line-break/>Legiuncula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Legio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lĕgo,</text:span> lēgi, lectum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. och i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Plocka, uppsamla, -taga, -fånga:</text:span></text:span> oleam, Cato; nuces; ossa mortui, C.; cochleas, Sa.; spolia cæsorum, L.; olivam, Hor.; extremum halitum alicujus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppfånga);</text:span> flores; mala; vela <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(berga);</text:span> fila <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(upp- l. utdraga ur totten),</text:span> Vg.; arbuteos fetus montanaque fraga, Ov.; sermonem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppfånga),</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Borttaga, -snappa, stjäla:</text:span></text:span> sacrum, C.; sacra, Hor. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uttaga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wälja:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> omnia, quæ virtus l-et quæque rejiciet, unam referentur ad summam; quod autem munus prudentiæ? an l-re intelligenter voluptates?; amasios, C.; ex duabus condicionibus alteram; dii auguriis l-rent, qui Romam regeret, L.; cui lecta potenter erit res, nec facundia deseret hunc nec lucidus ordo, Hor.; vir virum l-it <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i striden till motståndare),</text:span> Vg.; Tiberius respondit, nequaquam decorum pudori suo l-re alqd aut evitare ex eo, cui in universum excusari mallet, T.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. i offentliga förhållanden: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utse, wärfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till soldat; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wälja, nämna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till domare, till senator (det sista om censorerne):</text:span> exemplo militari, quo vir virum l-it, T.; milites viritim l-rat (Mardonius), N.; optimos viros (judices) l-re; censor me in senatum l-it; scribam l., C.; primores in patres l-it; in senatum l.; senatum l., L., T. <text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerfara, genomfara; wandra, fara förbi, utmed:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> pontum; freta; vestigia observata l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(följa)</text:span> retro; oram litoris, Vg.; vestigia (alicujus) gressu; saltus, Ōv.; oram Italiæ, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med ögonen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerfara, mönstra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> lustro): omnes adversos l-re et venientum discere vultus, Vg.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Läsa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för sig sjelf </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Läsa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">läsa om</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">studera</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (absol. l. med sakl. och personl. obj.):</text:span> libros; sepulcra (= inscriptiones sepulcrales); tempus consumere in l-do; mea; nostra; Græca; Latina; Platonis Gorgiam; scriptorem; Græci a Græcis l-untur; lucus ille - sæpe a me l-tus in Mario, C.; librum; facta, N.; contractum l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(studera);</text:span> l-es et percontabere doctos; legi digna, Hor.; Horatius solus fere lyricorum legi dignus, Qu.; alqd intente, Pn.; alqd invitis oculis, Ov. me l-at - puella, Ppt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppläsa, föreläsa:</text:span></text:span> Antimachum volumen suum l-entem omnes præter Platonem reliquerunt; l-re aliquid convivis suis; orationes alicujus, C.; l-do occidere alqm; obturem patulas impune l-ntibus aures, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="T2">part. pf.</text:span>:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lectus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wald, utsökt, (förträfflig, ädel):</text:span></text:span> l-i et exercitati in audaciam; centuriones l-os in primam aciem subducit, Sa.; verba l-a et illustria; femina l-ior, l-sima; adolescens l-simus, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lecte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span> (inc. l.): Varr., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lectio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Plockande:</text:span></text:span> lapidum, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utnämning, wal:</text:span></text:span> judicum, C.; senatus, L., Su.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Läsning; text; läsart:</text:span></text:span> librorum l-e delectari; l-em sine ulla delectatione negligo, C.; juris, Amm., Mcb. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lectiuncŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lätt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Läsning, lecture:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lectĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Frequ.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pläga samla:</text:span></text:span> conchulas in litore, Val.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ofta, flitigt läsa, studera; pläga läsa:</text:span></text:span> Platonem Demosthenes; auctores, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lector</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Läsare:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den, som (för tillfället) läser, studerar ngt:</text:span> quem ego l-em timeam?; jucunditate aliqua allicere l-em, C.; l-es exemplis docere, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Föreläsare, uppläsare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till yrket), person, som enskildt föreläser l. wid en offentlig förhandling uppläser handlingar:</text:span> Crassi scriptor et l. Diphilus, C.; Brutus (in judicio) duobus l-bus singulas Crassi orationes legendas dedit, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĕgŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppsamlare, plockare:</text:span></text:span> oleæ, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Allĕgo</text:span>, lēgi, lectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wälja till, ytterligare (ny); inwälja, upptaga:</text:span></text:span> augures, L.; patricios, Su.; alqm inter prætorios, Pn.; alqm in decurias; peregrinos in senatum, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collēga</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wald tillsammans med ngn,</text:span> Varr.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Embetsbroder:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> in censura; in prætura; regni, C.; c-am in locum Bruti (Valerius) non subrogaverat; Fabius consul creatur, Decio c-ā, L. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: (medbroder):</text:span> servi, Pt.; Metrodorus Epicuri c. sapientiæ, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collēgium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kamratskap</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i embete l. ss. embetsmän, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">samregering</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om consuler):</text:span> alicui pro c-o officia præstare, C. ep.; concordi c-o expertus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(pröfwad)</text:span> alicui, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Samfund af embetsbröder,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T2">collegium:</text:span></text:span> prætorum; pontificum; cooptare alqm in c-um; deferre alqd ad c-um; agere causam apud c-um, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om föreningar i allm. för gemensamma ändamål (wanl. för yrken och </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">borgerliga intressen,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mots.</text:span> sodalitas = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">religiöst samfund): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brödraskap, skrå, gille, samfund</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (auctoriseradt l. otillåtet):</text:span> mercatorum, L.; fabrorum; figulorum, Pn.; c-a, quæ senatus sustulerat, restituta et nova ex omni fæce urbis ac servitio concitata; nulla erat (Romæ) vectigalium societas, nullum c. aut concilium aut omnino aliquod commune consilium, quod non honorificentissime decrevisset de mea salute, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collēgiālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: Inscr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collĭgo</text:span>, lēgi, lectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Samla, sammanplocka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Samla, plocka, uppsamla,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med sakl. och personl. object:</text:span> rosas, Vg.; fructus; humores c-tos bibere, Hor.; uvas, Ov.; āer humorem; rebus opus est exquisitis undique et c-tis, arcessitis, comportatis, C.; sarmenta, Cs.; vasa, sarcinas c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(packa in),</text:span> Sa.; stipem, L.; bonos viros de pagis c-re; exercitus c-tus ex senibus desperatis, ex rusticis decoctoribus; testes domestico præconio, C.; manum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(här),</text:span> N.; se c-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om trupper);</text:span> in æstuaria c-i, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tigga:</text:span> vivere c-to <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af allmosor),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppsamla, -taga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, s. utbreder sig = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hopdraga, draga in, hämma;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">pass.</text:span>: = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sluta, draga sig tillsamman:</text:span></text:span> pallium, Pt.; nuda genu nodoque sinus c-ta fluentes, Vg.; capillos in nodum; equos, Ov.; hastas, T.; milites breviori spatio c-ti, L.; in alitis figuram c-tus, Ov. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">samla = draga till sig (om wätskor, s. samla sig i kroppen):</text:span> sanguinem vitiosum, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upptaga, -hemta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, s. fallit:</text:span> librum, Pn.; ex pulvere alqd, Mt.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tanken, i minnet, i tal, i skrift </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Samla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (erinra sig); spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">uppräkna, hopräkna, räkna:</text:span></text:span> animo veteres civitatum maximarum calamitates, C.; ea <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sådana fall)</text:span> Posidonius c-ēgit permulta; argumenta; peccata et vitia; laudes; multorum naufragia fortunæ; omnia bella civilia, C.; anni a regno alicujus ad illos consules c-untur, Pn.; centum et viginti anni ab interitu Ciceronis in hunc diem c-untur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(man får en summa af -, räknar),</text:span> T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hemta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mod, krafter; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fatta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> betagas af en känsla; wanl.</text:span> se c.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hemta sig, samla sig, fatta sig, besinna sig, komma till besinning:</text:span></text:span> animum, C.; hostes animos; vires c. ad alqd, L.; iras c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> ponere), Hor.; mentem, Ov.; Crassus sui c-di causa se in Tusculanum <text:soft-page-break/>suum contulerat; primo perterritus surrexit: dein quum se c-isset, recubuit; c-ite vos (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">besinnen, hejden eder),</text:span> tribuni plebis, conspirate nobiscum, consentite cum bonis; iratis subtrahendi sunt (ii, quibus sunt irati), dum se c-ant, C.; ex timore se c., Cs. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förwärfwa, winna, skörda; ådraga sig:</text:span></text:span> blanditiis benevolentiam civium; rumorem bonum; magnam gratiam ex labore aliquo; existimatio multo sudore, labore, vigiliis c-ta; injuriam, invidiam, C.; frigus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förkylning),</text:span> Hor.; sitim, Vg.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sluta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt af ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">döma:</text:span></text:span> ita ratione c-it, ut statuat - -; aperte, acute; bene c-it Aristoteles, hæc pueris et mulierculis grata esse, constanti viro non item; ex eo c-re potes, quanta occupatione distinear, C.; inde paucitatem c., L.; aliquid signis, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collecta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanskott, bidrag:</text:span></text:span> a conviva c-am exigere, C., Pn. ep. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collectāneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hopsamlad:</text:span></text:span> æs c-um; hoc est ex usu coëmptum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collectīcius</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collectītius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Samlad, hoprafsad:</text:span></text:span> miles, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collectio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanplockande, hopsamlande; samling, stockning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af wätskor:</text:span> membrorum (fratris Absyrthi), C.; panis mollit c-es, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hopsamlande af punkter, argument, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Recapitulation:</text:span></text:span> partitiones, de quibus dicturus esset, et c-es (eorum, quæ dicta erant), C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förwärfwande:</text:span></text:span> amicorum, Sen.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slutsats:</text:span></text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collectīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Samlad:</text:span></text:span> humor, Sen.<text:line-break/>b. quæstio, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. beror på slutsats (jfr</text:span> conjecturalis), Qu.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nomen, s. utmärker en samlad mångfald, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Collectiv:</text:span></text:span> Gramm. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Collectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Samlande:</text:span></text:span> aquæ, Lucr. (inc. l.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕcollĭgo</text:span>, lēgi, lectum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ånyo, åter samla, draga till sig, upptaga:</text:span></text:span> ova, Col.; milites; gladium, Js.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åter winna:</text:span></text:span> animum alicujus, C.<text:line-break/>b. iras, Lucr.; se æger <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hemtar sig);</text:span> vires a longa valetudine, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlĭgo</text:span>, lēgi, lectum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afplocka:</text:span></text:span> oleam; uvam, Cato; rosam, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afsöndra, -skilja, -lägsna:</text:span></text:span> amentem, Pt.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utwälja, -taga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ur ett antal ss. den förnämste); i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utse, -wälja, utkora:</text:span></text:span> virum optimum ad sacra accipienda; unum ex cunctis; alqm in senatum; milites <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wärfwa);</text:span> alqm ex omnibus, qui præponatur bello, C.; alqm ducem; idoneos homines rei d.; locum domicilio, castris; defensores oppido, Cs.; generum; oppida; domicilia, L.; ab omni ordine d. alqm; alqm comitem, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlectus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utwald, -sökt:</text:span></text:span> d-a legio, Cs.; manus d-a, Sa., N.; d-i equites, pedites, Sa.; d-a juventus, Vg.; eques, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dē</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="_GoBack"/><text:span text:style-name="T3">lectio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wal:</text:span></text:span> Vop.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dēlectus</text:span> (dīlectus), us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Urwal, wal:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> verborum d. origo est eloquentiæ, Cs. ap. C.; d. judicum; ad rem d-um adhibere, C.<text:line-break/>2.<text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Urskilning, åtskilnad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (eg. ss. handling):</text:span> habere d-um civis et peregrini; beneficiorum acceptorum d-us sunt habendi; rerum d-um tenere, tollere, relinquere, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utskrifning, wärfning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af soldater:</text:span> superbissimus d.; d-um agere, habere, C.; d-um militum habere, conficere, Cs.; novi, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlĭgo</text:span>, lexi, lectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utkora) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wärdera, hålla kär, finna behag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tycka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hålla af, älska:</text:span></text:span> (”d. ad judicium, amare ad animi sensum magis pertinet”): nunc denique amare videor, antea d-isse; me aut amabis aut - quo contentus sum - d-es; a me non d-eris solum, sed etiam amaris; feræ partus suos d-unt; alqm valde, mirifice, unice, admodum; usque eo ut - -; alicujus diligentiam, prudentiam - d.; se, C.; nimium d. amicum, Vg.; mulierem, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlectus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utkorad, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wärderad, kär, omtyckt:</text:span></text:span> d-i tibi Virgilius Variusque poētæ; d-e Mæcenas, Hor.; o luce magis d-a sorori, Vg.; d-simus, St.; d-ior, Mcb. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlector</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Älskare:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Delectus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr Madv.</text:span> Præf. ad. Ed. Liv.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlĭgens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sorgfällig, noggrann, aktsam, mån</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om -; spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sparsam,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (noga) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hushållsaktig:</text:span></text:span> cautus et d.; d. et attentus; d. et assidua scriptura; experientissimus ac d-simus; in promerendo; in omni genere; ad custodiendum; vir omnis officii, salutis meæ d-simus, C.; d-ior, Cs.; veritatis, N.; homo frugi et d.; in re hereditaria, C.; de suo d., negligens de alieno, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlĭgenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sorgfälligt, omsorgsfullt, noggrannt, samwetsgrannt, (wäl), warsamt:</text:span></text:span> curare aliquid studiose et d.; legere, audire, cogitare d.; tenere modum rei; d-sime obire diem et munus aliquod; iterum Lælius multo d-ius et melius dixit, C., Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dīlĭgentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sorgfällighet, omsorgsfullhet, noggrannhet, punktlighet, aktsamhet, samwetsgrannhet;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hushållsaktighet:</text:span></text:span> adhibere d-am in amicitiis comparandis; cura, attentio animi, cogitatio, vigilantia, assiduitas, labor: complectar uno verbo, - d-a; d-am consumere in re, conferre ad rem; d. quum in omnibus rebus, tum maxime in causis defendendis multum valet; scribere cum cura et d-a; industriam meam celeritas reditionis, d-am multitudo literarum et testium declaravit, C.; cur (milites) de sua virtute aut de ipsius (i. e. imperatoris) d-a desperarent?; non mediocrem sibi d-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(aktsamhet)</text:span> adhibendam esse intelligebat, Cs.; conservare rem familiarem parsimoniā et d-ā; tantum interest inter vestram (leges agrarias accipientium) et privatorum d-am, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indīlĭgens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T2">Comp.</text:span> -ior: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oaktsam, wårdslös</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ej hushållsaktig):</text:span> paterfamilias non i., N.; si i-ores fuerint, milia hominum LXXX una interitura demonstrat, Cs.; rei, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indīlĭgenter</text:span>, -ius, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wårdslöst, oaktsamt, liknöjdt:</text:span></text:span> nec i. nec illiberaliter facere, C.; bene parta i. tutari, Ter.; præsidia servare i-ius, Cs. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Indīlĭgentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wårdslöshet, oaktsamhet, liknöjdhet:</text:span></text:span> raro missarum literarum i., C.; veri, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Perdīlĭgens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mycket noggrann, punktlig:</text:span></text:span> res operosa est et hominis p-is, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Perdīlĭgenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlĭgo</text:span>, lēgi, lectum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utplocka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (utrycka):</text:span> stirpes; fibras stirpium e-re (alii: elidere), C.; herbas, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utplocka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = (excerpera) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utwälja, wälja, utse:</text:span></text:span> ex orationibus aut poēmatis exempla; minima e malis; e duobus malis levius; e-as, utrum velis; alqm de tribus; alqd a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från; ej af, bland)</text:span> multis; ad munus e-re alqm; vos duo elēgi, quos præcipue colerem, C.; urbi condendæ locum e-re, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlectus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wald, utwald, utsökt:</text:span></text:span> verba e-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wårdadt språk);</text:span> e-sima femina; viri e-simi ejus civitatis, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlecta</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T2">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utdrag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (excerpt):</text:span> Pn. ep.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlecte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med wal, urskilning:</text:span></text:span> descripte et e. in genus quodque causæ - ex hac copia digeremus, C.; e-ius, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlectĭbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: Ap. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlectĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: Varr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utsökt.</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlectio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wal:</text:span></text:span> judicium e-oque verborum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlecto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wärfwa, utskrifwa:</text:span></text:span> legionem, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlector</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wäljare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. förstår att wälja):</text:span> ipsi ab aliis eligendi potius, quam boni e-es existimentur, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ēlectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wal:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illectus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oläst:</text:span></text:span> scriptum i-um remittere, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intellĭgo</text:span>, lexi, lectum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uppfatta ngt, s. säges, ses, försiggår o. s. w. (jfr</text:span> intercipio)] <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med det tänkande förståndet; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Begripa, fatta, förstå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> Plato non solum i-di, sed etiam dicendi gravissimus auctor; i-di prudentia, C.; animum, sententiam alicujus i.; minus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(icke rätt),</text:span> satis i., Ter.; id si minus i-itur; id ex se i-itur; orationem alicujus; corpus quid sit, i-o: quasi corpus quid sit, nullo prorsus modo i-o; in vivo i-i potest, te regno carere, in mortuo non potest, C.; alqd; id est facile i-tu, Cs.; Catonem sua ætas non i-xit, Sen.<text:line-break/>2.<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Finna, märka, lägga märke till, inse, (lära sig att inse):</text:span></text:span> ex quo i-itur, corporis voluptatem non satis dignam esse hominis præstantia; ex Demosthenis epistolis i-itur, quam frequens fuerit Platonis auditor; magna ex parvis i.; ex literis, de gestu alicujus i. alqd; quid respondeat; i-dum est, nos duabus indutos esse personis; ipsi i-amus, naturā nasci amicitiam, C.; ante inito, ut i-tum est, consilio, Cs.; aliquid ex vultu alicujus; quo valeat; cur fiat, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Märka, finna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om sinl. förnimmelse), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">warseblifwa, förnimma, känna:</text:span></text:span> non i-itur quando obrepat senectus, C.; magnam i-xit solitudinem, Sa.; quæ ipse i-at, quæ civitas queratur, ostendit, Cs.; obrepit non i-ta senectus, Juv. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tänka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tänka sig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> förstå, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fatta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> något så l. så, såsom sådant l. sådant, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mena</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> det l. det med något:</text:span> hæc sine corpore nec fieri <text:soft-page-break/>possunt nec i-i; eam concursionem (atomorum) ex infinito tempore i-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tänkas skeende)</text:span> convenit; hoc ne in deo quidem majus quidquam i-i potest; deus alio modo i-i non potest, nisi mens soluta et libera; quæ talis animi figura i-i potest?; nemo eorum sic sapiens fuit, ut sapientem volumus i-i; videbunt, quem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hurudan)</text:span> (animum) in ipso corpore i-ant; et generale quoddam honestum i-imus - et aliud huic subjectum; prudentiam aliam quandam virtutem i-imus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intellĭgens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med förnuft</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tankeförmåga begåfwad; förnuftig:</text:span></text:span> nihil non i-ens i-ente præstantius est; deos i-es esse concedimus; i. et sentiens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förnuftig och sjelfmedweten),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förståndig, insigtsfull; sakförståndig, -kunnig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> isynn. i fråga om æsthetiska ting (kännare):</text:span> stulto i. quid interest!, Ter.; vir doctus et i.; i. dicendi existimator; homo i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i fr. om konstwerk)</text:span> et ingeniosus; judicium i.; rei; in re, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intellectio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: i. est, quum res tota parva ex parte cognoscitur aut ex toto pars (synecdoche): C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intellectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förstånd:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förstående, märkande, begripande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt:</text:span> patrii sermonis; precum, Pn.; dissimulare i-um insidiarum, T.; rei facilior i.; capere i-um rei, Qu.; i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sinlig)</text:span> acrimoniæ, Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förstånd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. förmåga:</text:span> i-u consequi aliquid, Qu.; noster i., Sen.<text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mening, betydelse:</text:span></text:span> duplex verborum, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intellectuālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till förståndet hörande:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intellĭgenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">begripligt; så att man förstås:</text:span> i. ut audiamur et attente, a rebus ipsis ordiendum est, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intellĭgentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Begrepp, begripande; begrepps-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fattnings-, omdömes-förmåga; förstånd:</text:span></text:span> id honestum, quod in nostram i-am cadit; ab imperitorum i-a sensuque disjunctum; communi i-ā contentum esse; deus inclusit i-am in animo; in odore, in sapore est quædam, etsi vitiosa, i., C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Insigt, insigter, klokhet, insigtsfullhet; sakkunskap, förstånd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på en sak:</text:span> anteire omnes i-ā; i-æ conjuncta justitia; habere i-am ruris, in rebus rusticis, pecuniæ quærendæ, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Intellĭgĭbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som med tanken kan fattas (ideel, andlig):</text:span> bonum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> sensibile), Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förnimbar:</text:span></text:span> corpus, Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Neglĭgo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(neglĕgo), lexi, (neglēgi, Lucr.), lectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ej upptaga), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ej wårda sig om:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wara likgiltig för; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ej bry sig om, ej fråga efter, ej akta; åsido-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillbakasätta, förakta:</text:span></text:span> credit se n-i, Ter.; periculum capitis sui præ amico; minas; spem; Epicurus ornamenta orationis n-xit; exempla majorum; leges; auctoritatem senatus; publica jura; mortem sapiens, C.; deos, Sa., Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ej l. illa sköta), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wårdslösa, försumma:</text:span></text:span> (negotium), Ter.; mandatum; provinciam, C.; forma n-ta, Ov.; rem familiarem, N.; n-ti <text:soft-page-break/>agri, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T2">inf.</text:span>: diem edicti obire, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Låta ske</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">passera, lemna ostraffad, ohämnad; ej sky</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. taga sig till wara för -:</text:span> pecuniam captam; n-i macula judiciorum non posse videbatur, C.; (promisit Cæsar) se injurias Hæduorum non n-turum, Cs.; Galliam vastari a Germanis, Su.; fraudem committere, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Neglĭgens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Likgiltig, liknöjd; s. ej aktar; ej frågande efter:</text:span></text:span> legum; officii; sociorum et amicorum; in alqm, C.; sui, Sen.; circa deos et religiones n-ior, Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wårdslös, försumlig, slarfwig (slösaktig):</text:span></text:span> dux n. et dissolutus; non potui in illo sumptu non necessario n. esse, C.; de alieno, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Neglectio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Likgiltig behandling,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> bristande månhet om -:</text:span> amicorum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Neglectus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: id.: hæc res mihi non est n-ui, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Neglĭgenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T2">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Likgiltigt, -nöjdt; med ringaktning; försumligt, wårdslöst:</text:span></text:span> amicos habere n-sime, Sen., Su.; n. agere, tractare alqd; scribere alqd n.; asservare n-ius, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Neglĭgentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Likgiltighet, likgiltig behandling:</text:span></text:span> cognatorum, Ter.; non ingrata n., C.; fortunæ, Sen. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wårdslöshet, försumlighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ngt:</text:span> harum rerum n-ā plerasque causas amitti videmus; plecti n-ā in aliqua re; fugere agrestem et inhumanam n-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i sitt yttre),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Perlĕgo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(pellego, Inscr.; Prisc.), lēgi, lectum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med ögonen) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerfara, mönstra:</text:span></text:span> omnia oculis, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomläsa, läsa, uppläsa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till slut:</text:span> librum tuum, C.; epistolam, Cs.; Tiberius librum (in senatu) p-dum filio tradidit, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Perlectio</text:span> <text:line-break/>(pellectio), ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomläsning:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prælĕgo</text:span>, lēgi, lectum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wälja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (framför andre):</text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fara förbi:</text:span></text:span> T. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Föreläsa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer ngt för någon:</text:span> pueris auctores, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prælectio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T2">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Föreläsande, -läsning:</text:span></text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prælector</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T2">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Föreläsare:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rĕlĕgo</text:span>, lēgi, lectum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åter upptaga, -samla, fara utmed, förbi</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">öfwer:</text:span></text:span> janua (Labyrinthi) inventa est filo r-to <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(åter följd),</text:span> Ov.; Asiam, T.; litora, Vg.; aquas, Ov.; iter, St.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Läsa om, läsa på nytt:</text:span></text:span> Trojani belli scriptorem, Hor.;</text:p>
  </office:text>
 </office:body>
</office:document>